earch it on the Internet. In this technologic era, you should see all of them as potential customers, as they will search on the web even for the things they buy or services they need. Having a website is so normal that customers suppose every business is present on the web on its own website. Being active in the social media is one side, but you also need a website where the followers can purchase your product or can search for more details of your services.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">23</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=13</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',208,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(325,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,209,1613898996,1532521450,5,0,0,2528,'theme_blogteaser','','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,125901,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">9 tendencat e dizajnit web pr vitin 2018</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Ekspertt e dizajn n web prballen me sfidat teknike por edhe vazhdojn t krijojn faqe t thjeshta pr prdoruesin, elegante dhe t prshtatshme me do pajisje mobile.N vitin 2017 ka avancuar shum prdorimi i faqeve t internetit n paisjet mobile. Aktualisht, lundrimi n aplikacione web mobile numron m shum prdorues sesa lundrimi n web nga kompjuter apo laptop. Kjo sht nj nga arsyet pse viti 2018 do t sjell funksionalitete dhe mnyra t reja pr paisjet mobile. N vazhdim prmenden disa tendenca t dizajnit web pr vitin 2018.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">24</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=14</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',209,'a:11:{s:5:\"CType\";s:20:\"fluidcontent_content\";s:14:\"tx_fed_fcefile\";s:21:\"Theme:BlogTeaser.html\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125901;s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1218:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">9 web design trends in 2018</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Web designers deal with the technical challenges, which are large in number. But they still continue to create user-friendly sites, stylish and flexible with every device and just beautiful all at once. 2017 made more advancement in mobile browsing, who now counts more users than desktop browsing. This is a reason why 2018 is going to have fully mobile functionalities in new ways. Meanwhile, desktops will evolve in such way to stay relevant. So, lets take a look at some web design trends in 2018.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">24</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=14</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i: