"vDEF\">Web Design vs Web Development</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">When someone asks me what I do for the living, I usually answer I am a web designer. This is what people mostly understand, in general.In fact, this term is used when I am introduced to someone who is not a computer scientist or programmer. The truth is that people use both web design and web development, as the same concept. But, when you apply for a job in the web industry, these terms are completely different. Lets specify in details these two terms.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">25</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=15</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',210,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(327,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,220,1613898965,1532521465,5,0,0,1539,'theme_blogteaser','','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,125903,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">TYPO3 Extensions per il tuo negozio online</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">TYPO3  una soluzione per la maggior parte dei siti Web, in particolare per le aziende e i grandi negozi. Quale  la soluzione di TYPO3 per l\'e-commerce? Quali sono i principali sistemi di negozi TYP