i responsive</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Me shum mundsi keni dgjuar pr dizajnin Responsive, por a e keni menduar ndonjher se far sht saktsisht nj dizajn i till dhe pse ka marr emrtimin si dizajn Responsiv? Dizajni Responsive ose ndryshe dizajni i prshtatshm sht teknologjia q lejon faqen e internetit t prshtatet me pajisjen e prdoruesit.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=23</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">34</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"alt\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\"></value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',353,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:16:\"theme_blogteaser\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125901;s:6:\"header\";s:21:\"Responsive Web Design\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1454:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Responsive Web Design</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Responsive Design is the technique which allows the website to adapt to the device of the user. The programmer can write the code once and publish it everywhere, meaning less work for him. The number of visitors that come to the website from a smartphone, tablet or iPods is increasing every minute. Statistically, in 2018 there are about 2.6 billion people in the world using the smartphone. Actually, the small businesses are increasing their presence in the mobile applications, using their websites, the social media, and other applications which promote their business. This means more and more websites are going to be Responsive.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=23</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">34</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"alt\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\"></value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',353,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(355,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,352,1613898963,1544249798,1,0,0,2096,'theme_blogteaser','Shopify apo Magento','','',NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,125902,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Shopify apo Magento?</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Deri pak vite m par, platforma kryesore e shitjeve online kishte emrin Magento. Por koht e fundit, nj tjetr platform sht e preferuara e shum shitsve dhe klientve. Ajo quhet Shopify.\n\nN t vrtet, Shopify dhe Magento jan dy nga platformat m t njohura t shitjeve online. Ata ndryshojn shum nga njra-tjetra. N kt artikull dalin n pah kto dallime, n mnyr q ju t vendosni vet se cila sht platforma m e prshtatshme pr dyqan tuaj online.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=19</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">31</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"alt\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\"></value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',352,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:16:\"theme_blogteaser\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125902;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1065:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Shopify vs Magento</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Shopify and Magento are two of the most popular e-commerce platforms on the market. They differ a lot from each other. In this article, these differences are highlighted, so you can decide which is the right e-commerce platform for your online store.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=19</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">31</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"alt\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\"></value>\n           