0,0),(358,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,358,1580827881,1580827881,13,0,0,512,'text','Shopify vs Magento','','','<p>A few years ago, the market of the e-commerce platforms was mainly called Magento. But recently, a different way of setting up an online store is attracting both sellers and clients. It is called Shopify.</p>\r\n<p>If you own a business, you may have an existing e-commerce store or are looking to expand into this area, youre probably wondering what the best e-Commerce platform to use in 2019? According to Google Trends, while comparing, Shopify vs Magento, Shopify looks more popular compared to Magento.<br /> Actually,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/free-trial?ref=wbe&amp;subid1=vsMagento&amp;subid2=23f8b8601d23ad4c1d3fc0ad2e001424\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Shopify</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://magento.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Magento</a>&nbsp;are two of the most popular e-commerce platforms on the market. They differ a lot from each other. In the end of this guide, youll have a much clear idea to choose, which is the right e-commerce platform for your online store.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:23:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(359,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,359,1580827969,1580827969,13,0,0,6144,'textpic','The main differences','','','<p>Shopify is commercial,&nbsp;a software-as-a-service (SAAS), so users pay a monthly fee to get its services.&nbsp;&nbsp;Magento is free and open source software. Shopify is hosted by its own host, which makes easier the setup and configurations. Magento is hosted by your hosting. The installation and configuration need web programming skills. At the end of the setup, you can start building the online store.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(360,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,360,1580890730,1580890730,13,0,0,6400,'textpic','The easy platform','','','<p>Starting a new business is not easy. At least, the platform of the web store should be easy and helpful. If you choose a platform that adds stress in your work, then you should not focus on your own products and sales, but in the store itself. You better build your store in a platform you soon master and in which you are comfortable with.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify gives you the interactive way to build the website just by drag and drop the elements in the interface. You can set up the store just by moving the components in the way you like to arrange them, so you can quickly start selling. The process of adding new images to the store makes it unique and personalized. Also, the process of setting up the payment method is so easy so you can soon start making money, without worrying about the procedures.&nbsp;Beginners will find Shopify easy to use.</p>\r\n<p>Although very flexible Magento is more complex to use than Shopify. You should learn some technical terms and some code before start selling at a Magento store. Magento platform is less user-friendly and the process of setting up the store requires to navigate is some blocks before becoming a seller. Magento is powerful for experienced users, but a bit difficult for the beginners. This means you need some professional tricks to manage the full functionality it offers.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(361,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1559406812,1544252008,1,0,0,6656,'textpic','More Apps means more functions','','','<p>Both Shopify and Magento have a huge number of main functions, which cover important tasks like marketing, inventory, finance, etc. But for any specific tool, you need to install a new app or an extension of your store. Such software helps you in adding extra functionality and to speed any procedure so you can focus on sales and not on the online store itself.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify App Store offers more than 2 300 applications, free and paid. You can install them by just clicking on it, and personalize it. Some useful apps are those who integrate your store with social media, or with your email. Such connections will increase dramatically the sales of your online store.</p>\r\n<p>Magento Marketplace has over 3 000 extensions, free or paid. Some of them require few coding skills to insert them in the online store and to personalize them. But to us, Magento seems powerful in the wide range of extra functions and in the extensions it offers. Practically, you can do quite everything with Magento extensions, and all you need is to choose the right one and to know how to use it properly.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(362,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,362,1580891157,1580891157,13,0,0,6912,'textpic','Your budget, a key factor','','','<p>The budget is crucial aspect to consider when choosing an e-commerce platform. Shopify and Magento differ in their fees and in their operating costs. Shopify comes with a monthly fee, but it includes the host fee and maintenance service fee. Each premium application has an extra monthly fee.</p>\r\n<p>Magento is a free and open source software but it does not include the cost of hosting. Many Magento apps have fees and in an overall overview, you will need to consult to a web developer to integrate and to configure the Magento apps.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(363,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,363,1580891717,1580891717,13,0,0,7168,'textpic','The size of the store will make you decide','','','<p>Shopify and Magento both are powerful eCommerce platforms, you can make the choice between Shopify vs Magento, based on the size of your business. Shopify offers the Shopify Lite which allow you to sell via Facebook. It also offers three packages: Basic Shopify, Advanced Shopify, and Shopify Plus. Shopify its easy to use with a great customer service.</p>\r\n<p>You can choose them depending on your needs and your budget. If you own a small business, Shopify is a promising eCommerce platform.</p>\r\n<p>Magento, on the other hand, is built on an open-source framework, its offers the Community package as the right platform for small online shops and the Enterprise package for larger online brands. It has a large extensions marketplace that enables more features for your site and is a platform that prides on its extraordinary scalability for complex and long-term operations.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(364,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1548606057,1544252968,1,0,0,7424,'textpic','Hosting the online store','','','<p>The process of setting up the host in a Shopify store is easy because the whole process can last few minutes, and Shopify provides you the complete solution for hosting your online store. Meanwhile, Magento gives you the responsibility of hosting, downloading, installing and setting up the platform for the new store.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(365,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1548606077,1544253013,1,0,0,7680,'text','The everyday Store Management','','','<p>As soon as you set up your online store, you should add or update product details and manage the inventory. Both Shopify and Magento have a product section which enables the seller to manage to products. If you are not an IT or Web specialist, Shopify is the easiest platform to manage your online store, because of its user-friendly interface.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:23:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(366,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,366,1580892183,1580892183,13,0,0,7936,'textpic','Best for SEO','','','<p>According to statistics, 93% of all website visits start with an online search. Ranking your page high on the list of relevance for a particular search term can be more important and useful than any form of advertising. The best shop is those who have customers shopping there. Both platforms offer good deliver traffic, which is translated as good SEO (search engine optimization) to deliver traffic.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(367,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,367,1580892347,1580892347,13,0,0,8192,'textpic','Themes for a stylish shop','','','<p>When your customers visit your website, the theme of your e-Commerce website will create the first impression.<br /> In both platforms, Shopify and Magento, the look and feel of the store are created by themes.</p>\r\n<p>In both platforms, Shopify and Magento, the look and feel of the store are created by themes. Some of their most basic themes are free. Themes with attractive features are in a symbolic price. If you want a classic image of your store, Magento has lots of such themes. If you want a different image of your store, Shopify themes are better from a design view.</p>\r\n<p>From the technical point, Shopify themes are easier in installation and in modification than the Magento themes.</p>\r\n<p>From the design and the UX aspect, Shopify offers the best-looking themes, without any doubt.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(368,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1548606141,1544253156,1,0,0,8448,'text','Point Of Sale','','','<p>It is an important key solution the web platform offers to the point of sale. Shopify offers a Point of Sale app that runs on any mobile or desktop device and accepts credit card payment. Magento also offers Point of Sales options which are extensions in the marketplace.<br /> <br /> &nbsp;</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:23:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(369,19,0,0,0,0,0,1582036416,0,369,1582034432,1582034432,13,0,0,8704,'textpic','So which one should you choose?','','','<p>Both Shopify and Magento are powerful e-commerce platforms. Shopify is far easier and fully managed system. Meanwhile, Magento is costless and more complex regarding the installations and customizations.</p>\r\n<p>We cannot define which is the only one choice, to all the stores and business managers that are such differences in needs and in the way they see their business. But as the last suggestion, here are some fantastic Shopify store and some examples of Magento Stores <a href=\"https://w3development.net/work/\" target=\"_blank\">https://w3development.net/work/</a>.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(370,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,358,1552466071,1544253472,1,0,0,3072,'text','Shopify apo Magento','','','<p>Deri pak vite m par, platforma kryesore e shitjeve online kishte emrin Magento. Por koht e fundit, nj tjetr platform sht e preferuara e shum shitsve dhe klientve. Ajo quhet Shopify.</p>\r\n<p>N t vrtet, Shopify dhe Magento jan dy nga platformat m t njohura t shitjeve online. Ata ndryshojn shum nga njra-tjetra. N kt artikull dalin n pah kto dallime, n mnyr q ju t vendosni vet se cila sht platforma m e prshtatshme pr dyqan tuaj online.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',358,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:18:\"Shopify vs Magento\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:480:\"<p>A few years ago, the market of the e-commerce platforms was mainly called Magento. But recently, a different way of setting up an online store is attracting both sellers and clients. It is called Shopify.</p>\r\n<p>Actually, Shopify and Magento are two of the most popular e-commerce platforms on the market. They differ a lot from each other. In this article, these differences are highlighted, so you can decide which is the right e-commerce platform for your online store.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',358,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(371,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,359,1566571710,1544253472,1,0,0,3328,'textpic','Dallimet kryesore','','','<p>Shopify sht me pages. Ju duhet t paguani nj tarif mujore pr t marr shrbimet e saj. Magento sht softuer falas dhe me kod t hapur.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify sht m i leht n konfigurim dhe n host-im. Magento-n do e host-oni ju vet. Instalimi dhe konfigurimi i nj dyqani n Magento krkojn aftsi programimi n Web. Pasi t prfundoni proesin e konfigurimit, ju mund t filloni ndrtimin e dyqanit tuaj online.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',359,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"The main differences\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:370:\"<p>Shopify is commercial. You should pay a monthly fee to get its services. Magento is free and open source software. Shopify is hosted by its own host, which makes easier the setup and configurations. Magento is hosted by your hosting. The installation and configuration need web programming skills. At the end of the setup, you can start building the online store.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',359,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(372,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,360,1566571789,1544253472,1,0,0,3584,'textpic','Platforma m e leht','','','<p>Nisja e nj biznesi t ri nuk sht aspak e leht. Prandaj t paktn platforma e dyqanit online duhet na vihet n ndihm. Nse zgjidhni nj platform q shton stres n punn tuaj, ather nuk do mund t prqendroheni n produktet dhe n shitjet tuaja, por n vet dyqanin. M mir ndrtojeni dyqanin tuaj n nj platform t thjesht dhe t dobishme.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify ofron nj mnyr interaktive pr t ndrtuar faqen e internetit. Ju mund t krijoni listn e produkteve vetm duke lvizur komponentt, duke i sistemuar sipas dshirs.N kt mnyr, ju mund t filloni shpejt shitjen e artikujve. Dyqani bhet me unik dhe i personalizuar duke shtuar imazhe t reja. Gjithashtu, procesi i prcaktimit t mnyrs s pagess sht kaq i leht, sa q shum shpejt ju mund t filloni t bni para, pa u shqetsuar pr procedurat.</p>\r\n<p>Krijimi i nj dyqani me Magento sht pak m ndryshe. Ju duhet t msoni paraprakisht disa terma teknike dhe disa instruksione para se t filloni shitjet. Proesi i krijimit t dyqanit krkon t prcaktimin e disa parametrave para se t bheni shits. Magento sht platform e fuqishme pr prdoruesit me prvoj, por pak e vshtir pr fillestart. Kjo do t thot q keni nevoj pr disa aftsi programimi pr t menaxhuar funksionalitetin e plot q ajo ofron.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',360,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"The easy platform\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1270:\"<p>Starting a new business is not easy. At least, the platform of the web store should be easy and helpful. If you choose a platform that adds stress in your work, then you should not focus on your own products and sales, but in the store itself. You better build your store in a platform you soon master and in which you are comfortable with.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify gives you the interactive way to build the website just by drag and drop the elements in the interface. You can set up the store just by moving the components in the way you like to arrange them, so you can quickly start selling. The process of adding new images to the store makes it unique and personalized. Also, the process of setting up the payment method is so easy so you can soon start making money, without worrying about the procedures.</p>\r\n<p>The beginning with Magento is a bit different. You should learn some technical terms and some code before start selling at a Magento store. Magento platform is less user-friendly and the process of setting up the store requires to navigate is some blocks before becoming a seller. Magento is powerful for experienced users, but a bit difficult for the beginners. This means you need some professional tricks to manage the full functionality it offers.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',360,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(373,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,361,1552464924,1544253472,1,0,0,3840,'textpic','\"M shum App\" do t thot \"M shum mundsi\"','','','<p>T dy, edhe Shopify edhe Magento, ofrojn nj numr t konsiderueshm funksionalitetesh, t cilat mbulojn detyra t rndsishme si marketing, inventar, financ, etj. Por, pr do funksion shtes, ju duhet t instaloni nj aplikacion t ri ose Extension n dyqanin tuaj. Nj softuer i till ju ndihmon n shtimin e funksionalitetit shtes.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify App Store ofron m shum se 2300 aplikacione, me ose pa pages. Ju mund t\'i instaloni ato me nj klik t vetm, dhe me pas ti personalizoni sipas dyqanit tuaj online. Disa aplikacione t dobishme jan ata q integrojn dyqanin tuaj me mediat sociale, ose me email-in tuaj. Lidhje t tilla do t rrisin ndjeshm shitjet e artikujve.</p>\r\n<p>Magento Marketplace ka mbi 3000 Extensions, me ose pa pages. Disa prej tyre krkojn pak aftsi programimi, pr t\'i integruar dhe pr t\'i personalizuar ato. Por pr mendimin e ekspertve tan, Magento sht shum i fuqishm pr vet gamn e gjer t funksioneve q ajo ofron, si dhe pr listn e Extensions. Praktikisht, ju mund t bni gjithka me Extensions n Magento. Gjithka q ju duhet sht t zgjidhni Extension e duhur dhe t dini se si ta prdorni si duhet.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',361,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"More Apps means more functions\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1097:\"<p>Both Shopify and Magento have a huge number of main functions, which cover important tasks like marketing, inventory, finance, etc. But for any specific tool, you need to install a new app or an extension of your store. Such software helps you in adding extra functionality and to speed any procedure so you can focus on sales and not on the online store itself.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify App Store offers more than 2 300 applications, free and paid. You can install them by just clicking on it, and personalize it. Some useful apps are those who integrate your store with social media, or with your email. Such connections will increase dramatically the sales of your online store.</p>\r\n<p>Magento Marketplace has over 3 000 extensions, free or paid. Some of them require few coding skills to insert them in the online store and to personalize them. But to us, Magento seems powerful in the wide range of extra functions and in the extensions it offers. Practically, you can do quite everything with Magento extensions, and all you need is to choose the right one and to know how to use it properly.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',361,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(374,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,362,1566577260,1544253472,1,0,0,4096,'textpic','Buxheti juaj: nj faktor ky','','','<p>Buxheti sht nj faktor q duhet marr parasysh n zgjedhjen e platforms pr shitjet online. Shopify dhe Magento ndryshojn n tarifat dhe n shpenzimet operative. Shopify sht kundrejt nj tarife mujore, e cila prfshin tarifn e host-imit dhe tarifn e shrbimit t mirmbajtjes. Gjithashtu, do aplikacion n nivel Premium ka nj tarif shtes mujore.</p>\r\n<p>Magento sht nj softuer pa pagese dhe me kod t hapur, por nuk prfshin koston e host-imit. Shum Extensions n Magento kan kosto, prandaj ju duhet t konsultoheni me nj zhvillues web pr t integruar dhe konfiguruar kto aplikacione.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',362,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Your budget, a key factor\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:537:\"<p>The budget is a factor you should consider in choosing the web platform. Shopify and Magento differ in their fees and in their operating costs. Shopify comes with a monthly fee, but it includes the host fee and maintenance service fee. Each premium application has an extra monthly fee.</p>\r\n<p>Magento is a free and open source software but it does not include the cost of hosting. Many Magento apps have fees and in an overall overview, you will need to consult to a web developer to integrate and to configure the Magento apps.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',362,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(375,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,363,1552464952,1544253472,1,0,0,4352,'textpic','Madhsia e dyqanit ju on drejt zgjedhjes','','','<p>Ju mund t bni zgjedhjen midis Shopify apo Magento, bazuar n madhsin e biznesit tuaj. Shopify ofron linjn Shopify Lite, e cila ju lejon t shisni nprmjet Facebook-ut. Gjithashtu ofron tre paketa: Basic Shopify, Advanced Shopify dhe Shopify Plus. Mund t\'i zgjidhni ato n varsi t nevojave tuaja dhe buxhetit tuaj. Pr nj fillim m t mir zgjidhni Advanced Shopify, sepse prmban shum opsione t vlefshme pr t filluar nj dyqan online.</p>\r\n<p>Magento ofron paketn Community, si platformn e duhur pr dyqanet e vogla online. Gjithashtu, ajo ofron dhe paketn e Enterprise pr bizneset e mdha.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',363,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:42:\"The size of the store will make you decide\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:562:\"<p>You can make the choice between Shopify vs Magento, based on the size of your business. Shopify offers the Shopify Lite which allow you to sell via Facebook. It also offers three packages: Basic Shopify, Advanced Shopify, and Shopify Plus. You can choose them depending on your needs and your budget. For a startup better choose Advanced Shopify. It contains a whole set of features to initialize an online store.</p>\r\n<p>Magento offers the Community package as the right platform for small online shops and the Enterprise package for large online brands.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',363,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(376,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,364,1566577339,1544253472,1,0,0,4608,'textpic','Host-imi i dyqanit online','','','<p>N Shopify, procesi i host-imit i nj dyqani sht i leht, sepse zgjat maksimumi disa minuta dhe Shopify ju ofron zgjidhjen e plot pr host-im. Ndrkoh, Magento ju ngarkon me prgjegjsin e shkarkimit, instalimit dhe host-imit t dyqanit t ri.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',364,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:24:\"Hosting the online store\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:325:\"<p>The process of setting up the host in a Shopify store is easy because the whole process can last few minutes, and Shopify provides you the complete solution for hosting your online store. Meanwhile, Magento gives you the responsibility of hosting, downloading, installing and setting up the platform for the new store.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',364,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(377,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,365,1552464983,1544253472,1,0,0,4864,'text','Menaxhimi i prditshm i dyqanit','','','<p>T dy, edhe Shopify edhe Magento kan nj seksion t produktit, i cili i mundson shitsit t menaxhoj artikujt n dyqan. Nse nuk jeni nj specialist i IT ose Web, Shopify sht platforma m e leht pr t menaxhuar dyqanin tuaj online, sepse ka ndrfaqen shum t thjesht.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',365,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:29:\"The everyday Store Management\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:351:\"<p>As soon as you set up your online store, you should add or update product details and manage the inventory. Both Shopify and Magento have a product section which enables the seller to manage to products. If you are not an IT or Web specialist, Shopify is the easiest platform to manage your online store, because of its user-friendly interface.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',365,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(378,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,366,1566577423,1544253472,1,0,0,5120,'textpic','Preferencat e SEO','','','<p>Dyqani m i mir sht ai q ka klient q blejn atje. T dy platformat ofrojn shikueshmri t mir nga vizitort.E thn ndryshe, t dyja kto platforma preferohen nga SEO (Search Engine Optimization) i cili rrit numrin e vizitorve.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',366,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"Best for SEO\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:188:\"<p>The best shop is those who have customers shopping there. Both platforms offer good deliver traffic, which is translated as good SEO (search engine optimization) to deliver traffic.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;}',366,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(379,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,367,1552465013,1544253472,1,0,0,5376,'textpic','Stili unik dhe me shije','','','<p>N t dyja platformat, Shopify dhe Magento, stili e dyqanit krijohet nga t ashtuquajtura Theme. Disa nga Theme baz ofrohen falas. Theme me stil unik dhe elegant jan kundrejt nj mimi simbolik. Nse doni nj imazh klasik pr dyqanin tuaj, Magento ofron m shum Theme. Nse doni nj imazh t veant pr dyqanin tuaj, Theme e Shopify jan m elegante nga pikpamja e dizajnit.</p>\r\n<p>Nga ana teknike, Theme t Shopify jan m t lehta n instalim dhe n modifikim sesa Theme n Magento.</p>\r\n<p>Nga dizajni dhe aspekti UX, Shopify ofron, pa dyshim, Theme m t bukura.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',367,'a:31:{s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Themes for a stylish shop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:589:\"<p>In both platforms, Shopify and Magento, the look and feel of the store are created by themes. Some of their most basic themes are free. Themes with attractive features are in a symbolic price. If you want a classic image of your store, Magento has lots of such themes. If you want a different image of your store, Shopify themes are better from a design view.</p>\r\n<p>From the technical point, Shopify themes are easier in installation and in modification than the Magento themes.</p>\r\n<p>From the design and the UX aspect, Shopify offers the best-looking themes, without any doubt.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',367,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(380,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,368,1566577495,1544253472,1,0,0,5632,'textpic','Pikat e shitjeve','','','<p>sht nj zgjidhje e rndsishme q platforma e shitjeve t ofroje disa variante pr pikat e shitjeve.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify ofron nj aplikacion t quajtuar \'Point of Sale\', e cila mund t instalohet n do pajisje mobile ose desktop, dhe pranon pages me kart krediti.</p>\r\n<p>Magento gjithashtu ofron opsione \'Point of Sale\' t cilat realizohen me Extensions dhe gjithashtu lehtsojn proesin e shitjeve.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',368,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"Point Of Sale\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:298:\"<p>It is an important key solution the web platform offers to the point of sale. Shopify offers a Point of Sale app that runs on any mobile or desktop device and accepts credit card payment. Magento also offers Point of Sales options which are extensions in the marketplace.<br /> <br /> &nbsp;</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;}',368,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(381,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,369,1544254526,1544253472,1,0,0,5888,'textpic','Pra, cila sht e duhura?','','','<p>T dyja platformat, Shopify dhe Magento, jan mbizotrueset n e-commerce. Shopify sht sistem shum m i leht dhe efektiv. Ndrkoh, Magento sht falas n nivel baz, por sht m komplekse pr sa i prket instalimeve dhe personalizimit t dyqanit.</p>\r\n<p>Ne nuk mund t prcaktojm se cila sht platforma m e mir pr t gjitha dyqanet online. Ato jan kaq shum n numr, n nevoja dhe n mnyrn se si shihet si biznes. Por, sugjerimi yn prmbylls: hidhini nj shikim dyqaneve online n Magento, t krijuar dhe personalizuar nga stafi yne ekspert, si dhe shembuj shum interesant dyqanesh n Shopify : https://w3development.net/work/.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',369,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:31:\"So which one should you choose?\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:562:\"<p>Both Shopify and Magento are powerful e-commerce platforms. Shopify is far easier and fully managed system. Meanwhile, Magento is costless and more complex regarding the installations and customizations.</p>\r\n<p>We cannot define which is the only one choice, to all the stores and business managers that are such differences in needs and in the way they see their business. But as the last suggestion, here are some fantastic Shopify store and some examples of Magento Stores <a href=\"https://w3development.net/work/\"> https://w3development.net/work/</a>.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',369,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(382,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612143778,1544261126,7,0,0,256,'textpic','Specify the terms','','','<p>When someone asks me what I do for the living, I usually answer I am a web designer. This is what people mostly understand, in general.</p>\r\n<p>In fact, this term is used when I am introduced to someone who is not a computer scientist or programmer.</p>\r\n<p>The truth is that people use both <strong>web design</strong> and web development, as the same concept. But, when you apply for a job in the web industry, these terms are completely different.</p>\r\n<p>Lets specify in details these two terms.<br /> &nbsp;</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(383,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612144714,1544261398,7,0,0,384,'textpic','Web Design','','','<p>Web design represents the set of technical skills used in building the user interface of the website.<br /> Through the use of color, images, typography, and layout, web design constructs the overall image of the website.</p>\r\n<p>Some different areas of web design include web <em><strong>graphic design</strong></em>, <em><strong>interface design</strong></em>, user <strong><em>experience design</em></strong>, and <em><strong>search engine optimization</strong></em>.</p>\r\n<p>A professional web designer knows the principles of the design and applies them to the web design making it look great and user-friendly.<br /> They make not just a pretty website, but also an easy and attractive interface.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(384,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612144958,1544261453,7,0,0,400,'textpic','Web Development','','','<p>Web development includes front-end development and back-end development. They have a different focus, but many web developers master both skills.</p>\r\n<p>Front-end development focuses on programming the layout of the website. A front-end developer builds the graphical layout of how the user sees the website, by using scripting languages such as <em><strong>HTML</strong></em>, styles of <em><strong>CSS</strong></em>, or <em><strong>JavaScript</strong></em>.</p>\r\n<p>The back-end development requires advanced programming skills to implement the functionalities of the website, such as the interface to a database, connections with web services, and similar features.</p>\r\n<p>A professional web developer masters programming skills such as <strong><em>PHP</em></strong>.</p>\r\n<p>He manages how different APIs (Application Programming Interface) is used to connect different web platforms to make the website more flexible and functional.</p>\r\n<p>In the case when the required functionality is not fulfilled from any current library, a professional back-end developer creates the code from scratch and adds the features that meet the clients need.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(385,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612145057,1544261509,7,0,0,416,'textpic','Somewhere in between web design and web development','','','<p>Some web developers are specialized in certain areas, but many others can do both web design and web development.</p>\r\n<p>They might prefer working with visual effects of the web, but also implement the layout in the styles of CSS and in tags of HTML.</p>\r\n<p>This kind of web designer is very useful in the industry of web. Similarly, a web developer who owns basic skills of design and visual communication is very helpful in building web projects and in making smart choices while coding.</p>\r\n<p>However, when someone applies for a job in the web technology, or look for someone to work on a website, the position should be well defined: web design or web development.<br /> The advanced skills will make the difference and will lead to the position.</p>\r\n<p>For larger sites and projects, a team of web professionals will cover all the different fields, both web design, and web development.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(386,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612145184,1544261569,7,0,0,432,'textpic','Full-stack developers','','','<p>Full-stack developers are those who have knowledge of all of the development tasks discussed above.</p>\r\n<p>A full-stack developer should be able to build a website from scratch, beginning with a design, creating the markup of the design, but also implementing back-end functionalities and database queries.</p>\r\n<p>Usually, a full-stack developer has a basic knowledge of design and user experience. Being a full-stack developer does not he should have experience in all programming languages. Its quite impossible to become an expert or a professional in each programming language.</p>\r\n<p>Its also hard to learn all the techniques and strategies on how to be most effective in all of the areas we discussed above. Remember, web technologies are evolving every day.</p>\r\n<p>Toward the same goal, both web designers and web developers work for the same goal  to create a website that attracts the users.</p>\r\n<p>To do this, both the design and development must be at the same professional level. A site should be attractive and functional.</p>\r\n<p>The colors, animations and multimedia elements should represent the brand and the interface needs to encourage visitors to stay longer on the website and to use all its functionality.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\