:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',409,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(492,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,410,1566824990,1544302123,7,0,0,6912,'textpic','Integrimi me Magento: Mage  UniTY','','','<p>Ky softuer sht nj integrim i Magento dhe TYPO3, i quajtur Mage-UniTY. Platforma kryesore sht Magento, por kur t dhnat jan marr nga TYPO3, ata kan prioritet mbi Magento. Konsumatori nuk e di nse prmbajtja e faqes sht nga Magento ose nga TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>M tepr detaje rreth Mage-UniTY:<br /> Homepage https://www.web-vision.de</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',410,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:40:\"Integration with Magento: Mage  UniTY\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:334:\"<p>This software is an integration of Magento and TYPO3, called Mage-UniTY. The main system is Magento, but when data are fetched from TYPO3 they have priority over Magento. The customer does not know if the content is from Magento or from TYPO3.<br /> <br /> More details about Mage-UniTY<br /> Homepage https://www.web-vision.de</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',410,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(493,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,411,1566825029,1544302123,7,0,0,7168,'textpic','Integrimi me Oxid: TOXID','','','<p>Ky softuer sht nj integrim i softuerit t dyqaneve online OXID dhe TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>M tepr detaje rreth TOXID:<br /> Homepage https://www.marmalade.de/kompetenzen/build/toxid/<br /> Repository https://github.com/jkrug/TOXID-cURL</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',411,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:28:\"Integration with Oxid: TOXID\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:231:\"<p>This software is an integration of the shop software OXID and TYPO3.<br /> <br /> More details about TOXID<br /> Homepage https://www.marmalade.de/kompetenzen/build/toxid/<br /> Repository https://github.com/jkrug/TOXID-cURL</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',411,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(494,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,415,1564489449,1544303636,7,0,0,3328,'textpic','Trende','','','<p>Nse ndiqni tendencat m t fundit t teknologjis, do e mendoni vazhdimisht pyetjen se si duket faqja juaj Web ne krahasim me miliona faqe t tjera. Cdo biznes synon rritjen e t ardhurave dhe zhvillimin e identitetit t marks stij.</p>\r\n<p>Nj faktor ky n marketing sht sigurisht faqja e internetit e kompanis suaj si dhe sistemi i saj i menaxhimit. Duke pas parasysh shifrat, sistemi WordPress aktualisht mbizotron tregun, megjithat, TYPO3 po merr gjithashtu nj rol dominues. N dilemn mes TYPO3 dhe WordPress, stafi i W3DEVELOPMENT ju ofron nj zgjidhje optimale t sistemit CMS, bazuar n krkesat tuaja.</p>\r\n<p>Duke iu referuar Google Trends, po rendisim karakteristikat kryesore t ktyre dy sistemeve CMS:</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',415,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Trends \";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:704:\"<p>Are you following the new trends and technologies and always asking how is your website compared to millions of others? Everyone is struggling with increasing revenue and developing its brand identity. A key factor in the market is, of course, the website of your company, and its content management system. Tracing the run of website market, WordPress has already been in the foreground, however, TYPO3 is also taking respectful place currently. In the competition TYPO3 vs WordPress, our team tries to offer an optimal solution for our clients by choosing the CMS according to their requirements.<br /> <br /> Referring to Google Trends, below are listed the key characteristics of both the CMS:</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',415,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(495,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,416,1556603549,1544303636,7,0,0,3584,'textpic','Versioni i Par','','','<p>N vitin 1997, Kasper Skrhj zhvilloi nga fillimi produktin m t ri TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>N vitin 2003, Matt Mullenweg njoftoi q versioni i par i WordPress sht n dispozicion t prdoruesve.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',416,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"First Version\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:168:\"<p>TYPO3s development was started from scratch by Kasper Skrhj in 1997. In 2003, Matt Mullenweg announced the availability of the first version of WordPress.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',416,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(496,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,417,1556603557,1544303636,7,0,0,3840,'textpic','Tendenc dhe aktualitet','','','<p>N t vrtet, TYPO3 sht CMS i prdorur nga 130.998 faqe interneti. Ky sistem sht falas. Ndrkoh, WordPress sht CMS i prdorur nga 27,449,706 faqe interneti. Ky sistem sht gjithashtu falas dhe shum e njohur pr ndrtimin e faqeve personale.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',417,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:19:\"Trend and actuality\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:228:\"<p>Actually, TYPO3 is the CMS used by 130,998 websites. It is free to use. Meanwhile, WordPress is the CMS used by 27,449,706 websites. It is also free to use, and it is well known as a semantic personal publishing platform.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',417,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(497,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,418,1556603567,1544303636,7,0,0,4096,'textpic','Thjeshtsia','','','<p>TYPO3 ofron nj ndrfaqe t leht pr menaxhimin e faqes web. Prdoruesi thjesht do t vendos menun, prmbajtjen dhe prmbajtjen e faqes web. WordPress e tregon thjeshtsin nga vet emri i tij. sht shum i thjesht n prdorim dhe do blogg-er e dashuron. Ju nuk keni nevoj t dini ndonj truk teknologjik pr t shtuar prmbajtje n faqen tuaj te internetit n WordPress.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',418,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Simplicity\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:322:\"<p>TYPO3 offers an easy implementation of content management. The user will just drag and drop the menu, content, and pages in the dashboard. WordPress shows the simplicity in its own name. It is user-friendly and each blogger loves it. You dont need to master any technological tool to add content in your website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',418,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(498,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,419,1556603587,1544303636,7,0,0,4352,'textpic','Ndrfaqe Responsive Web','','','<p>TYPO3 ofron mundsin e krijimit t ndrfaqes Responsive Web, duke prdor t ashtu-quajturat TYPO3 Template, pjes e funksionalitetit baz t TYPO3. Funksionalitete shtes mund t modifikohen duke prdor TYPO3 Extensions. Ky CMS ofron mundsi pafund pr ndrtimin e nj faqe interneti plotsisht t personalizuar. WordPress ndrton funksionalitetin e faqes web duke prdorur WordPress Extensions. Ndrkoh, dizajni i faqes n WordPress stilohet nga WordPress Theme e przgjedhur.</p>\r\n<p>Nuk ekziston nj pavarsi e plot midis Extensions dhe Theme n WordPress. Kjo do t thot q funksionalitete t caktuara jan n varsi t stilit t ndrfaqes.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',419,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Responsive Layout\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:595:\"<p>TYPO3 builds a responsive layout upon TYPO3 templates, which are core independent. Extra functionality could be added by using the TYPO3 extension. This CMS offers unlimited possibilities for building a fully optional website. WordPress builds the functionality by using WordPress Extensions.<br /> <br /> Meanwhile, the design of the website in WordPress is the style of a WordPress theme. But there does not exist a full independence between the extensions used by the developer and the WordPress Theme chosen by the designer. Certain features are dependent on and related to the theme.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',419,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(499,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,420,1556603608,1544303636,7,0,0,4608,'textpic','Qllimi i faqes Web','','','<p>TYPO3 sht shum i prshtatshm pr faqet e internetit t mdha, sisteme web pr kompani apo biznese. Ndrkoh, WordPress sht sistem pr cdo faqe t thjesht, q sht n fillimet e saj. WordPress prdoret shum n bloget personale, faqet e internetit t thjeshta, apo faqet e internetit pr biznese t vogla.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',420,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:26:\"The purpose of the website\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:261:\"<p>TYPO3 is very suitable for large websites used for companies or businesses. Meanwhile, WordPress is the CMS used in the very beginning of any website, for different purposes. WordPress is very used in personal blogs, small websites, or business websites.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',420,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(500,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,421,1556603618,1544303636,7,0,0,4864,'textpic','Siguria','','','<p>TYPO3 ofron nj sr funksionesh t integruara pr sigurin e t dhnave n Web. WordPress ofron siguri optimale kur sistemi azhornohet rregullisht.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',421,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:8:\"Security\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:145:\"<p>TYPO3 offers a set of built-in features for security. WordPress provides its optimal security when the system is updated on regular basis.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',421,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(501,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,422,1556603627,1544303636,7,0,0,5120,'textpic','Struktura','','','<p>TYPO3 i organizon faqet n nj struktur hierarkike, t ngjashme me sistemin e dosjeve dhe skedarve. WordPress i liston t gjitha faqet njra nn tjetrn.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',422,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:16:\"Layout structure\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:140:\"<p>TYPO3 organizes the pages in a tree-structure, similar to the folders in a filesystem. WordPress lists all pages one under the other.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',422,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(502,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,423,1564489484,1544303636,7,0,0,5376,'textpic','Cili sht m i miri, TYPO3 apo WordPress?','','','<p>Pr shum arsye, nuk ka nj konkurrenc t drejtprdrejt mes TYPO3 dhe WordPress. Ato ndryshojn n natyrn dhe qllimin e faqes Web, dhe t dy kto sisteme udhheqin fushat prkatse.</p>\r\n<p>Ju sugjerojm t zgjidhni WordPress nse:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Faqja juaj e internetit sht relativisht e thjesht, me disa karakteristika baz.</li> 	<li>Ju keni nj buxhet t vogl ose t mesm dhe preferoni t menaxhoni vet faqen e internetit.</li> 	<li>Faqja juaj e internetit nuk ka pse t jet n gjuh t ndryshme.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>TYPO3 sht CMS i duhur nse:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Faqja juaj e internetit sht e organizuar n nj struktur komplekse me faqe dhe nn-faqe.</li> 	<li>Faqja juaj e internetit do t jet promovimi i biznesit tuaj, n nj audienc ndrkombtare, dhe n shum gjuh.</li> 	<li>Faqja do prmbaj t dhna t integruara nga burime t tjera.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Ju keni nj buxhet t mesm pr t shpenzuar pr faqen tuaj, n fazn e projektimit, ndrtimit dhe mirmbajtjes.<br /> W3DEVELOPMENT sht nj grup ekspertsh web, t profilizuar n fushn e aplikacioneve web pr biznese.</p>\r\n<p>Ju garantojm se do jeni n rrugn e duhur pr t pasur sukses n biznesin tuaj.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',423,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"the best CMS\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1104:\"<p>Which one is the best, TYPO3 or WordPress?</p>\r\n<p>For many reasons, there is no direct competition between TYPO3 and WordPress. They differ in the types of the websites they suite, and both of them lead the respective fields.<br /> <br /> You better choose WordPress if :</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Your website is relatively simple, with some basic features.</li> 	<li>You have a small or a medium budget, and you prefer to manage yourself the website.</li> 	<li>Your website does not need to be in multiple languages.</li> </ul>\r\n<p><br /> TYPO3 is the right CMS if:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Your website is organized in a complex structure of pages and sub-pages.</li> 	<li>Your website will be the promotion of your business in many languages.</li> 	<li>There should be data integrated from other sources.</li> 	<li>You have a medium to large budget to spend on your website for assistance with the design, build and maintenance.</li> </ul>\r\n<p><br /> <br /> W3DEVELOPMENT do have expertise web developers with business excellence, so we can guarantee you will be guided to right track to succeed in your business.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:300;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:17;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:1;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',423,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(503,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,427,1564488864,1544307259,7,0,0,2816,'textpic','5 modelet m t njohura t dizajnit Responsive Web','','','<p>Gjithnj e m shum prdorues krkojn n web duke prdorur pajisje t llojeve t ndryshme. Ato ndryshojn n madhsi, duke nisur nga ekrani n laptop madhesin e ekranit t Smartphone. Projektimi i faqes Web bhet i vshtir, sepse duhen pas parasysh t gjitha kto lloje t ndryshme ekranesh.</p>\r\n<p>Faqet Responsive Web jan t ndrtuara n mnyr t till q dizajni t prshtatet me madhsin e ekranit. Por, ndrtimi i nj faqeje Responsive Web nuk sht aspak i leht, sepse do dit rritet numri i paisjeve t reja Smartphone. Modelet e dizajnit Responsive Web jan bashksi rregullash q duhen ndjekur gjat procesit t zhvillimit t faqes Web. Ato prfshijn disa komponente t prsritur q ndrtojn strukturn e ndrfaqes Web.</p>\r\n<p>Projektimi i ndrfaqes Web prfshin prcaktimin e disa parametrave teknik t till si gjersia, lartsia, madhsia e shkrimit dhe e imazheve. Ekspert t grafiks sugjerojn kto pes modele t dizajnit Web, si nj zgjidhje e mir pr projektimin e ndrfaqes:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Mostly Fluid,</li> 	<li>Column Drop,</li> 	<li>Layout Shifter,</li> 	<li>Tiny Tweaks,</li> 	<li>Off Canvas.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Le t prshkruajm m n detaje secilin prej ktyre modeleve.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',427,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:44:\"5 Examples of Responsive Web Design Patterns\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1312:\"<p>5 Examples of Responsive Web Design Patterns<br /> Nowadays, more and more users browse the web using different devices, in different screens. They vary in size, from desktop screen to tablet and Smartphone screen. The web development becomes difficult, assuming all these different options in size. By following some web design patterns, the workflow is kept more manageable. Building a responsive website isnt easy at all while developing for multiple devices.<br /> <br /> Responsive web design patterns are considered as rules to follow or kind of inspiration during the web development process. A responsive web design makes the site adjusts the layout to different sizes of the screen. If we focus on the modules and components of the layout, you will follow some patterns. They are some repeated components that build the design system. Web design patterns technically implement measures such as width, height, font size, and resolution.<br /> <br /> Professional designers suggest these five web design patterns as a good solution for web design project. These web design patterns are:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Mostly Fluid,</li> 	<li>Column Drop,</li> 	<li>Layout Shifter,</li> 	<li>Tiny Tweaks,</li> 	<li>Off Canvas.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Each of these web design patterns is explained in details, as follows.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',427,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(504,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,428,1569922845,1544307259,7,0,0,3072,'textpic','Modeli Mostly Fluid','','','<p>Modeli Mostly Fluid sht gjrsisht i prdorur, pr faktin se sht i thjesht pr t\'u implementuar. Ai prmban kolona t ndryshme me margjina m t mdha pr ndrfaqe m t madhe. Ky model web design sugjerohet pr revista apo pr faqe Web t lajmeve t mods.</p>\r\n<p>Modeli Mostly Fluid prfshin funksionalitetet e nj menuje zbritse, lidhje me rrjetet sociale etj. N kt model t dizajnimit Web, faqja ndryshon kufijt sipas madhsis s ekranit t pajisjes. N smartphone, ndrfaqja rregullon gjersit e kolonave.</p>\r\n<p>Avantazhi i ksaj strukture sht se faqosja ndryshon vetm kur ngushtohet gjersia e ekranit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,1,1,NULL,'',0,'',428,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:31:\"Mostly Fluid Web Design Pattern\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:641:\"<p>The very popular web design pattern is mostly fluid. One of the reasons for its popularity is the fact it is simple to implement.It contains different columns with larger margins on the larger interface. This web design pattern is suggested for magazines or fashion news websites. It can include functionalities of a drop-down menu, social accounts links, etc. In this web design pattern, the layout changes the margins according to the screen size of the device. On Smartphone, the layout reflows and arranges the columns vertically. The advantage of this structure is that the layout changes only when a smaller screen width occurs.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',428,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(505,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,429,1569922867,1544307259,7,0,0,3328,'textpic','Moduli Drop Column','','','<p>Ky model prmban kolona t ndryshme, por ndrsa ekrani ngushtohet, numri i kolonave zvoglohet. Ky model i dizenjimit web tenton t mbush t gjitha hapsirat e mundshme.</p>\r\n<p>Drop Column sht i prkryer pr faqet Responsive Web ku prdoruesi do t lexoj nga e gjith gjersia e ekranit. Madhsit e segmenteve kan tendencn t mos ndryshojn. Ndfaqja sht e ndrtuar n segmente t ndryshme pr rezolucione t ndryshme t ekranit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',429,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Column Drop Web Design Pattern\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:413:\"<p>This pattern contains different columns but while the screen narrows, the columns are reduced. This web design pattern tends to fill the available viewpoint. It is perfect for responsive websites that users will see from the wide range of screen sizes.The sizes of segments tent to stay the same. The layout is built in different breakpoint for different screen resolutions, and it differs for each design.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',429,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(506,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,430,1569922913,1544307259,7,0,0,3584,'textpic','Modeli Layout Shifter','','','<p>Modeli Layout Shifter sht shum kompleks, sepse ndryshon strukturn pr seciln gjersi ekrani. Kjo gj krijon vshtirsi gjat fazs s implementimit. Pr kt arsye, ky model nuk prdoret gjrsisht.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',430,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:33:\"Layout Shifter Web Design Pattern\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:278:\"<p>The layout shifter pattern does the most to adapt to the different displays sizes. The pattern is complex because it changes for each breakpoint for different widths. This requires more effort during the implementation phase, and this makes the patterns not much popular.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',430,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(507,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,431,1569927684,1544307259,7,0,0,3840,'textpic','Modeli Tiny Tweaks','','','<p>Ky model bn prshtatjen duke ndryshuar madhsin e shkronjave ose madhsin e imazheve. Faqet Web q ndjekin kt model ndryshojn madhsin e shkronjave sipas gjersis s ekranit ku prdoruesi shfleton Web. Nse prdoruesi po e lexon nga nj ekran desktop, ai do t shoh faqen me shkrim dhe me imazhe m t mdha.</p>\r\n<p>Ky model i dizajnit t Web prdoret kryesisht n paraqitjen me nj kolon t vetme, t cilat mund t prmbajn artikuj t gjat.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',431,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Tiny tweaks Web Design Pattern\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:411:\"<p>This pattern makes the adjustments by changing the font sizes, or resizing the images or moving the content. Websites that follow this pattern will change font size according to the width of the Users that browse the website from a desktop screen will see the site with bigger fonts and bigger images. This web design pattern is mostly applied in single column layouts, which might contain long articles.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',431,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(508,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,435,1564488269,1544307653,7,0,0,3328,'textpic','Ja pse biznesi juaj duhet t ket nj faqe interneti.','','','<p>Cdo dit e m tepr rritet numri i njerzve q prdorin internetin. Pr cdo informacion q iu nevojitet, ata do e krkojn n internet. Me zhvillimin e teknologjis dhe internetit, ju duhet t\'i shikoni t gjith si klient potencial.</p>\r\n<p>T rinjt sot krkojn n internet edhe pr gjrat q blejn ose shrbimet q u nevojiten. Prandaj sht krejt e natyrshme q konsumatort t mendojn se do biznes sht i pranishm n ueb, n faqen e vet t internetit.</p>\r\n<p>T qenit aktiv n mediat sociale sht njra an. Gjithashtu, duhet nj faqe interneti ku ndjeksit mund t blejn produktin tuaj ose mund t krkojn m shum detaje pr shrbimet tuaja.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',435,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Advantages of having a website\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:605:\"<p>The number of people that are using the internet is increasing each day. If they need information, they will search it on the Internet.<br /> In this technologic era, you should see all of them as potential customers, as they will search on the web even for the things they buy or services they need.<br /> Having a website is so normal that customers suppose every business is present on the web on its own website.<br /> <br /> Being active in the social media is one side, but you also need a website where the followers can purchase your product or can search for more details of your services.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',435,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(509,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,436,1566217367,1544307653,7,0,0,3840,'textpic','Nj faqe interneti rrit ndrgjegjsimin pr produktet dhe shrbimet tuaja.','','','<p>Faqja e internetit e biznesit tuaj sht mnyra m e leht q klientt t ken qasje n produktet ose shrbimet q ju ofroni. Kto produkte sht mir t\'i vendosni n faqen kryesore, n mnyr q blersit ti shohin sa m shpejt q t jet e mundur.</p>\r\n<p>Faqja e internetit duhet t paraqes listn e plot t produkteve q ofron biznesi juaj. Kjo list trheq klientin, i cili fillon krkimin e nj produkti, madje blen edhe nj t dyt. Ndoshta ai nuk e dinte se biznesi juaj e shet kt produkt, dhe prandaj duhet afishimi i nj liste t plot t artikujve n faqen e internetit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',436,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:62:\"A website increases awareness about your products and services\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:486:\"<p>The website of your business is the easiest way the customers access the products or services you offer. You better put them on the homepage, so they access it as soon as possible. The website should better present the full list of the products that your business. This list attracts the customer which starts searching a product and buys a second one. Maybe he didnt know your business sells it too, and thats the importance of showing a full list of items on the website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',436,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(510,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,437,1564488394,1544307653,7,0,0,4096,'textpic','Nj faqe interneti punon pavarsisht orarit tuaj.','','','<p>Faqja Ueb e biznesit tuaj do t jet online 24 or n dit, 365 dit n vit, duke iu dhn informacion miliona njerzve do dit. Gjithashtu, ajo do bj t mundur q klientt tuaj t\'ju kontaktojn jasht orarit tuaj t puns, nprmjet porosive ose email.</p>\r\n<p>Faqja juaj e internetit, e projektuar nga W3DEVELOPMENT, punon pr ju, ndrsa jeni n kohn tuaj t lir ose n gjum.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',437,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:43:\"A website increases your hours of operation\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:341:\"<p>Not only will your website be there 24 hours a day, 365 days a year with the possibility of reaching millions of people every day, but it will make it possible for your customers to contact you outside of your normal business hours. Your website, designed by W3DEVELOPMENT, is still working for you while you are at leisure or asleep.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',437,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(511,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,438,1566217414,1544307653,7,0,0,4352,'textpic','Nj faqe interneti redukton shpenzimet e biznesit tuaj.','','','<p><em>Nj faqe interneti zvoglon koston e publikimit:</em> sht media me koston m t ult, ku mund t reklamoni biznesin tuaj dhe produktet e tij. N kt mnyr, ju do t reduktoni letrat dhe materialet e printuara. Hapsira Ueb nuk sht nj promocion lokal, por nj reklam ndrkombtare.</p>\r\n<p><em>Nj faqe interneti zvoglon koston e marketingut:</em> Ju shpenzoni shum or n zgjedhjen e fjals s duhur pr ta shkruar n nj hapsir t vogl n nj reklam gazete, ose n 30 sekonda n TV. Nj faqe interneti ofron nj hapsir t pakufizuar pr biznesin tuaj. Ju mund t vendosni sa m shum informacion, duke shtuar t gjitha mjetet multimediale dhe duke e br at m trheqse se do media tjetr.</p>\r\n<p><em>Nj faqe interneti zvoglon shpenzimet e komunikimit:</em> ajo prmban t gjith informacionin q blersit duan t din, duke prfshir imazhet e produkteve, hartn e dyqaneve tuaja, stafin q ofron shrbimet, numrin e telefonit dhe e-mail ku mund t\'ju shkruajn, si dhe do informacion q ju dshironi t ndani me klientt tuaj. Partnert e biznesit, stafi juaj, furnitort, si dhe t gjith t interesuarit pr produktet dhe shrbimet tuaja, do t marrin informacionin e plot nga faqja juaj n internet.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',438,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:23:\"A website reduces costs\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1214:\"<p>A good website reduces publishing cost: It is the most affordable media where you can advertise your business and its products. You will reduce papers and print materials, and it is never locally, but a worldwide advertisement. You can keep your website more current, more affordable and easier to manage than any other media.</p>\r\n<p>A good website reduces marketing cost: You spend plenty hours in choosing the right word to say in a small space of a newspaper ad, or in a half minute in TV. A website offers an unlimited space for your business, you can put as many information as you need, by adding all type of multimedia content and making it more attractive than any other media.</p>\r\n<p>A good website reduces communication costs: The potential customers will get in the website all the information they need about your business, the images of the products, the map of the stores, the members of the team that offer the services, the phone number and e-mail where they can reach you, and any information you wish to communicate to the customers, but not only. Business partners, your team, suppliers, and everyone interested in your products and services will get this information from your website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_