e services of your business.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',440,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(514,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,441,1566217871,1544307653,7,0,0,5120,'textpic','Nj faqe interneti krijon mundsi pr komunikim me stafin, bashkpuntort, agjentt dhe furnitort.','','','<p>Ju mund t organizoni prmbajtjen e faqes n nivele t ndryshme. Prdorues t ndryshm mund t lexojn informacione q kan lidhje me to.</p>\r\n<p>Pr shembull, ju mund t postoni informacion pr ekipin tuaj n nj hapsir Ueb t mbyllur, t ciln ata arrijn vetm me fjalkalimin e duhur. Kto informacione t brendshme mund jen n lidhje me ndryshimet n staf, orare apo detyra pr stafin, ngjarje ose njoftime t ndryshme, etj. Ndrkoh, prdoruesit t internetit kan qasje vetm n detajet e produktit, format e kontaktit dhe postimet publike q lidhen me kompanin tuaj.</p>\r\n<p>Ju mund t vendosni shum ose pak informacion, sa t doni n faqen tuaj.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',441,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:90:\"A website opens new channels of communication with staff, affiliates, agents and suppliers\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:500:\"<p>You can organize the content of the website in different levels, so different users can read vary information related to them. You can post information for your team in a closed location, so they reach it only by a password. It might include changes in the team, task schedule, events or notifications. Meanwhile, the wide web users access the product details, contact forms and public posts related to your company. You can put as much or as little information as you want on your site.&nbsp;</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',441,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(515,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,442,1564436156,1544307653,7,0,1,5376,'textpic','Na kontaktoni','','','<p>Cfare po prisni? Na kontaktoni sot, dhe le t flasim pr faqen tuaj!</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',1,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',442,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Contact us\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:87:\"<p>What are you waiting for? Contact us today, and lets talk about your website!</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9: