</field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',352,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:16:\"theme_blogteaser\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125902;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1065:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Shopify vs Magento</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Shopify and Magento are two of the most popular e-commerce platforms on the market. They differ a lot from each other. In this article, these differences are highlighted, so you can decide which is the right e-commerce platform for your online store.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=19</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">31</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"alt\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\"></value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',352,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(518,13,0,0,0,0,0,1581950621,0,518,1580816373,1580816373,13,0,0,3072,'textpic','A website moves you a step forward from your competitors','','','<p>If your customers cant find your business online, they will find your competitors. If you arent present on the web, you are losing many opportunities.&nbsp;It is important that website of your store to be well designed, easy to navigate, and full of information and product details of your business or your customers wont buy anything. You should see it as an online representation of your shop and business. If the website is ugly or incomplete, it will send the clients to another company. It often happens that a customer chooses to buy a product online just because it is described in details and the website looks good and is stylish. So, you must have a professional-looking site if you want to be taken seriously. Studies show that once a consumer has an idea of what they need or want, they start researching, and 72% of them go online to find the service they need, according to this&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.pardot.com/buyer-journey/\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">report</a></p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(519,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,518,1564488342,1544308611,7,0,0,3584,'textpic','Me nj faqe interneti, ju jeni nj hap prpara konkurrentve tuaj.','','','<p>Nse blersit nuk mund ta gjejn biznesin tuaj online, ata do t gjejn konkurrentt tuaj. Nse nuk jeni t pranishm n internet, ju humbni shum mundsi.</p>\r\n<p>sht e rndsishme q faqja e internetit t jet e projektuar mir, e leht pr t lundruar, si dhe me informacion t plot dhe t detajuar n lidhje produktet e biznesit tuaj. Ju duhet ta shihni faqen Ueb si nj prezantim online t dyqanit dhe biznesit tuaj.</p>\r\n<p>Nse faqja e internetit sht e shmtuar ose jo e plot, ajo do t\'i largoj klientt drejt nj kompanie tjetr. Shpesh ndodh q nj klient zgjedh pr t bler nj produkt online vetm se produkti prshkruhet n detaje dhe faqja e internetit duket kndshm. Imazhi i biznesit tuaj prfaqsohet nga cilsia e faqes s internetit.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',518,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:56:\"A website moves you a step forward from your competitors\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:670:\"<p>If your customers cant find your business online, they will find your competitors. If you arent present on the web, you are losing many opportunities. It is important that website is well designed and easy to navigate, and full of information and product details of your business. You should see it as an online representation of your shop and business. If the website is ugly or incomplete, it will send the clients to another company. It often happens that a customer chooses to buy a product online just because it is described in details and the website looks good and is stylish. The image of your business is represented by the quality of its website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',518,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(520,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,443,1564487063,1544308966,7,0,0,3328,'textpic','Trendet Mobile web','','','<p>Ekspertt e dizajn n web prballen me sfidat teknike por edhe vazhdojn t krijojn faqe t thjeshta pr prdoruesin, elegante dhe t prshtatshme me do pajisje mobile.N vitin 2017 ka avancuar shum prdorimi i faqeve t internetit n paisjet mobile.</p>\r\n<p>Aktualisht, lundrimi n aplikacione web mobile numron m shum prdorues sesa lundrimi n web nga kompjuter apo laptop. Kjo sht nj nga arsyet pse viti 2018 do t sjell funksionalitete dhe mnyra t reja pr paisjet mobile.</p>\r\n<p>N vazhdim prmenden disa tendenca t dizajnit web pr vitin 2018.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',443,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Mobile web trends\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:512:\"<p>Web designers deal with the technical challenges that are large in number, and still continue to create user-friendly sites, stylish and flexible with every device and just beautiful all at once. 2017 made more advancement in mobile browsing, who now counts more users than desktop browsing. This is a reason why 2018 is going to have fully mobile functionalities in new ways. Meanwhile, desktops will evolve in such way to stay relevant.</p>\r\n<p>So, lets take a look at some web design trends in 2018.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',443,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(521,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,444,1566224128,1544308966,7,0,0,3584,'textpic','Drit-hijet','','','<p>Drit-hijet jan nj teknik e hershme grafike, por sapo sht cilsuar si trend i dizajnit web pr vitin 2018. Kjo teknik thekson rndsin e dizejnimit web n nj hapsir tre-dimensionale. N listn e tendencave t dizajnit web pr vitin 2018, do t vini re animacione, ilustrime dhe shkrime t mdha. T gjitha kto efekte grafike ndryshojn shum nga efektet e zvogluara, nj tendenc kjo e viteve t fundit.</p>\r\n<p>Koncepti i thellsis n grafik i jep faqes s internetit nj ndjenj unike dhe nj prshtypje t paharrueshme. Ai krijon ndjenjn e nj imazhi t vrtet, ndonjse sht abstrakt. Ky efekt mund t aplikohet n sfondin e faqes web, n logon ose ndonj imazh grafik t ndrfaqes. Efekti i thellsis n nj faqe web 2D shpesh bhet nj mnyr e mir pr t theksuar nj komponent n dizajn. E gjith ndrfaqja grafike merr m shum vmendje kur prdoret nj perspektiv e thellsis.</p>\r\n<p>N kt shembull, duke shtuar drit-hije, krijohet efekti i thellsis dhe nj perspektiv mbreslnse nga lart-posht.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',444,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:22:\"Drop shadows and depth\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:998:\"<p>Drop shadows are an old graphical technique, but its the newly implemented as web design trend in 2018, and it highlights the importance of designing the web in a three-dimensional space. In the list of web design trends 2018, you will notice broken grids, animations, illustrations and big fonts. All these graphical effects differ a lot from the minimalism which was a trend during past years.</p>\r\n<p>The concept of the depth in the graphic gives to the website the unique feeling and a memorable impression. It creates the sense of a real image, even if it is an abstract one. This effect is a web design trend in 2018 applied in web background, logo or any other graphical representation. The effect of depth in a flat page can be also a powerful tool to emphasize an element in the design. The whole design will get more attention when used this depth perspective.</p>\r\n<p>In this example, playing with translucency adds depth effect, and creates an impressive top-down perspective.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',444,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(522,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,445,1566224189,1544308966,7,0,0,3840,'textpic','Sfonde me ngjyra t forta','','','<p>Tendencat e dizajnit t web pr vitin 2018 jan absolutisht plot me ngjyra ndezura dhe plot drit. N vitet e fundit, markat e njohura prdorn m shum \"ngjyra t sigurta\", q do t thot nuk eksperimentuan shum me ngjyra t forta. Pr kt vit, ekspertt e dizajn n web po marrin guximin n prdorimin e ngjyrave, duke prfshir nuanca m t ndricuara. Prve ngjyrave, titujt n web nuk jan m vetm horizontale, por jan t ridimensionuar me tituj n knde t ndryshme.</p>\r\n<p>Ngjyra t gjalla sugjerohen sidomos pr markat e reja sepse ato trheqin menjher vmendjen e prdoruesve. Ky trend mund t jet i duhuri pr do mark q dshiron t largohet nga dizajni i tyre tradicional. Efekti i ngjyrave t ndezura sht trheqja e vmendjes, sidomos kur aplikohet n butona, links apo njoftime.</p>\r\n<p>N kt shembull, sht zgjedhur nj ngjyr e kuqe e mrekullueshme dhe e przier dhe nuancat e blu-marins. Vendi duket shum profesional dhe aspak i mrzitshm apo i zymt.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',445,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:35:\"Vibrant and saturated color schemes\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:932:\"<p>Web design trends 2018 are absolutely full of super excess colors online. In the past years, brands and designers used more the web-safe colors. In this year, web designers are becoming more courageous in their approach to colorincluding super-saturation and vibrant shades. Apart the colors, web headers are no longer just horizontal but resized with slashes and hard angles.</p>\r\n<p>Vibrant colors as web design trends in 2018 are suggested to the new brands because they attract immediately the attention of the users. This trend can be also perfect for every brand who wants to distant their design from the traditional one.</p>\r\n<p>The effect of saturated colors is the attraction of the attention, especially when used in buttons, links, alerts, and notifications. In this example, is chosen a striking red color and mixed with blues and navy tones. The site looks very professional, not dull or boring at all.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',445,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(523,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,446,1566224251,1544308966,7,0,0,4096,'textpic','Sfonde me grimca','','','<p>Nj nga tendencat e dizajnit web pr vitin 2018 sht sfondi q prmban grimca, forma t thjeshta gjeometrike, imazhe komplekse apo animacione. Efektet mund t jen rrath, shum trekndsha t thjesht ose forma t tjera gjeometrike.</p>\r\n<p>Dizajni prfshin nj sken dinamike, ku kto grimca lvizin rreth dikaje, dridhen, krcejn ose reagojn ndaj veprimeve t prdoruesit. Roli kryesor i ktij sfondi sht q t\'i jap ndrfaqes nj lvizje dhe nj efekt gjeometrik.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',446,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"Particle backgrounds\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:483:\"<p>One of the web design trends 2018 is the backgrounds containing simple dots, simple geometric shapes, complex images and particles animations. The effects might be vibrant balls, few circles, and a lot of plain triangles or other geometric shapes. The design includes a dynamic scene, when these particles move around something, vibrate, dance, or react to the users actions.</p>\r\n<p>The main role of all this scenery is to give the interface a motion and a geometric vibe.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',446,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(524,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,447,1566224306,1544308966,7,0,0,4352,'textpic','N prioritet grafika pr aplikacionet mobile','','','<p>Ndrsa numri i prdoruesve t paisjeve mobile sht n rritje, prdorimi i internetit n celular ka tejkaluar at n desktop. Grupi ekspert i grafiks krijon nj dizajn t posatshm pr paisjet mobile, i cili prfshin nj menu minimale pr ekranin e vogl.</p>\r\n<p>Pr kt vit vihet re tendenca e ndrtimit fillimisht t dizajnit t faqes web pr paisjet mobile, dhe m pas dizenjimi i grafiks t faqes web pr aplikacionet desktop. Vihet re tendenca q gjithnj e m shum faqe web do t strukturojn prmbajtjen e tyre pr ekranet e vegjl mobile, duke ln si zgjedhje dytsore versionin e web-it pr desktopit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',447,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"Mobile first\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:499:\"<p>As the number of Smartphones users is increasing, the mobile browsing has surpassed the desktop browsing. Designers have already a design for the Smartphone, which includes a minimal menu for the small screen. As one of most used web design tends 2018, the mobile-first design is the process of designing for mobile first, then working up to the bigger ones.</p>\r\n<p>More and more sites will deliver their content to the smaller screens first, leaving secondary choice the desktop version.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',447,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(525,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,448,1566224352,1544308966,7,0,0,4608,'textpic','Ilustrime t personalizuara','','','<p>Ilustrimet jan t fantastike, prfundimisht. Artist t grafiks arrijn t bjn ilustrime t prshtatura pr markn q ata prfaqsojn. Ky trend i grafiks web sht shum i prshtatshm pr markat q jan argtuese dhe energjike, por jo vetm.</p>\r\n<p>Markat q perceptohen si tradicionale dhe serioze mund t jen gjithashtu m trheqse duke prdorur kt tendence grafike. Cilido qoft identiteti i marks tuaj, ekziston gjithmon nj ilustrim grafik q e prfaqson m s miri at.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',448,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"Custom illustrations\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:414:\"<p>Illustrations are great, definitively. Professional artists can make illustrations tailored to the brand which they represent. This web design trend 2018 is awesome for brands which are fun and energetic, but not only them. Brands that are perceived as traditional and serious can be more attractive by using this trend.</p>\r\n<p>Whatever your brand identity is, theres always an illustration to match it.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',448,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(526,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,449,1566224412,1544308966,7,0,0,4864,'textpic','E madhe ose hi','','','<p>Nj nga tendencat q po dominojn qart stilet e web pr vitin 2018 sht tipografia e guximshme. Shkrimet e mdhenj po prdoren m s shumti n faqet e internetit. Ato shfrytzojn m mir hapsirn e bardh dhe trheqin vmendjen. Titujt e mdhenj jan zgjedhur pr t shfaq m n pah mesazhin e marks.</p>\r\n<p>Roli i titujve n nj faqe interneti sht pr t dhn informacion q do t trheq vizitorin e faqes. N tendencat aktuale t dizajnit t faqeve t internetit jan titujt shkrime kreative dhe t guximshme.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',449,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:14:\"Big or Nothing\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:398:\"<p>One of most notable web design trends 2018 is the bold typography. One reason is that the bigger fonts utilize better the white space, and draws attention. Big fonts are chosen to highlight the message of the brand. The role of the headers in a website is to order the information that will attract the visitor.</p>\r\n<p>In web design trends 2018, headers are full of creative bold typefaces.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',449,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(527,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,450,1566224466,1544308966,7,0,0,5120,'textpic','Asimetria dhe skemat e thyera','','','<p>Nj tendenc eksperimentale e dizajnit t web sht projektimi asimetrik dhe rrjetzimet e thyera. Ato jan unike dhe t veanta. Shumica e markave ende prdorin strukturat tradicionale t bazuara n paraqitjen e rrjetit t rregullt. Markat q duan t jen unike tentojn t provojn efekte t ndryshme dhe do dalin jasht skemave.</p>\r\n<p>Asimetria mund t jet e bukur dhe harmonike. Ai jep nj ndikim t veant tek vizitort. Nj shembull i ktij efekti n dizajn sht faqja e internetit ku pamja asimetrike nuk sht e balancuar n t dy ant e ekranit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',450,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:33:\"Asymmetry and broken grid layouts\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:533:\"<p>The most experimental web design trend 2018 is the asymmetric design and broken grids. They are unique and distinctive. Most brands still use the traditional structures based on the grid layout, but the brands who want to be unique will try different layouts and will design out the box. Asymmetry can be both beautiful and harmonious. It gives a special impact to the visitors.</p>\r\n<p>One example of this web design trend 2018 is the website where the asymmetric layout is not perfectly balanced on the left and right sides.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',450,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(528,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,451,1566224523,1544308966,7,0,0,5376,'textpic','Animacionet e integruara','','','<p>Tendencat e dizajnit t web pr vitin 2018 shkojn prtej imazheve statike. Ato synojn drejt animacioneve dhe efekteve multimediale. Prve animacioneve n sfond t faqes, t cilat u prmenden m lart si animacione t grimcave, tendenca prfshin edhe animacione t vogla q shoqrojn vizitorin prgjat leximit t faqes web.</p>\r\n<p>Nj animacion i vogl shkurton kohn e pritjes ndrsa faqja po ngarkohet. Gjithashtu, nj animacion i vogl nxit lexuesin t lviz posht ose t fokusohet n nj pjes interesante t faqes web. Animacione t tilla jan mjete t fuqishme q vendosin vizitorin n rol kryesor gjat lundrimit n web. Kto animacione t vogla krijojn ndrveprime dinamike me vizitorin dhe e nxitin at q t qndroj sa m gjat n faqen web.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',451,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:21:\"Integrated animations\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:672:\"<p>Web design trends 2018 go further than static images, towards animations and multimedia effects. Besides the animations in the background, which are mentioned above as the particle animations, this trend includes small animations which accompany the visitor along the experience on the website. A small animation makes shorter the waiting time while the page is loading. Also, a small animation encourages to scroll down or to focus an interesting part of the web page. Such animations are powerful tools which include the visitor as an actor in whole website story. They create dynamic interactions with the visitor and encourage him to stay longer on the website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',451,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(529,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,452,1566224571,1544308966,7,0,0,5632,'textpic','Shkallt dinamike','','','<p>Nj nga rikthimet m t mdha si tendenc e dizajnit web jan shkallt. Kt her, ata kthehen fuqishm si efekt i preferuar, ku efekti gradient i bn ato misterioze dhe intriguese. N nj rast kur asnj imazh nuk prshtatet me sfondin e faqes web, nj gradient ngjyrash sht zgjidhje interesante.</p>\r\n<p>Meq web-i tashm sht i mbushur me efekte dinamike, gradientt dinamik e prmbyllin kt prirje eksperimentale t dizajnit n web. Nj faqe e internetit mund t ket nj gradient kryesor t fiksuar n sfond i cili ju ndjek kudo ku jo shkoni n faqe.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',452,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Dynamic gradients\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:559:\"<p>One of the biggest comebacks as web design trends 2018 are of course the gradients. This time, they return loudly and colorful. The most popular effect is the gradient filter over photos, making them mysterious and intriguing. In a case when not any image fit with the background, the color gradient is an interesting solution. Since the modern web is packed with dynamic effects, dynamic gradients complete this experimental web design trend.</p>\r\n<p>This website has one main gradient fixed in the background and it follows you along while scrolling.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',452,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(530,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,453,1552437085,1544308966,7,0,0,5888,'textpic','Prmbledhje','','','<p>Tendencat e dizajnit web pr vitin 2018 duket se jan me ngjyra dhe plot energji, dika ndrmjet ngjyrave t ndezura, animacioneve t integruara dhe gradientve dinamik. Nuk dihet se deri ku do t shtyhet kufijt tradicionale t grafiks web.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',453,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Summary\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:255:\"<p>Web design trends in 2018 seems to be both colorful and funny, something between bright colors, integrated animations and dynamic gradients. We cant wait to see what designers are going to come up with and how theyre going to push the limits.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',453,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(531,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,396,1564493345,1544311745,7,0,0,1024,'textpic','Sistemi ECommerce in TYPO3','','','<p>TYPO3  una soluzione per la maggior parte dei siti Web, in particolare per le aziende e i grandi negozi. Quale  la soluzione di TYPO3 per l\'e-commerce? Quali sono i principali sistemi di negozi TYPO3? Ci sono diverse soluzioni su come creare il tuo negozio online nel sito web in TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Esistono tre tipi principali di TYPO3 Extensions per l\'e-commerce:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>TYPO3 Extensions Native</li> 	<li>Widget</li> 	<li>Integrazioni con un altro software.</li> </ul>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',396,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:18:\"TYPO3 Shop Systems\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:464:\"<p>Nowadays, TYPO3 is the solution for most websites, especially for businesses and large companies. But what does TYPO3 offer as a solution for the e-commerce? Which are main TYPO3 shop systems? In fact, there are several solutions how to create your online store within your TYPO3 website. There are three main types of e-commerce TYPO3 extensions:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Native extensions</li> 	<li>Widgets</li> 	<li>Integrations with a third party software.</li> </ul>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',396,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(532,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,397,1566825170,1544311745,7,0,0,1280,'textpic','Sistemi di negozio TYPO3 implementati come estensioni native','','','<p>Con un TYPO3 Extensions Native, tu puoi gestire il negozio online dall\'interno dell sistema TYPO3, attraverso le proprie funzioni principali. Altre funzionalit come consegna o pagamento possono essere aggiunte a queste estensioni.</p>\r\n<p>Vi presentiamo una lista con le estensioni di TYPO3 che puoi usarli per implementare il tuo negozio online TYPO3:</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',397,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:51:\"TYPO3 shop systems implemented as Native Extensions\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:289:\"<p>Native extensions run the online shop inside the TYPO3 platform, within its own core functions. Extra functionality like deliver or pay the item can be added to these extensions. Below, it is a list with TYPO3 Native Extensions. You may use them to implement your TYPO3 online shop:</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',397,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(533,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,398,1564493385,1544311745,7,0,0,1536,'textpic','tt_products','','','<p>Questa TYPO3 Extension  un vecchio sistema di negozio TYPO3 offerto come software open source, dal 2007. Se vuoi personalizzare i progetti TYPO3 aggiungendo questo Extensions, forse ti troverai difficolt come quale sara l\'implementazione di IVA per destinazioni diverse o come aggiungere i costi di spedizione per aree o pesi differenti.</p>\r\n<p>tt_products supporta queste funzionalit, ma ci vuole tempo e molto impegno per personalizzarle. tt_products ha un\'architettura vecchia, che usa il modello basato su Marker e le funzioni t3lib_div :: sono integrate con TYPO3 usando le estensioni wrapper.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su tt_products :<br /> Creato da Franz Holzinger<br /> Homepage https://www.ttproducts.de/<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/tt_products/<br /> Codice https://github.com/franzholz/tt_products</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',398,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:11:\"tt_products\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:809:\"<p>This extension is an old TYPO3 shop system offered as open software since 2007. If you try to customize TYPO3 projects adding this extension, you might encounter difficulties such as implementing different VAT for different destinations, or adding shipping cost for different regions or weight. tt_products supports these features, but it takes time and lot of effort to customize them.<br /> <br /> This extension has an outdated architecture. It uses the marker-based template and the t3lib_div:: functions are integrated with TYPO3 using the wrapper extensions.</p>\r\n<p>More details about tt_products : Maintainer Franz Holzinger<br /> Homepage https://www.ttproducts.de/<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/tt_products/<br /> Code https://github.com/franzholz/tt_products</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',398,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(534,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,399,1564493407,1544311745,7,0,0,1792,'textpic','Commerce','','','<p>Questo TYPO3 Extension  un software nativo di TYPO3 dal 2007, con un modello statico, che puoi integrarlo facilmente nel tuo sito web in TYPO3. Il codice si mantiene da Sebastian Fischer , e lavora sia per migliorare e aggiornare questa TYPO3 Extension. In futuro, Commerce sar implementato in modello Fluid.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Commerce:<br /> Si mantiene da Sebastian Fischer<br /> Codice https://github.com/CommerceTeam/commerce</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',399,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:8:\"Commerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:441:\"<p>This TYPO3 extension is a native TYPO3 shop system since 2007. It comes with a static template and you can integrate it easily into your website. Its maintainer Sebastian Fischer works both for re-factoring the extension to an up-to-date implementation and also in moving it to the fluid based template.<br /> <br /> More detailes about Commerce :<br /> Maintainer Sebastian Fischer<br /> Code https://github.com/CommerceTeam/commerce</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',399,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(535,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,400,1564493429,1544311745,7,0,0,2048,'textpic','Cart','','','<p>Questo TYPO3 Extension  adattato per un negozio online con un numero limitato di articoli. Questo sistema di negozio TYPO3  completamente funzionale, che include l\'elenco, la fatturazione, i pagamenti e i dettagli sulla spedizione dei prodotti. Lo sviluppatore lo configura manualmente.</p>\r\n<p>Cart usa il modello Fluid, che offre tutta la flessibilit del sistema TYPO3. Cart pu essere personalizzato per fornire le funzionalit di pagamento o altre funzioni di consegna.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Cart:<br /> Homepage https://cart.extco.de<br /> Si mantiene da Daniel Lorenz<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/cart/<br /> Codice https://github.com/extcode/cart</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',400,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:4:\"Cart\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:682:\"<p>This TYPO3 extension is adapted for an online shop with a limited number of items. This TYPO3 shop system offers a fully functional e-commerce platform including product listing, billing, payments and product shipping details. The developer configures it manually. It uses fluid templates, which makes use of the power and flexibility of the TYPO3 system. Cart extension can be customized to provide extra payment functionality or other delivery functions.<br /> <br /> More details about Cart<br /> Homepage https://cart.extco.de<br /> Maintainer : Daniel Lorenz<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/cart/<br /> Code https://github.com/extcode/cart</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',400,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(536,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,401,1564493471,1544311745,7,0,0,2304,'textpic','Aimeos','','','<p>Questo TYPO3 Extension  basato sull Arcavias, un progetto che contiene una intera libreria di software per diversi sistemi di negozi online. Uno di questi  il sistema di negozio in TYPO3. Aimeos  una versione migliorata del codice di questa libreria. Aimeos include pacchetti per altri framework di sistemi di negozio come Laravel. In effetti, Aimeos pu essere integrato nella maggior parte dei siti Web in PHP. La gestione di sessione dei messaggi di registrazione e altre funzionalit sono in codici in PHP.</p>\r\n<p>Aimeos include le funzionalit della infrastruttura TYPO3 per inviare e-mail, gestire le sessioni e generare gli URL. Il codice Aimeos per il framework TYPO3 non segue lo schema tipico dei nomi del database, come \"ext_tables.sql\" e il \"prefisso tx_\". Questo  uno dei problemi principali con Aimeos. Nel frattempo, il suo vantaggio  che puoi aggiungere molti prodotti nel tuo negozio online.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Aimeos:<br /> Homepage https://aimeos.org/<br /> Progetto aimeos<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/aimeos/<br /> Codice https://github.com/aimeos/aimeos-typo3</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',401,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:6:\"Aimeos\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1100:\"<p>This TYPO3 extension is based on Arcavias core which is a project that provides a library for different shop systems. One of them is TYPO3 shop system. Aimeos is an improved version of the code of this library. Aimeos includes packages for other shop systems frameworks such as Laravel. In fact, Aimeos can integrate into most PHP website. The logging messages session handler and other features are provided by the PHP code. When Aimeos is integrated with TYPO3, the TYPO3 infrastructure sends emails, handles the sessions and generates the URLs.<br /> <br /> The Aimeos code for the TYPO3 framework does not follow the typical database naming scheme, such as ext_tables.sql and the tx_ prefix. This is one of the main issues with Aimeos extension. Meanwhile, its advantage is that you can add in your store a wide range of products and many pricing structures.<br /> <br /> More details about Aimeos<br /> Homepage https://aimeos.org/<br /> Maintainer aimeos<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/aimeos/<br /> Code https://github.com/aimeos/aimeos-typo3</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',401,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(537,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,402,1564493496,1544311745,7,0,0,2560,'textpic','Multishop','','','<p>Multishop  un TYPO3 Extension che consente allo sviluppatore di modificare e gestire pi negozi online all\'interno della stessa struttura di pagine. Il catalogo si mantiene completamente nella parte front-end. Il catalogo pu essere facilmente modificato. Inoltre, tu pu facilmente aggiungere o rimuovere categorie di prodotti e voci del menu di navigazione. Tutto questo grazie alla sua semplice interfaccia. Il venditore non ha bisogno di conoscere lo sviluppo web o TYPO3 per aggiornare e per gestire il suo negozio in TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Multishop: https://extensions.typo3.org/extension/multishop/</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',402,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:9:\"Multishop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:611:\"<p>Multishop is a TYPO3 shop extension which provides the web developer to edit and to manage multiple online shops within the same page tree. The maintenance of the catalog happens completely in the front of the website. The content manager can easily edit the product catalog. He also can easily add or remove product categories and navigation menu items. This is because of its friendly interface. The seller does not need to know web development or TYPO3 to update and to manage his TYPO3 shop.<br /> <br /> More details about Multishop you will find in https://extensions.typo3.org/extension/multishop/</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',402,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(538,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,403,1566825251,1544311745,7,0,0,2816,'textpic','Quick Shop','','','<p>Quick Shop  un Extension utile per la creazione di un nuovo negozio in TYPO3, molto pratico soprattutto per le piccole imprese. Quick Shop offre la possibilit di e-payment, una interfaccia di acquisto simile a Ebay, una galleria d\'immagini, e altri dettagli sul prodotto come la sua quantit nel negozio. Quick Shop include le funzionalit come l\'invio di una email al venditore, la consegna e la fatturazione, la posta elettronica al cliente.</p>\r\n<p>Quick Shop offre la possibilit di pubblicare le specifiche dell\'articolo in qualsiasi lingua. Inoltre Quick Shop  ottimizzato per i motori di ricerca (SEO). Questo TYPO3 Extension  una soluzione ottimale per le piccole imprese che non contengono molti prodotti, con molte specifiche, come il colore o le dimensioni. Purtroppo non si pu gestire un negozio online molto complesso con Quick Shop.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Quick Shop :<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/quick_shop/Index.html</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',403,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Quick Shop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:929:\"<p>Quick Shop is a useful extension for building a TYPO3 shop, very practical expecially for a small business and small budget enterprises. This extension provides e-payment, shopping interface similar to ebay, image gallery and more product details like minimum or maximum quantities in the store. Quick Shop includes functionalities like sending an email to the seller, delivery and invoicing, email to the client and other helpful features.<br /> <br /> Quick Shop offers the possibility to publish the item specifications in any language. Also it is optimized for the search Engines (SEO). Quick Shop is an optimal solution for small businesses that do not contain a lot of products, with a lot of specifications, like colour or size. You cannot manage a complex online shop with Quick Shop.<br /> <br /> More details about Quick Shop :<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/quick_shop/Index.html</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',403,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(539,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,404,1556605843,1544311745,7,0,0,3072,'textpic','Sistemi di negozio TYPO3 implementati come Widget','','','<p>I Widget includono tutte le estensioni e gli elementi software collegati con servizi degli altri sistemi. Tali applicazioni includono l\'implementazione completa del negozio online, collegato alla piattaforma TYPO3.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',404,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:41:\"TYPO3 shop systems implemented as Widgets\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:199:\"<p>Widgets include all extensions and content elements that rely on third-party services. Such applications include the complete implementation of the online shop, linked with the TYPO3 platform.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',404,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(540,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,405,1566825329,1544311745,7,0,0,3200,'textpic','Supr','','','<p>Supr  un progetto di Wirecard, un partner di TYPO3 GmbH. Questo  un TYPO3 Extension che semplifica il processo di avvio di un nuovo negozio in TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Questi sono le istruzioni per avviare un nuovo negozio in TYPO3 con Supr:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>registrati in Supr</li> 	<li>aggiungi i prodotti del tuo negozio online</li> 	<li>seleziona lo stile</li> 	<li>installa il widget Supr sul tuo sito web TYPO3</li> 	<li>metti un link ai tuoi prodotti su Supr</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Il pagamento  implementato nel widget, ma puoi personalizzare la spedizione del prodotto e altre funzionalit del negozio online.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Supr:<br /> Homepage https://www.supr.com/&nbsp;<br /> Si mantiene da TYPO3 GmbH<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/supr/&nbsp;<br /> Codice https://bitbucket.typo3.com/projects/SUPR/repos/supr/browse</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',405,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:4:\"Supr\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:801:\"<p>Supr is a project of Wirecard, a TYPO3 GmbH partner. It is a TYPO3 extension and makes easier the process of starting a new shop in TYPO3. You should follow these steps :</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>register at Supr</li> 	<li>add the products of your online store</li> 	<li>select the theme of your online store</li> 	<li>install the Supr widget on your TYPO3 website</li> 	<li>add links to your products on Supr</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The payment functionality is implemented in the widget, but you can customize the product shipping and other features of the online shop.<br /> <br /> More details about Supr<br /> Homepage https://www.supr.com/<br /> Maintainer TYPO3 GmbH<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/supr/<br /> Code https://bitbucket.typo3.com/projects/SUPR/repos/supr/browse</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',405,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(541,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,406,1566825387,1544311745,7,0,0,3264,'textpic','Widget offerti da Amazon','','','<p>Amazon offre \"Fulfillment by Amazon\" che  un insieme di servizi che integrano fatturazione, spedizione e altre funzionalit nel negozio TYPO3. I widget Amazon non sono solo per il sistema TYPO3, ma possono essere integrati in diversi sistemi web.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Widgets offerti da Amazon:<br /> Homepage https://affiliate-program.amazon.co.uk/<br /> Amazon FBA https://services.amazon.co.uk/</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',406,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Widgets offered by Amazon\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:438:\"<p>Amazon offers the \"Fulfilment by Amazon\" which is a set of services that integrate services such as billing, shipping and other functionality in the TYPO3 shop. Amazon widgets are not only for the TYPO3 platform, but they can be integrated into several web environments.<br /> <br /> More details about Widgets offered by Amazon<br /> Homepage https://affiliate-program.amazon.co.uk/<br /> Amazon FBA https://services.amazon.co.uk/</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',406,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(542,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,407,1556605874,1544311745,7,0,0,3296,'textpic','Sistemi di negozio TYPO3 implementati come integrazioni con un altro software.','','','<p>L\'integrazione con un secondo software implementa il negozio online in un altro sistema come Magento, Oxid o Shopware, con un collegamento esterno al sito web TYPO3.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',407,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:76:\"TYPO3 shop systems implemented as integrations with a thirds party software.\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:172:\"<p>Integration with a third party software implements the online shop in another platform such as Magento, Oxid or Shopware, with an external link to the TYPO3 Website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',407,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(543,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,408,1566825587,1544311745,7,0,0,3312,'textpic','Integrazione con Shopware: px_shopware','','','<p>Questo software  un Extension offerto da Portrino GmbH, che integra TYPO3 con Shopware. TYPO3 offre la navigazione, gestione dei contenuti e modulo di accesso. Il login nell\'account Shopware utilizza l\'API HybridAuth. Questo Extension include la gestione di contenuti TYPO3 con i collegamenti ai prodotti del negozio online. Tu puoi inserire i dettagli del prodotto come un normale contenuto di TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su px_shopware:<br /> Homepage http://www.portrino.de/<br /> Creato da Portrino GmbH<br /> Codice https://github.com/portrino/px_shopware</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',408,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:38:\"Integration with Shopware: px_shopware\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:559:\"<p>This software is a third party extension offered by Portrino GmbH. It integrates TYPO3 with Shopware. TYPO3 provides navigation, content management and login form. The login in the Shopware account uses the HybridAuth API. This extension includes in the TYPO3 content manager with the links to the products of the online store. Editors insert product details like a normal TYPO3 content.<br /> <br /> More details about px_shopware<br /> Homepage http://www.portrino.de/<br /> Maintainer Portrino GmbH<br /> Code https://github.com/portrino/px_shopware</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',408,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(544,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,409,1564493683,1544311745,7,0,0,3320,'textpic','Integrazione con Magento: Mate','','','<p>Questo Extension utilizza Magento come il sistema principale di e-commerce, ma il contenuto viene inserito da TYPO3. Quando TYPO3 serve la pagina web, viene consegnato solo il contenuto di TYPO3. Il contenuto consegnato da Magento pu essere arricchito dai contenuti del CMS.</p>\r\n<p>Detagli su Mate:</p>\r\n<p>Homepage https://www.maxserv.com/mate/&nbsp;<br /> Codice https://github.com/MaxServ/MATE</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',409,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Integration with Magento: Mate\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:446:\"<p>This extension uses Magento as the main e-commerce platform, but the content is fetched from TYPO3. When TYPO3 serves the webpage, only the TYPO3 content is delivered. The content delivered by Magento can be enriched by content from the CMS.<br /> <br /> More details about Mate:</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Homepage: <a href=\"https://www.maxserv.com/mate/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.maxserv.com/mate/</a><br /> Code: https://github.com/MaxServ/MATE</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',409,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(545,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,410,1564493705,1544311745,7,0,0,3324,'textpic','Integrazione con Magento: Mage  UniTY','','','<p>Questo software  un\'integrazione di Magento e TYPO3, chiamato Mage-UniTY. Il sistema principale  Magento, ma quando i dati vengono dal TYPO3, hanno la priorit su Magento. Il cliente non sa se il contenuto proviene da Magento o da TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Mage-UniTY:<br /> Homepage https://www.web-vision.de</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',410,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:40:\"Integration with Magento: Mage  UniTY\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:334:\"<p>This software is an integration of Magento and TYPO3, called Mage-UniTY. The main system is Magento, but when data are fetched from TYPO3 they have priority over Magento. The customer does not know if the content is from Magento or from TYPO3.<br />