gono che ogni attivit commerciale sia presente sul Web.&nbsp;<br /> Essere attivi nei social media  importante. Pero,  necessario anche un sito Web, in cui i clienti possono acquistare il tuo prodotto o possono cercare ulteriori dettagli sui tuoi servizi.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',435,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Advantages of having a website\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:605:\"<p>The number of people that are using the internet is increasing each day. If they need information, they will search it on the Internet.<br /> In this technologic era, you should see all of them as potential customers, as they will search on the web even for the things they buy or services they need.<br /> Having a website is so normal that customers suppose every business is present on the web on its own website.<br /> <br /> Being active in the social media is one side, but you also need a website where the followers can purchase your product or can search for more details of your services.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',435,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(565,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,518,1564491741,1544314765,7,0,0,1280,'textpic','Con un sito Web, tu sei un passo avanti rispetto ai tuoi concorrenti.','','','<p>Se i tuoi clienti non riescono a trovare la tua attivit online, troveranno i tuoi concorrenti. Se non sei presente sul Web, stai perdendo molte opportunit.  importante che il sito Web sia ben progettato, facile da navigare, ricco di informazioni e dettagli sui prodotti della tua attivit.</p>\r\n<p>Un sito Web dovresti vederlo come una rappresentazione online del tuo negozio e del tuo business. Se il sito Web  incompleto, mander i clienti a un\'altro negozio. Accade spesso che un cliente scelga di acquistare un prodotto online solo perch  descritto precisamente nei dettagli, in sito web bello ed elegante.</p>\r\n<p>L\'immagine della tua azienda  rappresentata dalla qualit del suo sito web.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',518,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:56:\"A website moves you a step forward from your competitors\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:670:\"<p>If your customers cant find your business online, they will find your competitors. If you arent present on the web, you are losing many opportunities. It is important that website is well designed and easy to navigate, and full of information and product details of your business. You should see it as an online representation of your shop and business. If the website is ugly or incomplete, it will send the clients to another company. It often happens that a customer chooses to buy a product online just because it is described in details and the website looks good and is stylish. The image of your business is represented by the quality of its website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',518,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(566,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,436,1566220792,1544314765,7,0,0,1536,'textpic','Un sito web  una promozione dei tuoi prodotti e servizi.','','','<p>Il sito web della tua azienda  il modo pi semplice con cui i clienti accedono ai prodotti o ai servizi che tu offri.  meglio che le foto dei prodotti siano sulla homepage, in modo che gli clienti gli accedano al pi presto possibile.</p>\r\n<p>Il sito web dovrebbe presentare meglio l\'elenco completo dei prodotti della tua attivit. Questa lista attrae il cliente che inizia a cercare un prodotto e ne acquista anche un altro. Forse il cliente non lo sapeva che la tua attivit lo vendesse quell prodotto. Per questo  importante di mostrare un elenco completo di articoli sul sito web.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',436,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:62:\"A website increases awareness about your products and services\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:486:\"<p>The website of your business is the easiest way the customers access the products or services you offer. You better put them on the homepage, so they access it as soon as possible. The website should better present the full list of the products that your business. This list attracts the customer which starts searching a product and buys a second one. Maybe he didnt know your business sells it too, and thats the importance of showing a full list of items on the website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',436,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(567,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,437,1564491791,1544314765,7,0,0,1792,'textpic','Un sito web funziona oltre le tue ore di lavoro.','','','<p>Il tuo sito web sar in funzione 24 ore al giorno, 365 giorni all\'anno, con la possibilit di raggiungere milioni di persone ogni giorno, e permetter ai tuoi clienti di contattarti oltre le tue ore di lavoro.</p>\r\n<p>Il tuo sito web, progettato da W3DEVELOPMENT, funziona benissimo anche quando tu sei al riposo o alle vacanze.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',437,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:43:\"A website increases your hours of operation\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:341:\"<p>Not only will your website be there 24 hours a day, 365 days a year with the possibility of reaching millions of people every day, but it will make it possible for your customers to contact you outside of your normal business hours. Your website, designed by W3DEVELOPMENT, is still working for you while you are at leisure or asleep.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',437,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(568,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,438,1566220868,1544314765,7,0,0,2048,'textpic','Un sito Web minimizza i costi.','','','<p><em>Un sito web riduce i costi di pubblicazione:</em>  il modo pi economico dove puoi scrivere la publicitt della tua attivit e dei suoi prodotti. Non avrai poi bisogno delle carte e dei materiali di stampa. La publicitt non sar localmente, ma con una audienza internazionale. Puoi mantenere il tuo sito web pi attuale, pi economico e pi facile da gestire rispetto a qualsiasi altra media.</p>\r\n<p><em>Un sito web riduce i costi di marketing:</em> forse ora trascorri molto tempo nella scelta della parola giusta da dire in un piccolo spazio di un annuncio in un giornale o a trenta secondi in TV. Un sito web offre uno spazio senza limiti di parole per la tua attivit. Puoi inserire tutte le informazioni di cui hai bisogno, aggiungendo ogni tipo di contenuto multimediale e rendendolo pi attraente di qualsiasi altra media.</p>\r\n<p><em>Un sito web riduce i costi di comunicazione:</em> i clienti navigeranno nel sito web, trovando tutte le informazioni di cui hanno bisogno sulla tua attivit, le immagini dei prodotti, la mappa dei tuoi negozi, le persone che offrono i servizi, il numero di telefono e l\'e-mail dove possono raggiungerti e qualsiasi informazione che tu desideri comunicare ai clienti. I partner commerciali, gli impiegati , i fornitori e tutti gli interessati ai tuoi prodotti e servizi otterranno queste informazioni dal tuo sito web.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',438,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:23:\"A website reduces costs\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1214:\"<p>A good website reduces publishing cost: It is the most affordable media where you can advertise your business and its products. You will reduce papers and print materials, and it is never locally, but a worldwide advertisement. You can keep your website more current, more affordable and easier to manage than any other media.</p>\r\n<p>A good website reduces marketing cost: You spend plenty hours in choosing the right word to say in a small space of a newspaper ad, or in a half minute in TV. A website offers an unlimited space for your business, you can put as many information as you need, by adding all type of multimedia content and making it more attractive than any other media.</p>\r\n<p>A good website reduces communication costs: The potential customers will get in the website all the information they need about your business, the images of the products, the map of the stores, the members of the team that offer the services, the phone number and e-mail where they can reach you, and any information you wish to communicate to the customers, but not only. Business partners, your team, suppliers, and everyone interested in your products and services will get this information from your website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',438,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(569,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,439,1564492033,1544314765,7,0,0,2304,'textpic','Un sito web migliora l\'immagine della tua azienda.','','','<p>Il sito web  una rappresentazione della tua attivit. Lui dovrebbe riflettere lo spirito della tua azienda. Se il sito  progettato da W3DEVELOPMENT, lui metter in luce i migliori valori dell tuo negozio e dei tuoi prodotti.</p>\r\n<p>Il sito dovrebbe essere moderno e aggiornato. Il modo in cui tu costruisci il tuo sito web  l\'immagine che i clienti percepiranno sulla tua azienda.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',439,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:37:\"A website enhances your company image\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:429:\"<p>The website is a representation of the vision of your business. It should reflect the spirit of you and your company. If its stylish and designed by W3DEVELOPMENT, it will highlight the best values for your store and products. It should be modern and updated, and even if it is a small business, it will portray itself in its big stature. The way you build your website is the image that the customers will perceive it.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',439,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(570,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,440,1566220920,1544314765,7,0,0,2560,'textpic','Un sito Web migliora il servizio per i clienti.','','','<p>Un sito Web  un ottimo modo per attirare i tuoi clienti, ma  anche un ottimo modo per farli tornare da te ogni volta che hanno bisogno di nuovo dei tuoi prodotti o servizi. Oltre alle informazioni relative direttamente al prodotto, tu puoi offrire suggerimenti su come prendersi cura del prodotto che hanno acquistato da te, o su come abbinarlo ad altri articoli.</p>\r\n<p>Se la tua attivit offre un servizio, puoi aggiungere nel tuo sito qualche suggerimento su come utilizzare questo servizio.</p>\r\n<p>Un\'altra pagina interessante del tuo sito Web potrebbe essere quella delle domande frequenti. In questa pagina, i clienti trovano le risposte sui servizi della tua attivit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',440,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:38:\"A website can improve customer service\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:601:\"<p>A website is a great way to attract your customers but is also a great way to keep them coming back to you whenever they need again your products or services. Besides the information related directly to the product, you can offer any suggestions how to care about the product theyve purchased from you, or how to combine to other items. If your business offers a service, you can add in your website any post or tutorial how to use this service. Another interesting page of your website might be an FAQ page, where the customers find any the answers related to the services of your business.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',440,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(571,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,441,1566220980,1544314765,7,0,0,2816,'textpic','Un sito web migliora la comunicazione con team, affiliati, agenti e fornitori.','','','<p>Il contenuto del sito Web potrebbe essere organizzato in diversi livelli.In questo modo, diversi utenti possano leggere le varie informazioni. Puoi pubblicare informazioni sull tuo personale in una pagina chiusa, in modo di essere raggiunta solo un password. Il sito potrebbe includere cambiamenti nell gruppo, pianificazione delle attivit, eventi o notifiche.</p>\r\n<p>Nel frattempo, gli utenti del web accedono solo ai dettagli del prodotto, alle forme di contatto e ai post pubblici della tua azienda. Sul sito puoi inserire tutte le informazioni che tu vuoi.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',441,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:90:\"A website opens new channels of communication with staff, affiliates, agents and suppliers\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:500:\"<p>You can organize the content of the website in different levels, so different users can read vary information related to them. You can post information for your team in a closed location, so they reach it only by a password. It might include changes in the team, task schedule, events or notifications. Meanwhile, the wide web users access the product details, contact forms and public posts related to your company. You can put as much or as little information as you want on your site.&nbsp;</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',441,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(572,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,442,1564436163,1544314765,7,0,0,2944,'textpic','Scrivici','','','<p>Che cosa stai aspettando? Scrivici oggi sulle tue idee riguardo all tuo sito web!</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',1,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',442,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Contact us\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:87:\"<p>What are you waiting for? Contact us today, and lets talk about your website!</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\