zhdimisht smartphone. Shum biznese t vogla po bhen prezent n aplikacione mobile, duke prdorur faqet e tyre t internetit, mediat sociale si dhe aplikacione t tjera q promovojn biznesin e tyre. Kjo do t thot q gjithnj e m shum faqe interneti do jen me dizajn t prshtatshm.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',1,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(613,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612857051,1547400909,1,0,0,48,'textpic','Prkufizim i dizajnit t prshtatshm','','','<p>Nj faqe interneti e par n nj ekran desktop, mund t prmbaj t gjith informacionin n&nbsp;nj kolon t gjer.</p>\r\n<p>E njjta faqe interneti&nbsp;e par n nj smartphone nuk e shfaq dot t gjith informacionin n nj kolon, kshtu q prdoruesi duhet t lviz horizontalisht.<br /> Por, prdoruesve&nbsp;nuk u&nbsp;plqen t lvizin n faqe dhe t zmadhojn.</p>\r\n<p>Nj problem tjetr me faqet e internetit sht koha e ngarkimit t tyre n pajisjet mobile. Imazhet e mdha e ngadalsojn faqen e internetit.</p>\r\n<p>Duke prdorur dizajnin e prshtatshm, tablet-i dhe smartphone do t prshtaten automatikisht me gjersin e faqes s internetit.</p>\r\n<p>Prdoruesi lexon prmbajtjen e faqes pa patur nevoj t lvizin n faqe me ndihmn e ashensorit horizontal. Imazhet e mdha do t prshtaten mir dhe pa u shtrembruar.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',345,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:27:\"Responsive Design Explained\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:907:\"<p>A traditional website, when viewed in a desktop display, might contain one large column. The same website viewed on a smartphone does not display the whole information, and the user must scroll horizontally. But users don\'t like scrolling and zooming. Another problem with traditional websites is their loading time in the mobile devices. The large images on the website will slow it down.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Responsive web design, defined by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://alistapart.com/article/responsive-web-design/\" target=\"_blank\">Ethan Marcotte</a>&nbsp;responds to the needs of the users and the devices theyre using.</p>\r\n<p>By using Responsive Design, the tablet and the smartphone will adjust automatically the width of the website. The user reads the content of the page and navigates through the website without the need of scrolling. The large images will fit in, instead of distorting the layout.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(614,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612857292,1547400949,1,0,0,56,'textpic','Karakteristikat e dizajnit t prshtatshm','','','<p>Disa nga avantazhet kryesore e dizajnit t prshtatshm jan:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li><strong>SEO</strong> preferon faqet e internetit me dizajn t prshtatshm.<br /> 	Nj faqe interneti e cila nuk sht me dizajn t prshtatshm mund t ket nj version t veant pr pajisjet mobile. Kjo do t thot dyfish pun pr t krijuar dhe pr t mbajtur link pr t dyja versionet mobile dhe desktop.<br /> 	Duke pasur nj dizajn t prshtatshm, optimizimi dhe mirmbajtja e faqes fokusohen n nj URL t vetme. Kjo gj jep qndrueshmri n strukturn e URL-s, n t gjitha pajisjet, pr rrjedhoj faqja do renditet m lart n rezultateve e krkimit.<br /> 	&nbsp;</li> 	<li>Nj website q prshtatet do t thot i thjesht pr tu mirmbajtur. Ndrtimi i nj faqeje t vetme me dizajn Responsive do t prgjysmoj koston e dizajnit dhe koston e mirmbajtjes s faqes s internetit. N terma afatgjat, prdorimi i dizajnit t prshtatshm do t minimizoj prpjekjet e mirmbajtjes duke ndikuar ndjeshm n koston totale t faqes s internetit.<br /> 	&nbsp;</li> 	<li>Nj faqe interneti i dizenjuar me Responsive Web do t rris shitjet e dyqanit tuaj online. Nse menaxhoni nj dyqan online, t gjith vizitort nga pajisjet smartphone jan blers potencial, prandaj sht m mir t mos i injoroni ato. Nse prdoruesit do t plqejn faqen tuaj, ata do t qndrojn m gjat dhe ndoshta do t blejn produkte t dyqanit tuaj. Gjithashtu, nj lundrim i thjesht n faqen e internetit bn q marketingu dhe komunikimi me blersin t jen n nj tjetr nivel.</li> </ul>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',346,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Responsive Web Design Features\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:2209:\"<p>Some of the main benefits and features of a Responsive website are:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li><em>SEO prefers Responsive websites.</em></li> </ul>\r\n<p>When it comes to Google, its easier for google to craw and index websites with a responsive design, also a mobile-friendliness website is favored by google for a higher ranking.<br /> A website which is not Responsive might have a separate version for mobile devices. This means the double effort to create and maintain the links for both mobile and desktop sites. Having a Responsive Design means that optimization and maintenance are focused on one single URL, which gives consistency in URL structure on all devices. That will make the website more popular among the rest of the search results.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li><em>A responsive website means Easy in Maintenance.</em></li> </ul>\r\n<p>Building a single site with Responsive Layout will reduce both the cost of the design and maintenance of the website. In long terms, it will minimize the effort of maintenance in a cost-effective manner.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li><em>Responsive Design will increase the sales of your online store.</em></li> </ul>\r\n<p>Nowadays, the number of users accessing the internet from computers has declined dramatically, while significantly more people access the internet from their mobile devices.</p>\r\n<p>So, if you own an online store, all mobile visitors are potential buyers, and you better not ignore them. If the users will like your website, they will stay longer and most probably will buy a product in your store. Also, the user-friendly behavior of your site will lead to higher conversation rates.</p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;Responsive Design Improve Site Speed<br /> If user is visiting your site and it takes too long to load, user with no hesitation will go elsewhere. Site speed is another advantage of responsive web design also is a factor of Google ranking, because it affects user experience. To further illustrate this point,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://neilpatel.com/blog/loading-time/\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Kissmetrics</a>&nbsp;found a number of useful stats that prove how loading time affects the so-called bottom line.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(615,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612857534,1547400988,1,0,0,60,'textpic','Si funksionon dizajni i prshtatshm?','','','<p>Dizajni i prshtatshm bazohet n teknikat : Fluid Grids, imazhe fleksibl dhe Media Queries.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>1.Fluid Grids </em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Teknika e Fluid Grids(rrjeteve fluide) prbhet nga specifikimi i elementeve t faqes n varsi t madhsis s faqes dhe jo me pixel. Projektuesi prcakton nj madhsi maksimale t faqes web dhe rrjetzimi bhet me nj numr specifik kolonash. N kt mnyr faqosja organizohet e rregullt dhe e leht pr tu trajtuar.</p>\r\n<p>Secili element i faqes s internetit vendoset me gjersi dhe lartsi proporcionale, n vend t nj numri t pixel. Sa her q ndryshon pajisja ose madhsia e ekranit t prdoruesit, elementt e faqes do t prshtaten automatikisht n gjersit dhe lartsit e tyre, duke ruajtur prmasat e specifikuara n raport me gjersin e faqes.</p>\r\n<p>Pr shembull, nse faqja ka dy kolona dhe gjersia e elementeve n faqe nuk vendoset n pixel, por n prpjestim me gjersin e faqes. Kolona e par mund t ket 60% t gjersis s faqes dhe rrjedhimisht kolona e dyt do t ket pjesn tjetr prej 40% t gjersis totale t faqes.</p>\r\n<p>Avantazhi i tekniks Fluid Grids sht se dizajni prcakton gjersin e elementeve me gjersin maksimale t faqes, duke u prshtatur n ekranet m t mdha.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>2.Imazhe fleksibl </em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Nj imazh fleksibl ndryshon prmasat e tij n varsi t madhsis s pajisjes nga ku prdoruesi po lundron faqen e internetit. Nj opsion pr imazhin fleksibl sht q t gjitha pajisjet do t ngarkojn t njjtat imazhe. Ikonat dhe logot e vogla nuk prmbajn problematika, por imazhet e mdha krkojn vmendje t veant.</p>\r\n<p>N mnyr q t ngarkoni m shpejt faqen e internetit, shfletuesit paraprgatitin t gjitha imazhet e saj. Ata mund t\'i identifikojn imazhet n kodin burim, prpara se t ngarkojn stilet CSS apo kodin e JavaScript.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo qasje do t penalizonte n t vrtet vizitort q prdorin pajisjet smartphone, duke i detyruar ata t shkarkojn automatikisht t gjitha versionet e t njjtit imazh!</p>\r\n<p>Nj zgjidhje pr kt problem sht prdorimi i imazheve grafik vektorial, t cilt jan t shkallzueshm, ruajn cilsin e tyre dhe mund t prshtaten me madhsin e ekranit t do pajisjeje.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>3. Media Queries </em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Dizajni i prshtatshm realizohet duke prdorur Media Queries, t cilat tregojn si duhen zbatuar rregullat e CSS. Media Queries i tregojn shfletuesit nse duhen aplikuar ose jo rregulla t caktuara CSS.</p>\r\n<p>Ky fakt varet nga lloji i pajisjes q po prdor vizitori. Media Queries aplikojn rregulla t ndryshme t CSS pr t njjtn prmbajtje HTML. N vend q t krijohet nj version pr smartphones dhe nj version krejtsisht t ndryshm pr kompjutert desktop, programuesi prdor t njjtin skedar HTML pr t kto pajisje.</p>\r\n<p>Kur shtohet nj artikull t ri ose modifikohet dika n skedarin HTML, ndryshimet do t shfaqen njson n t dy llojet e pajisjeve: smartphone dhe desktop. N kt mnyr, prmbajtja dhe paraqitja jan n skedar t ndryshm.</p>\r\n<p>Shfletuesi tregon paraqitje t ndryshme pr pajisje t ndryshme. Duke prdorur Media Query, prmbajtjes do i aplikohen rregulla t ndryshme CSS.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',347,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:36:\"How does Responsive Web Design work?\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:2746:\"<p>Responsive Design consists of fluid grids, flexible images, and media queries.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Fluid Grids</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The technique of fluid grids consists of specifying the elements by portion the size of the webpage, and not by pixels. The designer defines a maximum layout size and the grid is divided into a specific number of columns. In this way, the layout is maintained clean and easy to handle. Each element of the web page is set with proportional widths and heights instead of a fixed number of pixels. Whenever the device or screen size is changed, elements will adjust automatically their widths and heights, maintaining the specified proportions to its parent container.</p>\r\n<p>For example, if the page has two columns, the width is not set in pixels, but in proportion to the maximum layout size. Column 1 might take up 60% of the page width and column 2 might take up 40%.</p>\r\n<p>The advantage of the fluid grid is that the designer changes the maximum layout size and it will still work on larger screens due to the percentage based calculations.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Flexible images</li> </ul>\r\n<p>A flexible image changes its dimensions depending on the size of the device the user is viewing the website. An option for the responsive image is that all devices will load the same images. Small icons and logos might not be too bad, but a problem compounds quickly as the images get larger.</p>\r\n<p>In order to load faster the webpage, browsers preload all of its images, so they can identify them in the source code, before loading any CSS or JavaScript. This approach would actually penalize mobile visitors, by forcing them to download all the variants of an image!</p>\r\n<p>A well-known solution to a good performance is using vector graphics, which are scalable, maintain their quality, and can fit the screen size of every device.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Media Queries</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Responsive Design is implemented by using the Media Queries, which is a way to apply the CSS rules. Media Queries tells the browser to apply certain rules or to ignore them. It all depends on which kind of device is using the visitor.</p>\r\n<p>Media Queries applies different CSS rules on the same HTML content. Instead of creating a version of the website for smartphones and a totally different version for desktop computers, the programmer uses the same HTML file for both of them. When the content editor adds a new article or edits something in the HTML file, the changes will be applied in both mobile and desktop layouts. In this way, the content and the presentation are in separated files. The developer implements different presentations for different main types of devices, and by using Media Query, different CSS rules are applied.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(616,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612857711,1547401016,1,0,0,62,'textpic','N fillim, versioni Mobile ','','','<p>Duke ndjekur modelin pr ndrtimin fillimisht t versionit pr pajisjet smartphone (teknika Mobile First), dizajni i prshtatshm sht ndrtuar n baz t pajisjeve m t vogla q mund t ket prdoruesi, si jan smartphone ose tablet. Kur projektuesi prfundon dizajnin pr pajisjet e vogla, ai shton pjes kodi pr do madhsi t ekranit.</p>\r\n<p>Dy avantazhet kryesore t tekniks Mobile First:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Projektuesi bn nj plan pr at q sht me t vrtet e nevojshme pr tu shfaq n ekranin m t vogl, dhe m pas ai do t shtoj prmbajtjen pr ekranin m t gjer. Ky rrugtim ndihmon shum n ndrtimin e prmbajtjes thelbsore t faqes.<br /> 	&nbsp;</li> 	<li>Me teknikn Mobile First, kodi do t jet i thjesht dhe elegant.</li> </ul>\r\n<p><br /> Smartphone kan procesor m t vegjl, kshtu q kodi nuk duhet t jet kompleks. M von, stile shtes mund t shtohen pr t prshtatur paraqitjen pr pajisje me ekran m t madh.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',348,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"Mobile First\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:824:\"<p>Following the pattern Mobile First, the Responsive Layout is built based on the smallest devices that the user might have, such as a smartphone or tablet. When the designer finishes the layout for the smallest device, he will add the layout for every screen size, in the same project.</p>\r\n<p>There are two main advantages of the pattern Mobile First:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>The designer makes a plan of what it is really necessary to put in the smaller screen, and later he will add the content for the wider screen.<br /> 	This helps a lot in the construction of the core of the website.</li> 	<li>With Mobile First, the code will be simple and elegant. Smartphones have smaller processors, so the code should not be complex.<br /> 	Later on, extra styles can be added to customize the layout for the desktop screen.</li> </ul>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:250;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:17;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(617,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612857898,1547401052,1,0,0,63,'textpic','Tipografia e dizajnit t prshtatshm.','','','<p>Tipografia sht paraqitja e tekstit. Mnyra se si shfaqet nj titull n faqe sht nj faktor ky pr t trhequr vizitort, pr t mbajtur vmendjen e tyre dhe pr ti inkurajuar q t qndrojn m shum n faqen web.</p>\r\n<p>Gjithashtu, tipografia sht e rndsishme pr t theksuar nj pjes teksti. Praktikisht, tipografi e mir sht ajo q prmirson komunikimin me vizitorin. Vlen pr tu theksuar q teksti n faqen e internetit duhet t lexohet lehtsisht.</p>\r\n<p>M posht listohen parametrat e tipografis, t cilat duhen prcaktuar n fazn e projektimit:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Fonti i shkrimit</li> 	<li>Madhsia e shkrimit</li> 	<li>Gjersia e tekstit</li> 	<li>Lartsia Parametri Font i shkrimit jep efektin emocional n leximin t tekstit.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Zakonisht, projektuesit gjejn Familjen optimale t Fontit, bazuar n temn e faqes s internetit. Tre parametra t tjer: madhsia e shkrimit, gjersia e tekstit dhe lartsia prcaktojn nse teksti sht lehtsisht i lexueshm.</p>\r\n<p>N dizajnin e prshtatshm, tipografia duhet t ndjek gjithashtu disa rregulla. Projektuesi duhet t rris madhsin e shkrimit kur kalon n nj version m t gjer t ekranit. Kjo, pr arsyen se ne tentojm t lexojm nga larg kur pajisja sht m e madhe.</p>\r\n<p>Gjithashtu, dizajni nuk duhet t ndryshoj proporcionin mes tekstit dhe elementve t tjer t faqes. Projektuesi duhet t\'i kushtoj vmendje theksimeve. Duke theksuar nj titull, pjesa tjetr e tekstit duhet t mbahet n nj madhsi relative q trheq vizitorin.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',349,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Responsive Web Typography\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1431:\"<p>Typography is the appearance of the text and the cornerstone of web design.&nbsp;The way it is designed is crucial to attract the visitor, to hold his attention and to encourage him to read more information on the website. Also, typography is important in highlighting or not any part of the text on the website. Practically, good typography is the one that improves the communication with the visitor. It is very important that the text on the website is easily readable. These properties of typography are the key factor in the design phase:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Font family</li> 	<li>Font size</li> 	<li>Text width</li> 	<li>Line height</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The Font Family parameter gives the emotional effect of reading the text. Usually, designers find the optimal Font Family based on the topic of the website. Three other parameters Font Size, Text Width, and Line Height determine if the text is easily readable or not.</p>\r\n<p>In the Responsive Design, Typography should follow some rules also. The designer should increase the Font Size when switching to a wider screen version. This is because we tend to read from a distance when the device is bigger. Also, the designer should not change the proportions between the text and other elements of the website. The designer should pay attention to the highlights. By emphasizing a title it should also maintain the rest of the text in a relative size that attracts the visitor.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(618,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612857953,1547401082,1,0,0,319,'textpic','JavaScript: sa m pak aq m mir ...','','','<p>Kodi n JavaScript nuk sht i detyrueshm pr nj dizajn t prshtatshm.</p>\r\n<p>sht e vrtet se JavaScript e bn faqen m t bukur dhe m t leht pr t\'u prdorur, por nj dizajn plotsisht i prshtatshm mund t krijohet vetm me HTML dhe CSS.</p>\r\n<p>Ne ju sugjerojm q projekti i dizajnit t jet sa m i thjesht.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',350,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:28:\"Less JavaScript is better...\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:327:\"<p>JavaScript codes are not mandatory in a Responsive website. It is true that JavaScript makes the website nicer and user-friendly, but a fully Responsive Design can be created just with HTML and CSS. We suggest keeping the design project as easy as possible. This is a key factor for the whole performance of the website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(619,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612858042,1547401111,1,0,0,447,'textpic','Por, n fund t fundit, efekti \"Smartphone\" sht m shum sesa thjesht \"madhsi ekrani\" ...','','','<p>Smartphone jan pjes e jets son, jan me ne kudo ku shkojm. Por, jo gjithmon jemi n lidhje me internetin. Gjithashtu, shpesh kemi nevoj pr informacion sa m t shpejt.</p>\r\n<p>Duke marr parasysh t gjitha kto, dizenjimi i versionit Mobile t faqes s internetit nuk sht thjesht eshtje \"prshtatja e prmasave\", por edhe zgjidhja e shum problemeve t projektimit n Mobile.</p>\r\n<p>Sfid sht ngarkimi i prmbajtjes s faqes web sa m shpejt q t jet e mundur, me t gjitha funksionet e saj.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo sfid sht kryesisht pr pajisjet smartphone. Versionet pr desktop dhe pr tablet nuk kan nevoj pr kt ngarkim t menjhershm t faqes. Shpresojm q ky artikull ju ndihmoi t kuptoni qllimin kryesor t dizajnit t prshtatshm.</p>\r\n<p>Nse jeni ende t paqart rreth ktij dizajni, mos hezitoni t na pyesni, duke na shkruajtur e-mail.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',351,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:70:\"But after all, the mobile context is more than just the screen size...\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:934:\"<p>The mobile devices are part of our lives, and we take them wherever we go. But we dont have a strong internet connection in every moment. Also, we need the information as quickly as possible, as we often hurry up. Taking all these into consideration, building the mobile version of the website is not just adjusting the size, but also solving many problems of mobile development. The challenge is to load the content of the page as quickly as possible, with all its functionalities. This fast-loading design and build are mainly for the smartphones. Tablets and desktop versions do not need this immediate effect.</p>\r\n<p>Hopefully, this article helped you in understanding the main goal of Responsive Design, but if youre still feeling confused about it, dont be afraid to leave a question or comment. If youre already using responsive web design in your site or web application, share the link here so we can see!</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(620,65,0,0,0,0,1,1583327420,0,620,1612147039,1580741328,13,0,0,256,'textpic','Preface','','','<p>An e-Commerce platform is a piece of software that allows you to build an online store and run a business online.</p>\r\n<p>Most of the <strong>eCommerce</strong> frameworks used are currently inexpensive or free. The open-source platforms are valuable as they are not only free but also managed and developed by experienced people across the globe.</p>\r\n<p>It is advisable to decide on the experience you require from your online store which may be a self-hosting or complete package at a small fee.</p>\r\n<p>People use open-source platforms as they are packed with unique features and developer-friendly.</p>\r\n<p>In this article, we will focus on the top 10 important open-source <strong>eCommerce</strong> platforms to watch out in 2020 and how to choose the right one for your business.</p>\r\n<p>Its a difficult task for you to find the right eCommerce platform for your business.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>What does open source mean?</strong></em><br /> Denoting software for which the original source code is made freely available and may be redistributed and modified.</p>\r\n<p>So, you dont have to deal with vendor lock. All you need to do is figure out what your business goals are, here is a complete quick guideline that will help decide which open source is right for your <em><strong>eCommerce business</strong></em>.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(621,65,0,0,0,0,1,1583327420,0,621,1612146851,1580802034,13,0,0,1536,'textpic','Magento 2','','','<p><a href=\"https://magento.com/\" title=\"Magento\">Magento</a>&nbsp;is one of the most popular <strong>eCommerce</strong> platforms in todays market, build on open source technologies&nbsp;which provides online merchants with a flexible shopping cart system, provides more than 50 payment gateways, it is a&nbsp;<strong>PHP</strong>-based framework that helps in building scalable solutions.</p>\r\n<p>This platform comes packed with multiple plugins and extensions that can be easily integrated with the third-party apps.</p>\r\n<p>As it is built for the developers, so they do not have to start from scratch.</p>\r\n<p>The user needs expertise in <em><strong>PHP</strong></em>&nbsp;<em><strong>programming</strong></em>. The <strong>Magento</strong> had two versions <strong>Magento 1</strong> and <strong>Magento 2</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>The Magento 2 version is the latest development as more than 200,000 online retailers use it.</p>\r\n<p>This version offers tools to cover advanced marketing, catalogue management, and SEO needs.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,0,17,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(622,65,0,0,0,0,1,1583327420,0,622,1612147138,1582033771,13,0,0,1792,'textpic','WooCommerce','','','<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce</a> is a WordPress plugin that has user-friendly features and functionalities that can be integrated easily with your existing <strong>WordPress</strong> site.</p>\r\n<p>It is <strong>free</strong> to download and renders enormous extendible features.</p>\r\n<p>If you want to start a perfect <strong>E-Commerce</strong> startup up with a great website, then it is easily understandable and highest recommended.</p>\r\n<p>One of the most recommended open-source eCommerce platforms in the world, <strong>WooCommerce</strong> includes its own secure payment processor and shopping card.</p>\r\n<p>It provides plenty of options that support in building an amazing store with greater flexibility.</p>\r\n<p>Its professional, simple, possess the latest WooThemes, and has many customization options.</p>\r\n<p>It connects all the major gateways to your website. It also renders <strong>Stripe</strong> and <strong>PayPal</strong> as the default <em>payment gateways</em>.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,0,17,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(623,3,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,601,1547953875,1547953771,1,0,0,3456,'theme_grid-columns-4',' (copy 1)','','',NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,4,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"settings.frame_type\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">frame1</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',601,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:20:\"theme_gri