qosjen e hapsirs tuaj n Web. N vend q t stiloni cdo gj nga e para, ju mund t prdorni template n TYPO3, t bni ndryshimet si preferoni dhe t ndrtoni prmbajtjen mbi kt template. Struktura mund t ndryshoj me kalimin e kohs, ose ju mund t prdorni nj template te ri dhe prmbajtja do t integrohet me t.</p>\r\n<p>Shum programues kan skicuar dhe zhvilluar template TYPO3, duke i vn n dispozicion t zhvilluesve t tjer, me nj mim minimal ose falas. Megjithat, duhet t keni parasysh se jo gjithmon mimi tregon cilsin. Ju mund t gjeni templates t mrekullueshm dhe falas, shum prej tyre mjaft t dobishem. N kt rast, ju nuk duhet t bni zgjedhjen e template n TYPO3 duke u bazuar tek mimi i saj.</p>\r\n<p>Esht shum e rndsishme q komponentt e template t prshtaten me elementet e faqes, me vizionin tuaj dhe me funksionalitetin e projektit tuaj. Nse nj template prmban vetm disa element q do t integroheni n faqen tuaj web, pjesa tjetr e elementve duhet t projektohet nga e para ose duhet t llogaritni se sa sht kostoja n para dhe n koh pr t\'i vn kto elemente t munguara n faqen tuaj web.</p>\r\n<p>Ne sugjerojm q t merrni parasysh disa extension kryesor, me veorit e mposhtme, prpara se t shkarkoni nj template TYPO3:</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',654,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1355:\"<p>TYPO3 offers a simple way of customizing the layout and the design of your website. Instead of creating the style and the framework from scratch, you can use the TYPO3 templates, make the changes as you prefer and build the content upon it. The structure might change later, or might even use another template and the content will be integrated to the new design. Many programmers have sketched and</p>\r\n<p>Developed TYPO3 templates and made them available to other developers, for free or with a minimal price. However, keep in mind that not always the price indicates the quality. You can find awesome templates for free, lots of them stylish and useful. In this case, you should not make the choice of the TYPO3 template you will use by its price. Much more important are the template components will be similar to the design and the elements of your website.</p>\r\n<p>It is important that the design and the layout of the TYPO3 template will fit both with your vision and with the functionality of your web project. If a template contains only few elements that you will integrate in your website, the rest of them you should design from scratch or you should reconsider the fact it is worth in money and time to put them on your website.</p>\r\n<p>We suggest you consider the following extensions and features before downloading a TYPO3 template:</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',654,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(751,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,655,1564490712,1564434020,10,0,0,960,'textpic','Dizajni Responsive sht nj domosdoshmri n vitin 2019','','','<p>sht e rndsishme q t zgjidhni nj template TYPO3 e cila sht me dizajn Responsive, dhe t ndrtoni faqen q nga fillimi kt dizajn. Me nj dizajn t till fleksibl, prmbajtja do t prshtatet automatikisht me do madhsi t ekranit. Ju nuk keni nevoj t krijoni nj version t faqes web pr paisjet smartphone dhe nj version t dyt pr kompjuter.</p>\r\n<p>Dizajni Responsive do t\'ju kursej shum koh dhe para.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',655,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:39:\"Responsive web design is a must in 2019\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:371:\"<p>It is important that you choose a TYPO3 template which is responsive, and build the content from the start upon the responsive design. With such flexible template, the content will fit automatically to every display size. You dont need to create a mobile version and a desktop version of you website. The responsive template will save you lot of time and money.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',655,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(752,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,656,1564490735,1564434020,10,0,0,992,'textpic','Kompatibiliteti me versionin e TYPO3','','','<p>Jo do template TYPO3 sht n prputhje me versionin TYPO3 q keni t instaluar. Zakonisht, do model ka nj dokumentacion q liston versionet e TYPO3 me t cilt sht kompatibl. Ne ju sugjerojm t kontrolloni q versioni juaj i TYPO3 t jet i shnuar n dokumentacionin e modelit, nse dshironi t q dizajni i TYPO3 t funksionoj plotsisht. Nj verifikim i till bhet esencial nse doni t paguani pr template-in n fjal.</p>\r\n<p>Gjithashtu, nse do t prditsoni faqen tuaj n TYPO3 me nj version m t ri, ather templat q do instalonu duhet t jet kompatibl edhe me versionet m t fundit t TYPO3.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',656,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:32:\"Compatibility with TYPO3 version\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:554:\"<p>Not every TYPO3 template will be compatible with the TYPO3 version you have installed. Usually, every template has a documentation that lists the TYPO3 versions who it is compatible with. Make sure to check the TYPO3 version is listed in the template documentation, if you dont want to risk the TYPO3 template wont work. It becomes more important if you are going to pay for the template. Also, notice if you are going to update your website to newer version, the template should be keep you up to date with the latest versions of the TYPO3.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',656,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(753,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,657,1564490761,1564434020,10,0,0,1008,'textpic','Licensimi i template n TYPO3','','','<p>Merrni parasysh faktin se template n TYPO3 jan me licensa t ndryshme. Ju duhet ta kontrolloni licensn para se t shkarkoni template, edhe kur sht nj licenc falas, edhe kur sht nj license komerciale.</p>\r\n<p>N disa raste nuk ju lejohet t bni ndryshime ose ta prdorni template pr qllime komerciale. N shum raste t tjera, duhet t prfshini nj link n faqen e internetit q i referohet zhvilluesit ose ofruesit t template.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',657,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:9:\"Licensing\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:399:\"<p>Consider the fact that TYPO3 templates come with different licenses. You should check it before downloading the template, in both cases when it is a free license or a commercial one. In some cases you are not allowed to make changes or use it for commercial purposes. In many other cases, you should include a link in you website that references the developer or the provider of the template.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',657,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(754,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,658,1564490781,1564434020,10,0,0,1016,'textpic','Serioziteti i burimit t template n TYPO3','','','<p>Jo cdo gj n Web sht e sakt. Ju mund t gjeni nj burim t gabuar, duke br q s bashku me template n TYPO3, t shkarkoni automatikisht Adware ose Malware. Kta ofrues nuk dallohen lehtsisht q jan t rrem, prandaj duhet t jeni t kujdesshm dhe t shikoni shenjat e nj ofruesi t sakt.</p>\r\n<p>Nj shenj q duhet par me vemendje jan komentet dhe reagimet e prdoruesve t tjer, q kan shkarkuar skedar t ngjashm nga ky burim. Gjithashtu, versionet demo dhe screenshotet e detajeve t template ju bjn t dalloni nj ofrues t besueshm.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',658,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:11:\"Reliability\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:565:\"<p>In the actual online world, while downloading TYPO3 template, you could meet a wrong provider, that along with the TYPO3 template, you will download automatically Adware or Malware. These providers are not easily recognized, and you should be careful and watch the signs of an established and honest provider. One good approach is the comments and the feedback of the other users that have downloaded similar templates from the same provider. Also, the demo versions and the screenshots of the details of the template are a clear sign of a reliable provider.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',658,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(755,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,659,1564490798,1564434020,10,0,0,1020,'textpic','TemplaVoil!: nj version alternativ pr template','','','<p>TemplaVoil! sht nj extension i TYPO3 e cila ofron nj mnyr t re t krijimit dhe redaktimit t elementve t faqes, duke ofruar nj tjetr ndrfaqe back-end t sistemit TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Ne ju sugjerojm TemplaVoil! si nj teknik pr krijimin e strukturave fleksibile t faqes, t cilat n sistemin TYPO3 njihen si kolona. TemplaVoil! prmban disa dizajne tradicionale pr elementt e faqes web, por n nj ndrfaqe mjaft t thjeshtuar, ku nevojitet vetm nj klik pr t prmirsuar pamjen. TemplaVoil! ju drejton n prmirsimin e TYPO3 Core, duke shtuar konceptin e FlexForms. Kjo lejon q sistemi TYPO3 t mbshtes prmbajtjen n skedart XML dhe n strukturat e t dhnave.</p>\r\n<p>Disa informacione t tjera n lidhje me TemplaVoil! mund t gjeni n kt link:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/templavoila/\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/templavoila/</a></p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',659,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:45:\"TemplaVoil : an alternative template engine\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:912:\"<p>TemplaVoil! is a TYPO3 extension which offers a new way of creating and editing the components of the website, which means another interface of the back-end of the TYPO3 system. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We suggest TemplaVoil! as a technique of creating flexible page structures, which in TYPO3 system are known as columns. TemplaVoil! maintains few traditional template design on content elements, but in a more user-friendly interface, where just a click is needed to improve the style. TemplaVoil! lead to improvements of the TYPO3 Core, by adding the concept and the implementation of the FlexForms. It allows the TYPO3 system back-end to store the content in XML files and data-structures.</p>\r\n<p>Some information related to this extension, you can find in this link :</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/templavoila/\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/templavoila/</a></p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',659,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(756,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,660,1564490840,1564434020,10,0,0,1022,'textpic','Sliding-Header: nj element profesional i template','','','<p>N ditt e sotme, nj element shum i zakonshm i dizajnit t nj faqe interneti sht nj sliding-header, i cili prmban nj imazh kryesor dhe nj slider si nj version i zgjeruar i ktij imazhi. N slider ka fotografi t ndryshme q lidhen me imazhin kryesor. Nj elementi i till i shton mjaft profesionalizm faqes tuaj n TYPO3. Slider-i mund t prmbaj do element multimedial, si pr shembull video ose butona CTA.</p>\r\n<p>Sliding-Header prdoret pr t nxjerr n pah kto elemente multimedial por njkohsisht prdor me kursim hapsirn n faqen web.Ai i impresionon vizitort, si nj element i thjesht, elegant, i leht pr t\'u lexuar dhe i dizajnuar mir.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',660,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:38:\"Sliding-Header: a professional element\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:611:\"<p>Nowadays, a very common element of the design of a website is a sliding header, with a main image in header, and a slider as an extended version of that. In the slider there are multiple photos related to the image header. You website will have a professional look with such TYPO3 content element. Sliders contains not only images, they can contain any multimedia element, such as videos or CTA buttons. Sliders are used to highlight these elements, and to reduce the space used for these elements.</p>\r\n<p>It impresses the visitors, which find the slider simple, stylish, easy to read and good designed.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',660,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(757,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,661,1564490876,1564434020,10,0,0,1023,'textpic','realURL','','','<p>Ne mbajm mend lehtsisht nj faqe interneti duke kujtuar URL-n e saj. Por, TYPO3 funksionon sipas ID-s s faqes. Kjo teknik vendos pr do faqe nj numr unik dhe URL-ja e faqes sht dika e till si \"... index.php?Id =123&amp;type=0\".</p>\r\n<p>N kto raste na hyn n pun nj extension i quajtur realURL, i cili prkthen ID t faqes n URL. N kt mnyr, ne mund t kujtojm faqen duke u bazuar tek emri dhe URL-ja e saj. Natyrisht q ekzistojn extension t tjer n TYPO3 Repository, q bjn kt konvertim, por realURL sht m i njohuri.</p>\r\n<p>Ne sugjerojm t shkarkoni nj template n TYPO3 q prfshin extension realURL, duke br q ky funksionalitet t jet vetm nj klikim i butonit n editorin e faqes suaj t internetit.</p>\r\n<p>M shum detaje n lidhje me realURL, ju mund t gjeni n linkun:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://extensions.typo3.org/extension/realurl/\">https://extensions.typo3.org/extension/realurl/</a></p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',661,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"RealURL\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:906:\"<p>Normally, we remember easily a web page by its URL. But, TYPO3 works by page-ID. This technique sets to each page a unique number, and the URL of the page is something like ...index.php?id=123&amp;type=0.</p>\r\n<p>There is a useful extension, named realURL which provides a translation from page ID to URLs, so we can remember the page by its name and URL. Of course there are other alternate TYPO3 Extensions in the Repository, that make this conversion, but realURL is the most known one. With this tool, you can handle also redirects to the page. We suggest to download a TYPO3 template that includes the realURL extension, so this functionality will be just one button click in the design of your website.</p>\r\n<p>More details related to realURL, you can find in the link:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://extensions.typo3.org/extension/realurl/\">https://extensions.typo3.org/extension/realurl/</a></p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',661,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(758,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,662,1564435509,1564434020,10,0,0,1279,'textpic','NEWS-System','','','<p>Nse dshironi t integroni n faqen tuaj edhe modulin e lajmeve, ju duhet t kontrolloni s pari nse template n TYPO3 do t prfshij kt funksionalitet. Moduli i lajmeve prmban pjes t ndryshme. Sistemi i lajmeve prfaqsohet si artikuj dhe ruhet n nj dosje. Nj faqe do t prmbaj extension q lexon t gjitha artikujt n dosjen e lajmeve. Kjo faqe duhet t mbetet e pandryshueshme pasi nj modifikim i saj mund t shkaktoj mosfunksionimin e modulit t lajmeve.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Pr m shum detaje, ndiqni kt link:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/news/\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/news/</a></p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',662,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:11:\"NEWS-System\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:600:\"<p>If you want to integrate the news module in your website, you should check first if the TYPO3 template will include this functionality. The news module contains different parts. News system is represented as articles, and is stored in a folder. One of couple of pages in the website will contain the extension that reads all the articles in the news folder. These pages should never be altered; it might cause an issue of the news feeds.</p>\r\n<p>For more details, follow this link: https<a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/news/\">://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/news/</a></p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',662,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(759,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,663,1564435607,1564434020,10,0,0,1407,'textpic','Przgjedhja nga SEO','','','<p>Aktualisht, Search Engine Optimization sht nj faktor ky drejt nj faqeje t rekomanduar. Vizitort dhe motort e krkimit duhet t gjejn leht faqen tuaj te internetit, mes shum faqeve t tjera t ngjashme. Por si t ngjisim m lart n renditje krkimi faqen ton?</p>\r\n<p>Kompanit si Google, Bing ose Yahoo, ofrojn motor krkimi t cilt na ndihmojn pr t gjetur informacionin q po krkojm. Ata indeksojn faqet e internetit dhe i rendisin ato, bazuar n fjal kye t prmbajtjes dhe n vendndodhjen s tyre. Kur nj prdorues po krkon pr nj fjal kye specifike, n nj vend t caktuar, motori i krkimit do t rendis faqet e internetit, bazuar pikrisht n kt indeksin q ata i kan caktuar.</p>\r\n<p>Cdo modifikim i minuts s fundit ndoshta nuk sht indeksuar ende. Pr motorin e krkimit nevojiten deri n tre muaj koh pr t gjetur dhe indeksuar versionin m t fundit t faqes suaj t internetit.</p>\r\n<p>Shtimi i extension-it SEO_dynamic_tag n faqen tuaj t internetit, do t prmirsoj mnyrn se si motort e krkimit e shohin dhe e rendisin at. Ky extension n TYPO3 krijon etiket pr titullin, etiket kanonike si dhe autorin e meta tag, fjalt kye dhe prshkrimin. Ai mund t lidh deri n tre fusha t bazs s t dhnave.</p>\r\n<p>Pr m shum informacion n lidhje me kt shtojc TYPO3, mund t gjeni n:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/seo_dynamic_tag/stable/Introduction/\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/seo_dynamic_tag/stable/Introduction/</a></p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',663,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"SEO Extension\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1421:\"<p>Nowadays, Search Engine Optimization is a key factor toward an attractive and recommended website. Visitors and web search engines should find your website easily, among many other related websites. But how we can improve the way our website will be reached?</p>\r\n<p>Companies like Google, Bing or Yahoo, offers search engines which help us to find the information we are searching for. The can move on web and download websites. Later they index the websites, and rank them, based on keywords of their contents and location. When a user is searching for a specific keyword, in a specific location, the search engine will list the related pages, based on this index.</p>\r\n<p>You could understand that any last minute modification most probably is not indexed yet. It takes up to three months to the search engine to find and index the latest version of your website.</p>\r\n<p>Adding SEO_dynamic_tag to your website, will improve the way that search engines see and rank your website. This TYPO3 extension generated the title tag, the canonical tag and the meta tag author, keywords and description. It can concatenate up to three fields of the database,</p>\r\n<p>For more information related to this TYPO3 extension, you can find in :</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/seo_dynamic_tag/stable/Introduction/\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/seo_dynamic_tag/stable/Introduction/</a></p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',663,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(760,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,664,1564490947,1564434020,10,0,0,1471,'textpic','Forma e kontaktit: nj mnyr e leht q vizitort t mund t\'ju kontaktojn','','','<p>Ne rekomandojm q faqja e internetit t prmbaj nj element Form Kontakti, pasi shum prdorues duan t shkruajn ose t lidhen me ju, pr ndonj pyetje n lidhje me shrbimet q ju ofroni. Prandaj duhet t kontrolloni nse template i TYPO3 q po prdorni, prmban elemente pr formn e kontaktit. Kto forma jan pak m t komplikuara sesa elementt e tjer t nj faqe interneti. Ato jan nj koleksion elementesh t tilla si subjekti, emaili i drguesit (ktu prfshihen disa rregulla t vlefshmris), si dhe nj hapsir tekst pr emailin. Mos harroni butonin q drgon e-mailin pr tek administratori i faqes.</p>\r\n<p>Ne ju sugjerojm t prdorni extension ContactForm.</p>\r\n<p>Pr m tepr informacion mbi kt extension do gjeni n linkun:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/EditorsTutorial/ContentElements/ContactForm/Index.html\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/EditorsTutorial/ContentElements/ContactForm/Index.html</a></p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',664,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:54:\"Contact form: an easy way the visitors can contact you\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:820:\"<p>We recommend the website contain a Contact Form element, as many users want to write or contact to you, asking any question regarding the service you offer. You should check if the TYPO3 template you are using will offer any contact form element. Contact forms are a bit more complicated than other elements of a website. They are seen as a collection of input elements, such as topic, email, which requires validation rules, and an input text area for the message. Dont forget the submit button that sends the email to the admin of the webpage. We suggest you the ContactForm elements, and the documentation link:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/EditorsTutorial/ContentElements/ContactForm/Index.html\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/EditorsTutorial/ContentElements/ContactForm/Index.html</a></p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',664,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(761,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,665,1564435716,1564434020,10,0,0,1503,'textpic','Multilanguage: pr nj faqe interneti ndrkombtare','','','<p>Sistemi i TYPO3 ndrton gjuht duke i strukturuar n shtresa. T gjitha gjuht jan n t njjtn faqe. Faqja e internetit TYPO3 sht krijuar n gjuhn e paracaktuar nga zhvilluesi, dhe faqet mund t prkthehen n gjuh t tjera. Pr kt prkthim, duhet t ekzistoj nj lidhje mes gjuhs s paracaktuar q n ndrtim dhe gjuhve t huaja. Kjo do t thot q i gjith prkthimi n nj gjuh t huaj ka nj lloj treguesi pr versionin origjinal t paracaktuar.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',665,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:53:\"Multilanguage Extension: for an international website\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:379:\"<p>TYPO3 system builds the languages in layers. All languages are on the same page. The TYPO3 website is created in the default language, and multiple pages can be translated in other languages. There needs to be a connection between the default language and their translation. This means all the translation needs to have a kind of pointer to their original default element.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',665,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(762,90,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,666,1564490957,1564434020,10,0,0,1519,'textpic','static_info_tables: Informacione themelore','','','<p>Extension i TYPO3 i quajtur static_info_tables sht nj grup tabelash t bazs s t dhnave, q rujan t dhnat n lidhje me vendet, gjuht, shtetet, krahinat dhe monedhat e huaja.</p>\r\n<p>T dhna t tilla ruhen si variabla statik, q do t thot se sistemi nuk mund t ndryshoj vlerat e tyre, por i prdor ato si referenc. T dhnat ruhen n back-end t TYPO3, n nivelin rrnj n hierarkin e faqes.</p>\r\n<p>Static_info_tables prfshin:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp; &nbsp; prkufizimet e tabelave dhe prmbajtjet pa vendodhje t prcaktuar;</li> 	<li>&nbsp; &nbsp; nj model domain extbase i zgjeruar;</li> 	<li>&nbsp; &nbsp; metodat e prgjithshme t aksesit n Repository;</li> 	<li>&nbsp; &nbsp; nj API pr plug-in dhe template tradicionale pre-Extbase;</li> 	<li>&nbsp; &nbsp; nj modul back-end t Extbase pr krijimin e paketave t gjuhve;</li> 	<li>&nbsp; &nbsp; modulet t cilat tregojn vendndodhjen e prmbajtjeve t tabelave.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>M shum detaje n lidhje me static_info_tables, ju mund t gjeni n linkun e mposhtm:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/static_info_tables/\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/static_info_tables/</a></p>\r\n<p>Si prmbledhje, ju sugjerojm t vini re kto cilsi dhe extension, para se t przgjidhni se cilin template n TYPO3 do prdorni, n mnyre q t prfshijn t gjitha funksionalitetet baz pr faqen tuaj, duke i dhn nj pamje profesionale dhe karakteristika t dobishme pr prdoruesit.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',666,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:38:\"static_info_tables : Basic information\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1233:\"<p>The TYPO3 Extension named static_info_tables is a set of database tables which stores data related on locations, countries, languages, states, provinces and currencies.</p>\r\n<p>Such data are stored as static variables, which means the system cannot change their values, but only use them as reference. Data are stored in the TYPO3 backend, in the root level of the page tree.</p>\r\n<p>The static_info_tables includes:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>the tables definitions and non-localized contents;</li> 	<li>an extensible Extbase domain model;</li> 	<li>the generic repository access methods;</li> 	<li>an API for traditional pre-Extbase plugins and modules;</li> 	<li>an Extbase backend module for creating language packs;</li> 	<li>Modules which provide localization of the tables contents.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>More details related to the static_info_tables Extension, you can find in the following link: <a href=\"https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/static_info_tables/\">https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/static_info_tables/</a></p>\r\n<p>As conclusion, we highlight the use of TYPO3 templates that include all the functionalities that you design in your website, by adding a professional look and useful features to the users.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',666,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(763,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,729,1564434933,1564434829,1,0,0,384,'image','','','',NULL,0,0,0,0,1,750,0,2,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,1,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',729,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";s:5:\"image\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:1;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:750;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:4:\"none\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',729,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,