,620,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Preface\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:547:\"<p>Most of the ecommerce frameworks used presently are inexpensive or free. The open-source platforms are worthy as they are not only free but also managed and developed by experienced people across the globe. It is advisable to decide about the experience you require from your online store that may be a self-hosting or complete package at a small fee, etc. People use open-source platforms as they are packed with unique features and developer friendly. Lets discuss top 10 important open-source ecommerce platforms to watch out in 2019.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',620,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(796,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,621,1567427643,1567427542,10,0,0,960,'textpic','Magento 2','','','<p>Magento bazohet kod PHP, i cili ndihmon n ndrtimin e algoritmeve t prshkallzuara. Kjo platform vjen e mbushur me plugins dhe extensions, t cilat mund t integrohen lehtsisht me aplikacionet e palve t treta. Magento 2 sht ndrtuar pr zhvilluesit, kshtu q ata nuk kan pse t nisin kodin nga e para. Prdoruesi i ksaj platforme ka nevoj pr eksperience programimi n PHP. Magento vjen me dy versione: Magento 1 dhe Magento 2. Versioni Magento 2 sht risia e fundit, pasi m shum se 200,000 shits me pakic n internet e prdorin kt version. Ai ofron mjete pr t mundsuar marketingun, menaxhimin e katalogut dhe nevojat e SEO.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',621,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:9:\"Magento 2\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:577:\"<p>Magento is based upon the PHP-based framework that helps in building scalable solutions. This platform comes packed with multiple plugins and extensions that can be easily integrated with the third-party apps. As it is built for the developers, so they do not have to start from scratch. The user needs expertise in PHP Programming. The Magento had two versions Magento 1 and Magento 2. The Magento 2 version is the latest development as more than 200,000 online retailers use it. This version offers tools to cover advanced marketing, catalog management, and SEO needs.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',621,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(797,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,622,1567427765,1567427542,10,0,0,992,'textpic','WooCommerce','','','<p>WooCommerce sht nj plugin n WordPress, i cili ka karakteristika dhe funksionalitete t thjeshta pr prdoruesit. Ai mund t shkarkohet falas dhe ka funksionalitete t jashtzakonshme t zgjerueshme. Nse dshironi t filloni nj faqe t suksesshme shitjesh online, ju rekomandojm platformn WooCommerce pr thjeshtsin q ofron. Ajo siguron shum mundsi n ndrtimin e nj dyqani t mahnitshm, me nj fleksibilitet mjaft t madh. WooCommerce sht profesional, i thjesht, me WooThemes t fundit dhe me opsione t reja. Ajo lidh t gjitha portat kryesore me faqen tuaj te internetit. WooCommerce gjithashtu mund t lidhet me Stripe dhe me PayPal, t cilat jan portat e paracaktuara pr pagesn online.</p>\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',622,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:11:\"WooCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:595:\"<p>WooCommerce is a WordPress plugin that has user-friendly features and functionalities. It is free to download and renders enormous extendible features. If you want to start a perfect E-Commerce startup with a great website, then it is easily understandable and highly recommended. It provides plenty of options that support in building an amazing store with greater flexibility. Its professional, simple, possess latest WooThemes, and has many customization options. It connects all the major gateways to your website. It also renders Stripe and PayPal as the default payment gateways.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',622,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(798,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,628,1567427819,1567427542,10,0,0,1008,'textpic','Aimeos','','','<p>Aimeos sht nj librari me kod t hapur, n PHP. Duke qn nj framework pr e-Commerce, ajo ofron nj seri prbrsish pr aplikacionet e dyqaneve online. Aimeos sht e integruar n komponent t thjesht pr tu prdorur, q jan t disponueshm pr nj gam t gjer framework. Integrimet e saj ekzistuese prfshijn:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Extension i TYPO3 Web Shop</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paketa Laravel E-Commerce</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paketa Flow Online shop</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paketa SlimPHP E-Commerce</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Karakteristikat kryesore platforms Aimeos konsistojn n integrim t thjesht, veprime m t shpejta, aftsi pr menaxhimin e shum dyqaneve, funksione shum t shkallzueshme, fleksibilitet si dhe optimizimi pr paisjet mobile.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',628,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:6:\"Aimeos\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:643:\"<p>It is open-source PHP library and an E-Commerce framework offering a set of featured components for online shop applications. The Aimeos is integrated into simple to use components that are available for a wide range of frameworks. Its existing integrations include:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>TYPO3 Web shop extension</li> 	<li>Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>Laravel E-Commerce package</li> 	<li>Flow Online shop package</li> 	<li>SlimPHP E-Commerce package</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The main features of this platform consist of easy integration, faster operations, multi-store capability, highly scalable, flexible, mobile optimized, and configurable.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',628,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(799,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,630,1567427856,1567427542,10,0,0,1016,'textpic','osCommerce','','','<p>osCommerce sht n tregun e platformave e-Commerce pr 15 vitet e fundit. Ajo sht par si nj mundsi e vjetr, e besueshme pr shum biznese t vogla dhe startup-e.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo platform e-Commerce ofron m shum se 7,000 integrime falas me 13,000 dyqane online, t cilat funksionojn n kt platform.</p>\r\n<p>Sipas nj studimi, osCommerce sht e 11-ta m e popullarizuara n mesin e 1 milion site-ve, n kategorin me kod t hapur.<br /> Shitsit me pakic n internet e prdorin osCommerce pr lehtsin q ofron n ndrtimin nj dyqani online, lehtsisht t menaxhueshm.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo platform integrohet me t gjitha aplikacionet e palve t treta, duke paraqitur faqen tuaj n Web n gjuh t ndryshme.<br /> Ju mund t gjeni nj numr t madh programuesish n komunitetin e osCommerce, t cilt jua lehtsojn procesin e zhvillimit, dhe pse osCommerce nuk sht aspak komplekse.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',630,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"OsCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:788:\"<p>OsCommerce is into the business for the last 15 years. It is seen as an old reliable option for many small businesses and startups to get seamless features.</p>\r\n<p>This E-Commerce platform renders more than 7,000 free integrations with 13,000 stores running on this platform.</p>\r\n<p>According to a <a href=\"https://trends.builtwith.com/shop/osCommerce\">study</a>, it is 11th most popular amongst Top 1 million sites in the open-source category.<br /> The online retailers use it for its ease to design a well-managed online shop.</p>\r\n<p>This platform easily integrates with all the third-party apps, presents your online site in multiple languages.<br /> You can find a vast number of community developers to ease out your development process, and OsCommerce is not all complex.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',630,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(800,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,631,1567427919,1567427542,10,0,0,1020,'textpic','xtCommerce','','','<p>Kjo sht nj platform e re n tregun e e-Commerce. Ajo sht me kod t hapur, e prdorur nga mjaft biznese online n ditt e sotme. Zhvillimi i vazhdueshm i prmirson funksionalitetet e ksaj platform.</p>\r\n<p>xtCommerce ju ndihmon t promovoni nj numr t pakufizuar t produkteve n internet. Ju mund t krijoni nn-seksione t ktyre produkteve pr t\'i shfaqur ato me lehtsi.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo zgjidhje me kod t hapur siguron opsionin e nj dyqani ndrkombtar n gjuh t ndryshme, menaxhon kategori t pakufizuara, me nj ndrfaqe t thjesht, etj. xtCommerce, gjithashtu, ndihmon n krijimin e prgjigjeve t Cart2Cart ndaj krkesave t tregtarve online.</p>\r\n<p>Nse nuk jeni t sigurt pr integrimin e ksaj platforme E-Commerce, ather mund t jua besoni ndrtimin e dyqanit online profesionisteve t xtCommerce, duke e kaluar si shrbim outsource.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',631,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"xtCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:703:\"<p>This is a newer open-source <em><strong>ecommerce</strong></em> platform used by the business houses nowadays. The ongoing development is done with this platform to enhance its functionalities.</p>\r\n<p>This platform helps the store owners to promote an unlimited number of products online. You can even create sub-sections of these products to display them with ease.</p>\r\n<p>This open-source solution renders multilingual support, manage unlimited categories, easy to navigate interface, etc. xtCommerce also helps in making Cart2Cart responses to the requirements of e-merchants.</p>\r\n<p>If you are not aware of integrating this E-Commerce platform, then you can outsource the related services.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',631,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(801,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,632,1567427992,1567427542,10,0,0,1022,'textpic','WP E-Commerce','','','<p>Kjo platform mbahet si \"zgjidhja origjinale pr e-Commerce\" pr WordPress. Zhvilluesit e kan shkarkuar WP E-Commerce m shum se 3 milion her. Kodi pr kt plugin n WordPress sht mjaft i thjesht. Nse jeni profesionist n HTML dhe CSS, ather mund ta trajtoni lehtsisht kt plugin. Shitsit me pakic n internet mund t marrin mbshtetje nga agjensi t njohura pr zhvillimin e WordPress, ose mund t\'i drejtohen pr mbshtetje komunitetit t madh t zhvilluesve online. Shembuj t WP E-Commerce jan Mayruns Goods, MollyMeg, dhe Cronut.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',632,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"WP E-Commerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:522:\"<p>This plugin boasts as the original E-Commerce solution for WordPress. The developers have downloaded the WP E-Commerce more than 3 million times. The coding for this WordPress plugin is quite simple. If you are good at HTML and CSS, then you can handle this plugin with utmost ease. The online retailers can take support from the reputed WordPress development agency or can turn to the large community of online developers for support. The examples of WP E-Commerce are Mayruns Goods, MollyMeg, and Cronut.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',632,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(802,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,633,1567428031,1567427542,10,0,0,1023,'textpic','PrestaShop','','','<p>PrestaShop sht nj platform e re n E-Commerce, por po bhet mjaft e njohur pr shkak t instalimit, aksesit t leht dhe ndrfaqes t plqyer nga prdoruesit.</p>\r\n<p>Ju nuk keni pse t jeni ekspert n programim pr t instaluar PrestaShop dhe pr t filluar dizenjimin e dyqanit tuaj online.</p>\r\n<p>Sipas W3Tech, PrestaShop prdoret nga gati 1.4% e t gjitha faqeve t e-Commerce. Ajo preferohet nga bizneset e vogla bizneset e vogla.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop ka nj ndrfaqe t thjesht pr prdoruesin, me sistemin e menaxhimit t inventarit dhe me mirmbajtjen s dyqaneve online. PrestaShop siguron nj sistem menaxhimi pr shum shits dyqani, me nj navigim t leht pr shitsit.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',633,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"PrestaShop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:716:\"<p>The PrestaShop may be a newer E-Commerce platform, but it is getting popular because of easy installation, accessibility, and provision of the amazing interface.</p>\r\n<p>You do not have to be technically sound to install its plugin and start designing your store.</p>\r\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/cm-prestashop/all/all\">W3Tech</a>, PrestaShop is used by nearly 1.4% of all the online shopping websites. It is quite beneficial for small businesses to start with it.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop has a user-friendly interface with seamless inventory management system and store maintenance process. It also provides a multi-vendor support system with easy navigation across the site.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s: