,0,0,0),(808,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,620,1613030466,1567506551,11,0,0,320,'textpic','Le 10 migliori framework di e-commerce da non perdere nel 2021 ','','','<p>La maggior parte dei framework di e-commerce utilizzati attualmente sono economici o gratuiti. I framework open source<br /> sono preferite perch si offrono gratuite e possono essere gestite e sviluppate da persone esperte da tutto il mondo.<br /> I framework open source sono piene di funzionalit uniche e facili da sviluppare.</p>\r\n<p>In questo articolo c\' un elenco con le 10 principali framework di e-commerce open source, da non perdere nel 2021.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',620,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Preface\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1332:\"<p>An e-Commerce platform is a piece of software that allows you to build an online store and run a business online.</p>\r\n<p>Most of the <strong>eCommerce</strong> frameworks used are currently inexpensive or free. The open-source platforms are valuable as they are not only free but also managed and developed by experienced people across the globe.</p>\r\n<p>It is advisable to decide on the experience you require from your online store which may be a self-hosting or complete package at a small fee.</p>\r\n<p>People use open-source platforms as they are packed with unique features and developer-friendly.</p>\r\n<p>In this article, we will focus on the top 10 important open-source <strong>eCommerce</strong> platforms to watch out in 2020 and how to choose the right one for your business.</p>\r\n<p>Its a difficult task for you to find the right eCommerce platform for your business.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>What does open source mean?</strong></em><br /> Denoting software for which the original source code is made freely available and may be redistributed and modified.</p>\r\n<p>So, you dont have to deal with vendor lock. All you need to do is figure out what your business goals are, here is a complete quick guideline that will help decide which open source is right for your <em><strong>eCommerce business</strong></em>.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',620,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(809,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,621,1612147893,1567506551,11,0,0,352,'textpic','Magento 2','','','<p>Magento si basa su PHP, che aiuta a costruire funzionalit scalabili. Questo framework include numerosi plug-in<br /> ed extensions che possono essere facilmente integrati con le app di terze parti.</p>\r\n<p>Magento  stato creato per gli esperti, per costruire un plugin di Magento si ricomincia da capo.</p>\r\n<p>L\'utente ha bisogno di esperienza nella programmazione PHP.<br /> Magento ha due versioni: Magento 1 e Magento 2.</p>\r\n<p>La versione Magento 2  l\'ultimo sviluppo, in quanto la utilizzano oltre 200.000 venditori online.</p>\r\n<p>Questa versione offre strumenti per le funzionalit avanzate di marketing, gestione del catalogo e SEO.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,1,0,17,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',621,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:9:\"Magento 2\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1029:\"<p><a href=\"https://magento.com/\" title=\"Magento\">Magento</a>&nbsp;is one of the most popular <strong>eCommerce</strong> platforms in todays market, build on open source technologies&nbsp;which provides online merchants with a flexible shopping cart system, provides more than 50 payment gateways, it is a&nbsp;<strong>PHP</strong>-based framework that helps in building scalable solutions.</p>\r\n<p>This platform comes packed with multiple plugins and extensions that can be easily integrated with the third-party apps.</p>\r\n<p>As it is built for the developers, so they do not have to start from scratch.</p>\r\n<p>The user needs expertise in <em><strong>PHP</strong></em>&nbsp;<em><strong>programming</strong></em>. The <strong>Magento</strong> had two versions <strong>Magento 1</strong> and <strong>Magento 2</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>The Magento 2 version is the latest development as more than 200,000 online retailers use it.</p>\r\n<p>This version offers tools to cover advanced marketing, catalogue management, and SEO needs.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:17;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',621,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(810,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,622,1612147927,1567506551,11,0,0,368,'textpic','WooCommerce','','','<p>WooCommerce  un plug-in di WordPress, con caratteristiche e funzionalit intuitive. Questo plug-in  gratuito, e rende enormi funzionalit estendibili.</p>\r\n<p>Se vuoi iniziare una perfetta esperienza della vendita online, WooCommerce  facilmente comprensibile e altamente raccomandato.</p>\r\n<p>WooCommerce offre molte opzioni che supportano la costruzione di un negozio fantastico con una maggiore flessibilit, perch  professionale,  semplice, possiede gli ultimi WooThemes di personalizzazione.</p>\r\n<p>WooCommerce collega tutti i principali gateway al tuo sito Web, e rende anche Stripe e PayPal come gateway di pagamento predefinito.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',622,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:11:\"WooCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1028:\"<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce</a> is a WordPress plugin that has user-friendly features and functionalities that can be integrated easily with your existing <strong>WordPress</strong> site.</p>\r\n<p>It is <strong>free</strong> to download and renders enormous extendible features.</p>\r\n<p>If you want to start a perfect <strong>E-Commerce</strong> startup up with a great website, then it is easily understandable and highest recommended.</p>\r\n<p>One of the most recommended open-source eCommerce platforms in the world, <strong>WooCommerce</strong> includes its own secure payment processor and shopping card.</p>\r\n<p>It provides plenty of options that support in building an amazing store with greater flexibility.</p>\r\n<p>Its professional, simple, possess the latest WooThemes, and has many customization options.</p>\r\n<p>It connects all the major gateways to your website. It also renders <strong>Stripe</strong> and <strong>PayPal</strong> as the default <em>payment gateways</em>.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:17;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',622,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(811,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,628,1567507223,1567506551,11,0,0,376,'textpic','Aimeos','','','<p>Aimeos  una libreria PHP di e-commerce, con codice aperto, e che offre una serie di componenti per le applicazioni dei negozi online. Aimeos  integrato in componenti semplici da usare, disponibili per diversi framework. Le sue integrazioni esistenti includono:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp;TYPO3 Web shop extension</li> 	<li>&nbsp;Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>&nbsp;Laravel E-Commerce</li> 	<li>&nbsp;Flow Online shop</li> 	<li>&nbsp;SlimPHP E-Commerce</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Le caratteristiche principali di questo framework consistono in una facile integrazione, in operazioni pi veloci, in capacit multi-store, essendo altamente scalabile, flessibile, ottimizzata per dispositivi mobili e configurabile.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',628,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:6:\"Aimeos\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:643:\"<p>It is open-source PHP library and an E-Commerce framework offering a set of featured components for online shop applications. The Aimeos is integrated into simple to use components that are available for a wide range of frameworks. Its existing integrations include:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>TYPO3 Web shop extension</li> 	<li>Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>Laravel E-Commerce package</li> 	<li>Flow Online shop package</li> 	<li>SlimPHP E-Commerce package</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The main features of this platform consist of easy integration, faster operations, multi-store capability, highly scalable, flexible, mobile optimized, and configurable.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',628,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(812,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,630,1612147993,1567506551,11,0,0,380,'textpic','OsCommerce','','','<p>OsCommerce esiste da 15 anni.  vista come una vecchia opzione affidabile per molte piccole imprese e startup.</p>\r\n<p>Questo framework di e-commerce offre oltre 7.000 integrazioni gratuite con 13.000 negozi che sono costruite su basano su OsCommerce.</p>\r\n<p>Secondo uno studio, OsCommerce  l\'undicesimo framework pi popolare tra i primi 1 milione di siti con codice aperto.</p>\r\n<p>I venditori online lo utilizzano per la sua facilit di progettazione di un negozio online ben gestito.</p>\r\n<p>OsCommerce si integra facilmente con tutte le app di terze parti, presentando il tuo sito online in molte lingue straniere.</p>\r\n<p>Esiste un gran numero di sviluppatori che pu aiutarti per rendere pi facile il tuo processo di sviluppo, e per di pi, OsCommerce non  per niente difficile.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',630,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"OsCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:788:\"<p>OsCommerce is into the business for the last 15 years. It is seen as an old reliable option for many small businesses and startups to get seamless features.</p>\r\n<p>This E-Commerce platform renders more than 7,000 free integrations with 13,000 stores running on this platform.</p>\r\n<p>According to a <a href=\"https://trends.builtwith.com/shop/osCommerce\">study</a>, it is 11th most popular amongst Top 1 million sites in the open-source category.<br /> The online retailers use it for its ease to design a well-managed online shop.</p>\r\n<p>This platform easily integrates with all the third-party apps, presents your online site in multiple languages.<br /> You can find a vast number of community developers to ease out your development process, and OsCommerce is not all complex.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',630,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(813,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,631,1612148044,1567506551,11,0,0,382,'textpic','xtCommerce','','','<p>Questo  un nuovo framework di e-commerce open source utilizzata dalle case di business al giorno d\'oggi.</p>\r\n<p>Lo sviluppo in corso  fatto con questo framework per migliorare le sue funzionalit.</p>\r\n<p>xtCommerce aiuta i proprietari dei negozi a promuovere un numero illimitato di prodotti online.</p>\r\n<p>Puoi persino creare sottosezioni di questi prodotti per visualizzarli facilmente.</p>\r\n<p>Questa soluzione open source offre supporto multilingue, gestione di categorie illimitate, interfaccia facile da navigare, ecc.</p>\r\n<p>XtCommerce aiuta anche a fornire risposte Cart2Cart ai requisiti degli e-commerce. Se non sei a conoscenza dell\'integrazione di questo framework di e-commerce, puoi rivolgerti ai servizi correlati.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',631,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"xtCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:811:\"<p><a href=\"https://www.xt-commerce.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">xtCommerce</a>&nbsp;is open-source eCommerce Webshop Software (GPL). The ongoing development is done with this platform to enhance its functionalities.</p>\r\n<p>This platform helps the store owners to promote an unlimited number of products online. You can even create sub-sections of these products to display them with ease.</p>\r\n<p>This open-source solution renders multilingual support, manage unlimited categories, easy to navigate interface, etc.</p>\r\n<p>xtCommerce also helps in making Cart2Cart responses to the requirements of e-merchants.</p>\r\n<p>If you are not aware of integrating this E-Commerce platform, then you can outsource the related services.</p>\r\n<p>XtCommerce offer solutions for every eCommerce business type.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',631,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(814,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,632,1612148080,1567506551,11,0,0,383,'textpic','WP E-Commerce','','','<p>Questo plugin  \"la soluzione di e-commerce\" per WordPress.</p>\r\n<p>Gli sviluppatori hanno scaricato il WP E-Commerce<br /> pi di 3 milioni di volte. Il codice di questo plugin di WordPress  abbastanza semplice.</p>\r\n<p>Se sei bravo in HTML e CSS, tu puoi gestire questo plugin con la massima facilit.</p>\r\n<p>I venditori online possono ottenere un supporto dalla agenzia di sviluppo WordPress o rivolgersi alla comunit di sviluppatori online. Gli esempi di WP E-Commerce sono Mayrun, MollyMeg e Cronut.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',632,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"WP E-Commerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:853:\"<p>This plugin boasts as the original E-Commerce solution for WordPress. The developers have downloaded the WP E-Commerce more than 3 million times, this means that many online shoppers are familiar with this plugin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>WP-ECommerce has some pre-installed payment gateways such as, PayPal - Express, Google, Checkout etc.</p>\r\n<p>The coding for this WordPress plugin is quite simple.&nbsp;You only have to be good to HTML and CSS, and you can handle this plugin with utmost ease.</p>\r\n<p>The online retailers can take support from the reputed WordPress development agency or can turn to the large community of online developers for support.</p>\r\n<p>The examples of <a href=\"https://wpecommerce.org/\" target=\"_blank\">WP E-Commer</a><a href=\"https://wpecommerce.org/\" target=\"_blank\">c</a>e are Mayruns Goods, MollyMeg, and Cronut.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',632,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(815,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,633,1612149374,1567506551,11,0,0,639,'textpic','PrestaShop','','','<p>PrestaShop  un nuovo framework di e-commerce, ma sta diventando popolare grazie alla facilit d\'installazione, accessibilit e alla straordinaria interfaccia.</p>\r\n<p>Non  necessario essere un tecnico per installare PrestaShop e per iniziare a progettare il tuo negozio.</p>\r\n<p>Secondo W3Tech, PrestaShop  utilizzato da quasi l\'1,4% di tutti i siti Web di shopping online. Questo plugin  il preferito per le piccole imprese.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop ha un\'interfaccia intuitiva con un sistema di gestione dell\'inventario e di manutenzione del punto vendita.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop offre un sistema di supporto multi-vendor, con una facile navigazione all\'interno del sito.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',633,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"PrestaShop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:790:\"<p>The <a href=\"https://www.prestashop.com/en\" target=\"_top\">PrestaShop</a> may be a newer E-Commerce platform, but it is getting popular because of easy installation, accessibility, and provision of the amazing interface.</p>\r\n<p>You do not have to be technically sound to install its plugin and start designing your store.</p>\r\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/cm-prestashop/all/all\" target=\"_blank\">W3Tech</a>, PrestaShop is used by nearly 1.4% of all the online shopping websites. It is quite beneficial for small businesses to start with it.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop has a user-friendly interface with seamless inventory management system and store maintenance process. It also provides a multi-vendor support system with easy navigation across the site.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',633,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(816,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,634,1612149414,1567506551,11,0,0,767,'textpic','ZenCart','','','<p>Anche se non sei uno sviluppatore esperto, con l\'utilizzo di ZenCart puoi migliorare il tuo negozio di e-commerce.</p>\r\n<p>ZenCart ha circa 150.000 membri nella sua comunit di supporto.</p>\r\n<p>Secondo l\'ultimo studio, ZenCart  utilizzato dallo 0,1% di tutti i siti Web di shopping online. ZenCart include le seguenti funzionalit:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Fornisce un ottimo sistema di gestione del prodotto&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li> 	<li>Crea un inventario specializzato&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li> 	<li>Mantiene le vendite a portata di mano&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li> 	<li> costituito da modelli personalizzati&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li> 	<li>Si concentra al 100% sulle esigenze del cliente</li> </ul>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',634,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"ZenCart\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1069:\"<p>If you are not a skilled developer, then also with the usage of <a href=\"https://www.zen-cart.com/\" target=\"_blank\">ZenCart</a>, you can upscale your E-Commerce store.</p>\r\n<p>It has around 150,000 members in its support community.</p>\r\n<p>According to the <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/cm-zencart/all/all\" target=\"_blank\">latest study</a>, ZenCart is used by 0.1% of all the online shopping websites.</p>\r\n<p>ZenCart includes the following features:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Provides great product management system</li> 	<li>Creating specialized inventory</li> 	<li>Keeping sales at your fingertips</li> 	<li>It consists of customized templates</li> 	<li>100% focus on the customer needs</li> </ul>\r\n<p>ZenCart is a great decision, for business owners who decided to enter the online market or if you are looking to sell internationally ZenCard has some great multilingual options available.</p>\r\n<p>The system is user-friendly, although ZenCart is free it offers powerful features and services, making it a top contender in the shopping cart market.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6: