olto probabilmente hai sentito parlare di Responsive Web Design. Ti sei mai chiesto che cos\' esattamente un sito che applica il disegno Responsive Web?</p>\r\n<p>Responsive Web Design  la tecnica che consente al sito Web di adattarsi al dispositivo dell\'utente. Il programmatore pu scrivere il codice una volta e pubblicarlo ovunque, il che significa meno lavoro per lui. Il numero di visitatori che arrivano al sito Web da uno smartphone, un tablet o un iPod si aumenta ogni minuto. Statisticamente, nel 2018 ci sono circa 2,6 miliardi di persone nel mondo che usano lo smartphone. In realt, le piccole imprese stanno aumentando la loro presenza nelle applicazioni mobili, utilizzando i loro siti Web, i social media e altre applicazioni che promuovono la loro attivit. Ci significa che sempre pi siti Web saranno flessibili con un Responsive Design.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,300,2,NULL,'',0,'',344,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:33:\"Overview of Responsive Web Design\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:783:\"<p>Most probably you have heard about Responsive Web Design, but have you ever asked yourself what is it exactly a Responsive Website?</p>\r\n<p>Responsive Design is the technique which allows the website to adapt to the device of the user. The programmer can write the code once and publish it everywhere, meaning less work for him. The number of visitors that come to the website from a smartphone, tablet or iPods is increasing every minute. Statistically, in 2018 there are about 2.6 billion people in the world using the smartphone. Actually, the small businesses are increasing their presence in the mobile applications, using their websites, the social media, and other applications which promote their business. This means more and more websites are going to be Responsive.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:300;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',344,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(822,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,345,1568908644,1567774367,11,0,0,960,'textpic','Nei detagli del Responsive Web Design...','','','<p>Un sito Web tradizionale, visualizzato su uno schermo desktop, potrebbe contenere una colonna di grandi dimensioni. Lo stesso sito Web visualizzato su uno smartphone non mostra tutte le informazioni e l\'utente deve scorrere in orizzontale. Agli utenti non piace lo scorrimento e lo zoom. Un altro problema con i siti Web tradizionali  il tempo di caricamento nei dispositivi mobile. Le immagini di grandi dimensioni sul sito Web lo rallenteranno.</p>\r\n<p>Utilizzando Responsive Web Design, il tablet e lo smartphone regoleranno automaticamente la larghezza del sito Web. L\'utente legge il contenuto della pagina e naviga attraverso il sito Web senza la necessit di scorrere in orizzontale. Le immagini di grandi dimensioni si adatteranno invece di distorcere il layout.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',345,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:27:\"Responsive Design Explained\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:682:\"<p>A traditional website, when viewed in a desktop display, might contain one large column. The same website viewed on a smartphone does not display the whole information, and the user must scroll horizontally. But users don\'t like scrolling and zooming. Another problem with traditional websites is their loading time in the mobile devices. The large images on the website will slow it down.</p>\r\n<p>By using Responsive Design, the tablet and the smartphone will adjust automatically the width of the website. The user reads the content of the page and navigates through the website without the need of scrolling. The large images will fit in, instead of distorting the layout.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',345,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(823,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,346,1568908656,1567774367,11,0,0,992,'textpic','Le funzionalit del Responsive Web Design','','','<p>Alcuni dei principali vantaggi e funzionalit di un sito in Responsive Web Desing sono:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SEO preferisce i siti con un Responsive Web Design.</p>\r\n<p>Un sito Web pu avere una versione separata per i dispositivi mobili, ci significa un doppio lavoro per creare e mantenere i collegamenti per siti, sia mobili che desktop. Avere un Responsive Web Design significa che l\'ottimizzazione e la manutenzione usano un singolo URL, mantenendo una coerenza nella struttura dell\'URL su tutti i dispositivi. Il sito Web diventa cosi pi popolare tra il resto dei risultati della ricerca.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Il sito con Responsive Web Design  piu facile da mantenersi.</p>\r\n<p>La costruzione di un singolo sito con Responsive Web Design ridurr i costi di progettazione e di manutenzione. A lungo termine, ridurr al minimo lo sforzo di manutenzione, in modo conveniente.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Responsive Web Design aumenter le vendite del tuo negozio online.</p>\r\n<p>Se possiedi un negozio online, tutti i visitatori mobili sono potenziali acquirenti, quindi  meglio non ignorarli. Se gli utenti apprezzeranno il tuo sito Web, rimarranno pi a lungo e molto probabilmente compreranno un prodotto nel tuo negozio. Inoltre, una interfaccia intuitiva del tuo sito, porter il sito un al altro livello.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',346,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Responsive Web Design Features\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1253:\"<p>Some of the main benefits and features of a Responsive website are:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li><em>SEO prefers Responsive websites.</em></li> </ul>\r\n<p>A website which is not Responsive might have a separate version for mobile devices. This means the double effort to create and maintain the links for both mobile and desktop sites. Having a Responsive Design means that optimization and maintenance are focused on one single URL, which gives consistency in URL structure on all devices. That will make the website more popular among the rest of the search results.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li><em>A responsive website means Easy in Maintenance.</em></li> </ul>\r\n<p>Building a single site with Responsive Layout will reduce both the cost of the design and maintenance of the website. In long terms, it will minimize the effort of maintenance in a cost-effective manner.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li><em>Responsive Design will increase the sales of your online store.</em></li> </ul>\r\n<p>If you own an online store, all mobile visitors are potential buyers, and you better not ignore them. If the users will like your website, they will stay longer and most probably will buy a product in your store. Also, the user-friendly behavior of your site will lead to higher conversation rates.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',346,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(824,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,347,1568908708,1567774367,11,0,0,1008,'textpic','Come funziona il Responsive Web Design?','','','<p>Responsive Design  costituito da Fluid Grids, Flexible images e query multimediali.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br /> Fluid Grids</p>\r\n<p>La tecnica delle Fluid Grids consiste nello specificare gli elementi per porzione della dimensione della pagina Web, e non per pixel. La grafica si definisce con una dimensione massima del layout, che  diviso in un numero specifico di colonne. In questo modo, il layout viene mantenuto pulito e facile da gestire. Ogni elemento della pagina Web  impostato con larghezze e altezze proporzionali, anzich un numero fisso di pixel. Ogni volta che il dispositivo o le dimensioni dello schermo vengono modificati, gli elementi regolano automaticamente le loro larghezze e altezze, mantenendo le proporzioni specificate al contenitore principale.</p>\r\n<p>Ad esempio, se la pagina ha due colonne, la larghezza non  impostata in pixel, ma in proporzione alla dimensione massima del layout. La colonna 1 potrebbe occupare il 60% della larghezza della pagina e la colonna 2 potrebbe occupare il 40%.</p>\r\n<p>Il vantaggio della fluid grids  che continuer a funzionare su schermi pi grandi, a causa dei calcoli basati sulla percentuale.</p>\r\n<p>Flexible images ( immagini flessibili)</p>\r\n<p>Un\'immagine flessibile cambia le sue dimensioni a seconda delle dimensioni del dispositivo che l\'utente sta visualizzando il sito Web. Un\'opzione per l\'immagine flessibile  che tutti i dispositivi caricheranno le stesse immagini. Icone di piccole dimensioni potrebbero non essere un problema.</p>\r\n<p>Per caricare pi velocemente la pagina Web, i browser caricano in anticipo tutte le sue immagini, in modo che possano identificarle nel codice sorgente, prima di caricare CSS o JavaScript. Questo approccio penalizza i visitatori mobili, costringendoli a scaricare tutte le varianti di un\'immagine!</p>\r\n<p>Una soluzione ben nota per una buona prestazione  l\'uso della grafica vettoriale, che  scalabile, mantiene la sua qualit e pu adattarsi alle dimensioni dello schermo di ogni dispositivo.</p>\r\n<p>Media Queries</p>\r\n<p>Responsive Web Design viene implementato utilizzando Media Query, che  un modo per applicare le regole CSS. Media Query indica al browser di applicare determinate regole o di ignorarle. Tutto dipende dal tipo di dispositivo che utilizza il visitatore.</p>\r\n<p>Media Query applica regole CSS diverse sullo stesso contenuto HTML. Invece di creare una versione del sito Web per smartphone e una versione totalmente diversa per i computer desktop, il programmatore utilizza lo stesso file HTML per entrambi. Quando l\'editor dei contenuti aggiunge un nuovo articolo o modifica qualcosa nel file HTML, le modifiche verranno applicate sia nel layout mobile che desktop. In questo modo, il contenuto e la presentazione sono in file separati. Lo sviluppatore implementa diverse presentazioni per diversi tipi principali di dispositivi e, utilizzando Media Query, vengono applicate diverse regole CSS.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',347,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:36:\"How does Responsive Web Design work?\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:2746:\"<p>Responsive Design consists of fluid grids, flexible images, and media queries.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Fluid Grids</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The technique of fluid grids consists of specifying the elements by portion the size of the webpage, and not by pixels. The designer defines a maximum layout size and the grid is divided into a specific number of columns. In this way, the layout is maintained clean and easy to handle. Each element of the web page is set with proportional widths and heights instead of a fixed number of pixels. Whenever the device or screen size is changed, elements will adjust automatically their widths and heights, maintaining the specified proportions to its parent container.</p>\r\n<p>For example, if the page has two columns, the width is not set in pixels, but in proportion to the maximum layout size. Column 1 might take up 60% of the page width and column 2 might take up 40%.</p>\r\n<p>The advantage of the fluid grid is that the designer changes the maximum layout size and it will still work on larger screens due to the percentage based calculations.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Flexible images</li> </ul>\r\n<p>A flexible image changes its dimensions depending on the size of the device the user is viewing the website. An option for the responsive image is that all devices will load the same images. Small icons and logos might not be too bad, but a problem compounds quickly as the images get larger.</p>\r\n<p>In order to load faster the webpage, browsers preload all of its images, so they can identify them in the source code, before loading any CSS or JavaScript. This approach would actually penalize mobile visitors, by forcing them to download all the variants of an image!</p>\r\n<p>A well-known solution to a good performance is using vector graphics, which are scalable, maintain their quality, and can fit the screen size of every device.</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Media Queries</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Responsive Design is implemented by using the Media Queries, which is a way to apply the CSS rules. Media Queries tells the browser to apply certain rules or to ignore them. It all depends on which kind of device is using the visitor.</p>\r\n<p>Media Queries applies different CSS rules on the same HTML content. Instead of creating a version of the website for smartphones and a totally different version for desktop computers, the programmer uses the same HTML file for both of them. When the content editor adds a new article or edits something in the HTML file, the changes will be applied in both mobile and desktop layouts. In this way, the content and the presentation are in separated files. The developer implements different presentations for different main types of devices, and by using Media Query, different CSS rules are applied.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',347,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(825,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,348,1568908895,1567774367,11,0,0,1016,'textpic','Mobile First: prima di tutto, per il Smartphone...','','','<p>Seguendo il modello Mobile First, il Responsive Layout  costruito in base ai dispositivi pi piccoli che l\'utente potrebbe avere, come uno smartphone o un tablet. Quando il disegnatore completa il layout per il dispositivo pi piccolo, aggiunger il layout per ogni dimensione dello schermo, nello stesso progetto.</p>\r\n<p>Ci sono due vantaggi principali del modello Mobile First:</p>\r\n<ol> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Il sviluppatore fa un piano di ci che  veramente necessario inserire nello schermo pi piccolo, e successivamente aggiunger il contenuto per lo schermo pi grande. Questo aiuta molto nella costruzione del sitemap.</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Con Mobile First, il codice sar semplice ed elegante. Gli smartphone hanno processori pi piccoli, quindi il codice non dovrebbe essere complesso. Successivamente,  possibile aggiungere altri stili per personalizzare il layout dello schermo del desktop.</li> </ol>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,1,0,17,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,250,2,NULL,'',0,'',348,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"Mobile First\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:824:\"<p>Following the pattern Mobile First, the Responsive Layout is built based on the smallest devices that the user might have, such as a smartphone or tablet. When the designer finishes the layout for the smallest device, he will add the layout for every screen size, in the same project.</p>\r\n<p>There are two main advantages of the pattern Mobile First:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>The designer makes a plan of what it is really necessary to put in the smaller screen, and later he will add the content for the wider screen.<br /> 	This helps a lot in the construction of the core of the website.</li> 	<li>With Mobile First, the code will be simple and elegant. Smartphones have smaller processors, so the code should not be complex.<br /> 	Later on, extra styles can be added to customize the layout for the desktop screen.</li> </ul>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:250;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:17;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',348,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(826,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,349,1568908962,1567774367,11,0,0,1020,'textpic','La tipografia','','','<p>La tipografia  l\'aspetto del testo. Il progetto della tipografia  cruciale per attirare l\'attenzione del visitatore, e incoraggiarlo a leggere ulteriori informazioni sul sito Web. Inoltre, la tipografia  importante per evidenziare o oppure no qualsiasi parte del testo sul sito Web. In pratica, una buona tipografia  quella che migliora la comunicazione con il visitatore.  molto importante che il testo sul sito Web sia facilmente leggibile.<br /> Queste atributi della tipografia sono il fattore chiave in fase di progettazione:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Font Family</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dimensione del testo</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Larghezza del testo</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Altezza della linea</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Il Font Family d l\'effetto emotivo della lettura del testo. Di solito, il disegnatore trova la famiglia di caratteri ottimale in base all\'argomento del sito Web. Altri tre parametri: dimensione del testo, larghezza del testo e altezza della linea determinano se il testo  facilmente leggibile.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Nel Responsive Web Design, la tipografia dovrebbe seguire anche alcune regole. Il disegnatore dovrebbe aumentare la dimensione del carattere quando passa a una versione pi grande dello schermo. Questo perch tendiamo a leggere a distanza quando il dispositivo  pi grande. Inoltre, il disegnatore non dovrebbe modificare le proporzioni tra il testo e altri elementi del sito Web. Lui dovrebbe prestare attenzione ai parti importanti del testo. Sottolineando un titolo dovrebbe mantenere il resto del testo in una dimensione relativa, in modo di attirare il visitatore.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',349,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Responsive Web Typography\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1392:\"<p>Typography is the appearance of the text. The way it is designed is crucial to attract the visitor, to hold his attention and to encourage him to read more information on the website. Also, typography is important in highlighting or not any part of the text on the website. Practically, good typography is the one that improves the communication with the visitor. It is very important that the text on the website is easily readable. These properties of typography are the key factor in the design phase:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Font family</li> 	<li>Font size</li> 	<li>Text width</li> 	<li>Line height</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The Font Family parameter gives the emotional effect of reading the text. Usually, designers find the optimal Font Family based on the topic of the website. Three other parameters Font Size, Text Width, and Line Height determine if the text is easily readable or not.</p>\r\n<p>In the Responsive Design, Typography should follow some rules also. The designer should increase the Font Size when switching to a wider screen version. This is because we tend to read from a distance when the device is bigger. Also, the designer should not change the proportions between the text and other elements of the website. The designer should pay attention to the highlights. By emphasizing a title it should also maintain the rest of the text in a relative size that attracts the visitor.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',349,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(827,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,350,1568909026,1567774367,11,0,0,1022,'textpic','Meno JavaScript, meglio  !','','','<p>I codici JavaScript non sono obbligatori in un sito Responsive Web Design.  vero che JavaScript rende il sito web pi gradevole e intuitivo, ma  possibile creare un disegno flessibile solo con HTML e CSS. Noi vi suggeriamo di mantenere il progetto pi semplice possibile. Questo  un fattore chiave per l\'intera performanca del sito web.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',350,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:28:\"Less JavaScript is better...\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:327:\"<p>JavaScript codes are not mandatory in a Responsive website. It is true that JavaScript makes the website nicer and user-friendly, but a fully Responsive Design can be created just with HTML and CSS. We suggest keeping the design project as easy as possible. This is a key factor for the whole performance of the website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',350,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(828,23,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,351,1568909078,1567774367,11,0,0,1023,'textpic','Ma dopotutto, il contesto mobile  pi che la dimensione dello schermo ...','','','<p>I dispositivi mobili fanno parte della nostra vita e li portiamo ovunque noi andiamo. Ma non sempre abbiamo una forte connessione a Internet. Inoltre, noi abbiamo bisogno delle informazioni il pi rapidamente possibile, poich spesso ci affrettiamo.<br /> Tenendo conto di tutto ci, la costruzione della versione mobile del sito Web non si limita semplicemente ad adeguare le dimensioni, ma risolve molti problemi di sviluppo mobile e la sfida  caricare il contenuto della pagina il pi rapidamente possibile, con tutte le sue funzionalit.</p>\r\n<p>Spero che questo articolo ti abbia aiutato a capire l\'obiettivo principale del Responsive Web Design, ma se ti senti ancora confuso al riguardo, puoi scriverci email. Se stai gi utilizzando la tecnica Responsive Web Design nel tuo sito o nella tua applicazione web, puoi convidere il link!</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',351,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:70:\"But after all, the mobile context is more than just the screen size...\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:934:\"<p>The mobile devices are part of our lives, and we take them wherever we go. But we dont have a strong internet connection in every moment. Also, we need the information as quickly as possible, as we often hurry up. Taking all these into consideration, building the mobile version of the website is not just adjusting the size, but also solving many problems of mobile development. The challenge is to load the content of the page as quickly as possible, with all its functionalities. This fast-loading design and build are mainly for the smartphones. Tablets and desktop versions do not need this immediate effect.</p>\r\n<p>Hopefully, this article helped you in understanding the main goal of Responsive Design, but if youre still feeling confused about it, dont be afraid to leave a question or comment. If youre already using responsive web design in your site or web application, share the link here so we can see!</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',351,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(829,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,726,1569456830,1569456809,10,0,0,192,'image','','','',NULL,0,0,0,0,1,730,0,1,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,1,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',726,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";s:5:\"image\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:1;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:730;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:1;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:4:\"none\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',726,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(830,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,645,1569643998,1569456809,10,0,0,896,'text','','','','<p><strong>5 arsye pr t kaluar shrbimet Web n outsource n Europn Lindore</strong></p>\r\n<p>Shum biznese n t gjith botn i zhvillojn produktet dhe shrbimeve t tyre n outsource drejt kompanive tjera. N fakt, outsource nuk sht nj teknik e re, por shpesh nuk sht i qart si koncept. N thelb, outsource ka t bj me delegimin e detyrave, shrbimeve ose prodhimit t kompanis drejt nj individe ose nj kompanie tjetr, me qllim minimizimin e kostos monetare si dhe kohs s realizimit t procesit. Ky prkufizim thekson qarte arsyet pse mund t kalohen produktet dhe shrbimet si outsource: pr t zvogluar kohn, koston dhe pr tia deleguar punn nj stafi m profesional. N t vrtet, bizneset mbulojn shum funksione e veprimtari, dhe kjo on n munges t burimeve njerzore dhe t nj stafi t specializuar pr do zhvillim t produktit, ose pr do shrbim q ata mbulojn. Kjo sht arsyeja pse ata delegojn disa shrbime n outsource drejt kompanive t specializuara n fushn prkatse.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',645,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:860:\"<p>Many businesses all over the world develop the products of their services by outsourcing some of their tasks. In fact, the concept of outsourcing is not a new technique, but often it is not clear enough. Lets see in details the definition of outsourcing as a concept itself.<br /> Outsourcing is the practice of delegating company tasks, services or product manufacture to an individual or another company, in order to save costs and time.<br /> The definitions put in light the reason why companies practice outsourcing. It is to reduce the time, cost and the work of the professional team. Actually, businesses cover more areas of activity, and this leads to a lack of resources and the professional staff for every product development, or for any service they cover. That is why they call for help other companies, specialized in the related area.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',645,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(831,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,646,1569944267,1569456809,10,0,0,960,'textpic','Rndsia e nj shrbimi outsource afatgjat','','','<p>Transferimi i nj procesi zhvillimi t aplikacionit Web nuk sht thjesht nj zgjidhje e menjhershme. Shpesh sht mjaft e prshtatshme t krijohet nj bashkpunim afatgjat me nj ofrues shrbimi outsource. Nj bashkpunim i till shmang vonesat dhe keqkuptimet q mund krijohen nga nj lidhje outsource e re.<br /> Partneriteti afatshkurtr pr outsource do t krkoj t mbledh dhe analizoj t dhnat ligjore, t dhnat pr burimet njerzore. T gjitha kto t dhna jan mjaft t vlefshme pr biznesin tuaj. Bashkpunimi afatgjat do t ndihmoj pr t zgjidhur kto shtje, sepse nj partner me t cilin bashkpunoni pr nj koh t gjat, do t njoh m thell nevojat dhe preferencat specifike tuaja pr biznesin. Partnert afatshkurtr nuk e njohin vizionin e biznesit tuaj. Ata nuk kujdesen pr qllimet tuaja n vazhdimsi.</p>\r\n<p>Ne ju rekomandojm q t vendosni nj partneritet afatgjat pr outsource, n vend q t punsoni nj partner t ri sa her q do t delegoni nj detyr.</p>\r\n<p>Gjat ndryshimeve dhe zhvillimit t politiks, ekonomis dhe t biznesit, n ditt e sotme Europa Lindore sht n fokusin e shum ndrmarrjeve q krkojn shrbime outsource n teknologji informacioni. Ky rajon sht vendbanimi pr shum zhvillues t apasionuar dhe t talentuar. Gjithashtu, n Europn Lindore jan pozicionuar shum kompani profesionale t programimit n Web. Kjo sht nj nga arsyet pr t deleguar shrbime Web n outsource t n Europn Lindore. M posht po jap n detaje disa avantazhe t tjera pr outsource n kt rajon.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',646,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:39:\"The importance of long-term outsourcing\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1507:\"<p>Outsourcing a Web Development task is not only an immediate solution. Its more convenient to set up long-term cooperation and to keep collaborating with the same service provider. Its because outsourcing business-related operations is a complicated process. There will be delays and misunderstandings that may be worth money and time.</p>\r\n<p>Short-term outsourcing partnership will demand to collect and analyze legal, HR, and commercial data that are valuable to your business. Long-Term cooperation will help to fix these issues, because a partner that you collaborate for a long time, will know more deeply your specific business needs and preferences. Short-term partners do not know the vision of your business. They dont care about your future business goals.</p>\r\n<p>We highly recommend you to set a long term outsourcing, instead of hiring a new partner each time you have a task.</p>\r\n<p>During changes and development in politics, economics and the whole perception of the business, nowadays the Eastern Europe is the focus of many companies that search for outsourcing their web development tasks. This region is becoming the residence for many motivated and talented developers. Also, here is located many professional companies of IT, Web Development, similar fields, and industries. &nbsp;This is one of the reasons why to outsource your Web Development task to Eastern Europe. Let us explain in details what other reasons and benefits are noticed in outsourcing in this area.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',646,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(832,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,647,1569456984,1569456809,10,0,0,992,'textpic','Kosto e ult, por cilsi e lart','','','<p>N biznesin e zhvillimit t aplikacioneve Web, shpesh prpiqemi t krahasojm mimet. Por kostoja monetare nuk sht kriteri i vetm. Shum kompani moderne nuk e din nse duhet t zgjedhin nj opsion t shtrenjt dhe me cilsi t lart apo nj opsion t lir, por me cilsi t dobt. N fakt, kompani t Europs Lindore ofrojn ekuilibrin optimal midis mimit dhe cilsis.</p>\r\n<p>Vende si Bullgaria, Polonia, Rumania dhe gjithashtu Shqipria do t ofron shrbime me cilsi t lart. Ata kan nj ekip profesional, dhe ju do t befasoheni nga rezultatet e tyre n inxhinierin software si dhe n zhvillimin e aplikacioneve Web. Statistikat tregojn se siprmarrje t tilla jan duke u rritur n numr, por duke ruajtur ekuilibrin me kosto t ult - cilsi shum t mir t shrbimit. Megjithat, disa nga faktort m t rndsishm pr tu mbajtur n mend, mbeten mijra projekte t suksesshme t realizuara nga zhvilluesit lokal t aplikacioneve Web.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',647,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Low cost but high quality\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:892:\"<p>In the softwares world, we often try to compare prices. But the cost is not the only priority. Many modern companies dont know if they should choose an expensive and high quality onshore or a cheap but poor quality option. In fact, Easter Europe offers the optimal balance between price and quality.</p>\r\n<p>Countries like Bulgaria, Poland, Romania and also Albania will offer high-quality service. They have a professional team, and you will be surprised by their results in software engineering also in Web Development Area. Statistics show that such companies are increasing in number, but maintaining the balance low cost- very good quality of the service. &nbsp;Some of the most important factors to keep in mind, however, remain the thousands of successful projects done by local website developers and web app developers demonstrating their masterful skills and hard-work.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',647,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(833,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,648,1569944295,1569456809,10,0,0,1008,'textpic','Arsimi sht nj faktor mjaft i rndsishm','','','<p>Universitetet e Europs Perndimore jan lider n Shkencat Kompjuterike, por Universitetet e Europs Lindore kan programet dhe lndt m t vshtira n degt e Shkencave t Natyrs dhe n Inxhinieri. Kjo do t thot q studentt q jan diplomuar n Europ Lindore, n programe studimi si Matematik, Informatik dhe Inxhinieri Elekronike jan shum t talentuar dhe me shum vullnet e pasion.</p>\r\n<p>Statistikat tregojn se mbi 35% e popullsis zotron diplom universitare, Shqipria ofron disa prej profesionistve m t arsimuar. N fakt kto statistika mund t\'ju befasojn, por nse keni komunikuar me profesionist t ktij rajoni, mund t keni vn re kt fakt: profesionalizm t bazuar n arsimim.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',648,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Education is a key factor\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:743:\"<p>Western Europe Universities are leaders in the IT Fields, but Naturals Sciences and Engineering have the toughest courses in Eastern Europe Universities. This means the students that are graduated in the Natural Sciences and Engineering are very good ones, with attitude and good results in Programming, Mathematics and Engineering courses.</p>\r\n<p>With more than 35% of the population holding university degrees, Albania offers some of the most educated professionals. While these statistics may come as a surprise to you, it was no surprise for everyone who has ever worked with local experts. The geographic benefits of the region generated a great base for the large talent pool of programmers, designers, and everything in-between.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',648,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(834,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,649,1569457073,1569456809,10,0,0,1016,'textpic','Lidhjet kulturore','','','<p>Disa kompani trhiqen nga mimet e ulta q kompanit ofrojn pr shrbimin software, por prapseprap, rezultati nuk sht i duhuri. Arsyeja mund t mos jet profesionale, por efekt i nj hendeku ndrmjet kulturave.</p>\r\n<p>Europa Lindore ndrthur t dy bott: Europn Perndimore dhe Azin. Zhvilluesit software q jan vendosur n kt rajon, i kuptojn mjaft mir t dy kulturat. Ata mund t flasin rrjedhshm shum gjuh t huaja dhe t ken etik europiane. Gjithashtu, ata e din m s miri rndsin e korrektess profesionale. T gjitha kto specifikime duhen marr parasysh kur t delegoni nj shrbim pr outsource drejt nj kompanie t huaj.</p>\r\n<p>Programuesit e Europs Lindore kan aftsi t mira n gjuhn angleze, n t shkruar dhe n t folur. Pr m tepr, shum prej tyre flasin rrjedhshm gjuhn gjermane, italiane ose frnge. Fleksibiliteti i tyre pr t komunikuar n gjuhn tuaj amtare do t oj n nj nivel mjaft t mir komunikimin mes jush.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',649,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:21:\"The cultural affinity\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1237:\"<p>Most companies make an important decision in outsourcing the project abroad. Taking into consideration all the factors, an important one is a cultural affinity. This is because West and Eastern countries often differ in culture and concepts.</p>\r\n<p>Some companies are attracted by the low prices that companies abroad offer for the specific service, but still, the result does not impress so much. The reason might not be professional but the effect of the multicultural gap.</p>\r\n<p>Eastern Europe combines both two worlds, Europe and the Eastern World. The developers that are located in this part, understand both cultures, by showing good expertise in the technological field. They can speak fluently many foreign languages and posses the European value of ethics. Also, they know best the importance of having a professional attitude. All these specifications are better to take into consideration when hiring a web development outsourcing company.</p>\r\n<p>Eastern European programmers have good English skills, both in writing and speaking. Moreover, many of them are speaking fluently German, Italian or French languages. Their flexibility to communicate in your native language will lead to a high level of understanding.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',649,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(835,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,650,1569942420,1569456809,10,0,0,1020,'textpic','Pozita gjeografike mjaft e favorshme','','','<p>Nj arsye pr t deleguar shrbime outsource drejt Europs Lindore sht pozita gjeografike. Natyrisht sht e leht t udhtosh drejt Europs Lindore dhe t marrsh pjes n takimet me grupin e puns, t kontrollosh nse bashkpunimi sht i suksesshm. &nbsp;Nj mundsi e till pr t par direkt procesin e puns ju bn t kontrolloni zbatimin dhe aftsin pr t realizuar ndryshime, ashtu si dshironi ose keni ju nevoj.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',650,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:31:\"The favorite geography position\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:473:\"<p>Another reason to outsource to Eastern Europe is the favorite location. its easier to travel to East Europe and to participate in team meetings, to check whether the collaboration is successful and to participate in the process. Its cheap to go to the neighboring country and ensure that you can trust your service provider. Such an opportunity to see the process brings better control over the implementation and ability to add changes as you want or need it.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',650,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(836,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,651,1569944366,1569456809,10,0,0,1022,'textpic','Trendi i aplikacioneve Mobile','','','<p>Zhvillimi i aplikacioneve Mobile ka prfshir mjaft siprmarrje n Europn Lindore, duke nxitur zhvilluesit lokal n krijimin e disa aplikacioneve shum t njohura pr paisjet Smartphone. Krahasuar me Evropn Perndimore dhe me USA, zhvilluesit e aplikacioneve Web dhe Mobile n Evropn Lindore ofrojn produkte me kosto mjaft t ult.</p>\r\n<p><br /> M posht po prmend disa statistika rreth projekteve n Web t Evrops Lindore:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Raporti i Easy of Doing Business 2018 tregon se vendet e Europs Lindore treguan nj rritje t konsiderueshme n krahasim me vitet e kaluara.</li> 	<li>PHP cilsohet si gjuha m e njohur dhe m e prhapur n t gjith vendet e Europs Lindore.</li> 	<li>Numri e programuesve n Node.JS sht rritur n t gjith vendet e Europs Lindore, gjat viteve t fundit.</li> 	<li>Shprndarja e zhvilluesve n Web dhe Mobile sht e ngjashme pr t gjith vendet e Evrops Lindore.</li> </ul>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',651,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:31:\"Advanced Mobile Web Development\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1628:\"<p>The trend of building and implementing Mobile Applications involved Eastern Europe, by provoking the local developers into creating some very popular applications on Smartphones. &nbsp;The developers located in Eastern Europe will impress you in building complex user interfaces and in complex functionalities of such applications, with low prices and very high quality. Compared to the American and Western Europe, the developers located in Eastern Europe offer low-cost products in outsourcing your Mobile Web Development.</p>\r\n<p>Some statistics and numbers related to the Web Development projects in Eastern Europe:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.doingbusiness.org/content/dam/doingBusiness/media/Annual-Reports/English/DB2018-Full-Report.pdf\">Ease of Doing Business 2018</a> rating shows that Eastern European countries demonstrated considerable growth in comparison with the previous years.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://infoshare.pl/news/one,66,248,1,central-eastern-europe-developer-landscape-2017-a-report-by-stack-overflow.html\">PHP</a> is reported to be the most popular and widespread language throughout Eastern European countries.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://infoshare.pl/news/one,66,248,1,central-eastern-europe-developer-landscape-2017-a-report-by-stack-overflow.html\">Node.JS developer share</a> has risen throughout Eastern European countries over the past few years<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://infoshare.pl/news/one,66,248,1,central-eastern-europe-developer-landscape-2017-a-report-by-stack-overflow.html\">The distribution of Web and Mobile developers</a> is similar across Eastern European countries.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',651,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(837,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,652,1569457221,1569456809,10,0,0,1023,'textpic','Si konkluzion:','','','<p>Kur kompani t ndryshme vendosin t delegojn shrbime outsource drejt zhvilluesve t aplikacioneve Web n Europn Lindore, me shum mundsi do ken avantazhe t tilla si: marrjen e nj produkti me kosto t ult dhe me cilsi t lart, n kushte t lehta pr t udhtuar, staf profesional q komunikon mir n anglisht. Pr m tepr, kto zhvillues software jan n gjendje t ofrojn zgjidhje inovative dhe unike.</p>\r\n<p>Duhet t kini parasysh se shrbimet outsource ndihmojn n uljen e kostove dhe prmirsimin e performancs s biznesit n t njjtn koh. Ata jan nj mundsi e shklqyeshme pr t zgjeruar horizontet dhe prfitimet e kompanive globale.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',652,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"To summarize:\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:554:\"<p>When the companies from Western Europe decide to use Eastern European app developers, they get such benefits: a low-cost product with a high-quality, comfortable time zone and easy to travel conditions, fluent English for successful cooperation. Moreover, these countries are able to deliver innovative and unique solutions.</p>\r\n<p>Keep in mind that outsourcing helps to cut the costs and improve business performance at the same time. It is a great opportunity to broaden the horizons and take advantage of global companies and their experience.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',652,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(838,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,726,1569602619,1569602523,11,0,0,160,'image','','','',NULL,0,0,0,0,1,730,0,1,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,1,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',726,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";s:5:\"image\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:1;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:730;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:1;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:4:\"none\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',726,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(839,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,645,1569602681,1569602523,11,0,0,320,'text','5 motivi per affidare i servizi Web in outsourcing nell\'Europa dell\'Est','','','<p>Molte aziende in tutto il mondo sviluppano i prodotti all estero. In effetti, questa non  una nuova tecnica, ma spesso non  abbastanza chiaro come funziona. In questo articolo aggiungeremo la definizione di outsourcing come un metodo di preparare i servizi all estero e cinque ragioni per farlo.</p>\r\n<p>Outsourcing  la pratica di creare prodotti e delegare servizi a una persona o un\'altra azienda, in modo di risparmiare costi e tempo.<br /> Questa definizione mette in luce il motivo per cui le aziende praticano l\'outsourcing: per ridurre il tempo, i costi e il lavoro del gruppo di professionisti.</p>\r\n<p>In realt, le aziende contengono diverse attivit e questo porta alla mancanza di risorse umane per ogni servizio. Questo  il motivo per cui molte aziende creano partnerita con altre aziende specializzate in un area in qui loro hanno bisogno di outsourcing.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',645,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:860:\"<p>Many businesses all over the world develop the products of their services by outsourcing some of their tasks. In fact, the concept of outsourcing is not a new technique, but often it is not clear enough. Lets see in details the definition of outsourcing as a concept itself.<br /> Outsourcing is the practice of delegating company tasks, services or product manufacture to an individual or another company, in order to save costs and time.<br /> The definitions put in light the reason why companies practice outsourcing. It is to reduce the time, cost and the work of the professional team. Actually, businesses cover more areas of activity, and this leads to a lack of resources and the professional staff for every product development, or for any service they cover. That is why they call for help other companies, specialized in the related area.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',645,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(840,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,646,1569944660,1569602523,11,0,0,352,'textpic','L\'importanza dell\'outsourcing di servizi Web','','','<p>Affidare in outsourcing un\'attivit di sviluppo Web non  solo una soluzione immediata e conviene di pi stabilire una cooperazione a lungo termine. Spesso l\'outsourcing  un processo non immediato. Una partnerit per affidare outsourcing a breve termine richieder di raccogliere e analizzare dati legali, risorse umane e commerciali che sono importanti per le decisioni della azienda. La cooperazione a lungo termine aiuter a risolvere questi problemi, perch un partner con cui collaborate da molto tempo conoscer pi profondamente le vostre esigenze e preferenze specifiche. Un partner a breve termine non conosce la visione della tua attivit. A lui non importa dei tuoi futuri obiettivi aziendali.</p>\r\n<p>Ti consigliamo di affidare un outsourcing a lungo termine, invece di assumere un nuovo partner ogni volta che hai un compito da finire.</p>\r\n<p><br /> Durante i cambiamenti e lo sviluppo in politica, economia e il business, attualmente l\'Europa dell\'Est  al centro di molte aziende che cercano affidare in outsourcing i loro servizi di sviluppo web. Questa regione sta diventando la residenza di molti sviluppatori appassionati. Inoltre, qui si trovano molte aziende professionali di tecnologia e di sviluppo Web. Vi spieghiamo in dettaglio quali sono i motivi e gli avvantaggi in outsourcing in servizi web.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',646,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:39:\"The importance of long-term outsourcing\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1507:\"<p>Outsourcing a Web Development task is not only an immediate solution. Its more convenient to set up long-term cooperation and to keep collaborating with the same service provider. Its because outsourcing business-related operations is a complicated process. There will be delays and misunderstandings that may be worth money and time.</p>\r\n<p>Short-term outsourcing partnership will demand to collect and analyze legal, HR, and commercial data that are valuable to your business. Long-Term cooperation will help to fix these issues, because a partner that you collaborate for a long time, will know more deeply your specific business needs and preferences. Short-term partners do not know the vision of your business. They dont care about your future business goals.</p>\r\n<p>We highly recommend you to set a long term outsourcing, instead of hiring a new partner each time you have a task.</p>\r\n<p>During changes and development in politics, economics and the whole perception of the business, nowadays the Eastern Europe is the focus of many companies that search for outsourcing their web development tasks. This region is becoming the residence for many motivated and talented developers. Also, here is located many professional companies of IT, Web Development, similar fields, and industries. &nbsp;This is one of the reasons why to outsource your Web Development task to Eastern Europe. Let us explain in details what other reasons and benefits are noticed in outsourcing in this area.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',646,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(841,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,647,1569602799,1569602523,11,0,0,368,'textpic','Ottima qualit e prezzo','','','<p>Nel mondo del software, spesso proviamo a confrontare i prezzi. Il costo non deve essere l\'unica priorit. Molte aziende moderne non sanno se dovrebbero scegliere un\'opzione onshore costoso e di alta qualit o un\'opzione economica ma di scarsa qualit. In effetti, l\'Europa dell\'Est offre l\'equilibrio ottimale tra prezzo e qualit.</p>\r\n<p>Paesi come Bulgaria, Polonia, Romania e anche l\'Albania offrono dei servizi web di alta qualit. In questi regioni ci sono aziende con il team di professionisti e rimarrai sorpreso dai loro risultati nell\'ingegneria del software e nell\'area di sviluppo Web. Le statistiche mostrano che molte aziende stanno aumentando di numero, mantenendo l\'equilibrio a basso costo e ottima qualit del servizio. Alcuni dei fattori pi importanti da tenere a mente sono moltissimi progetti di successo realizzati da sviluppatori di siti Web in questa regione europea.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',647,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Low cost but high quality\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:892:\"<p>In the softwares world, we often try to compare prices. But the cost is not the only priority. Many modern companies dont know if they should choose an expensive and high quality onshore or a cheap but poor quality option. In fact, Easter Europe offers the optimal balance between price and quality.</p>\r\n<p>Countries like Bulgaria, Poland, Romania and also Albania will offer high-quality service. They have a professional team, and you will be surprised by their results in software engineering also in Web Development Area. Statistics show that such companies are increasing in number, but maintaining the balance low cost- very good quality of the service. &nbsp;Some of the most important factors to keep in mind, however, remain the thousands of successful projects done by local website developers and web app developers demonstrating their masterful skills and hard-work.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',647,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(842,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,648,1569943993,1569602523,11,0,0,376,'textpic','L\'educazione  un fattore chiave','','','<p>Le universit dell\'Europa occidentale sono leader nei settori IT, ma le Scienze e la Ingegneria hanno dei corsi pi difficili nelle universit dell\'Europa dell\'Est. Ci significa che gli studenti laureati in Scienze e Ingegneria sono molto bravi, con attitudine nei corsi di Programmazione, Matematica e Fisica.</p>\r\n<p>Con oltre il 35% della popolazione in possesso di un diploma universitaria, l\'Albania offre dei professionisti in sviluppo Web. Queste statistiche possono essere una sorpresa per te, ma non  stata una sorpresa per quelli che hanno lavorato con esperti locali.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',648,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Education is a key factor\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:743:\"<p>Western Europe Universities are leaders in the IT Fields, but Naturals Sciences and Engineering have the toughest courses in Eastern Europe Universities. This means the students that are graduated in the Natural Sciences and Engineering are very good ones, with attitude and good results in Programming, Mathematics and Engineering courses.</p>\r\n<p>With more than 35% of the population holding university degrees, Albania offers some of the most educated professionals. While these statistics may come as a surprise to you, it was no surprise for everyone who has ever worked with local experts. The geographic benefits of the region generated a great base for the large talent pool of programmers, designers, and everything in-between.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',648,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(843,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,649,1569602898,1569602523,11,0,0,380,'textpic','L\'affinit culturale','','','<p>La maggior parte delle aziende prende una decisione importante nell affidare un progetto in outsourcing. Considerando tutti i fattori, un ruolo importante ha un\'affinit culturale. Questo perch i paesi orientali hanno diverse culture e concetti.</p>\r\n<p>Alcune aziende sono attratte dai prezzi bassi che offrono all\'estero, ma il risultato non impressiona per niente. La ragione potrebbe non essere professionale ma l\'effetto della differenze multiculturale.</p>\r\n<p>L\'Europa dell\'Est unisce le due culture, quella dell\'Europa dell\'Est. Gli sviluppatori che si trovano in questa parte, comprendono entrambe le culture, mostrando una buona esperienza nel campo tecnologico. Loro sono in grado di parlare diverse lingue straniere e possiedono il valore europeo dell\'etica. Inoltre, conoscono meglio l\'importanza di avere un atteggiamento professionale. Tutte queste specifiche sono da prendere in considerazione quando si assume una societ per affidare in outsourcing il sviluppo web.</p>\r\n<p>I programmatori dell\'Europa dell\'Est hanno una buona conoscenza dell\'inglese. Molti di loro parlano fluentemente tedesco, italiano o francese.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',649,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:21:\"The cultural affinity\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1237:\"<p>Most companies make an important decision in outsourcing the project abroad. Taking into consideration all the factors, an important one is a cultural affinity. This is because West and Eastern countries often differ in culture and concepts.</p>\r\n<p>Some companies are attracted by the low prices that companies abroad offer for the specific service, but still, the result does not impress so much. The reason might not be professional but the effect of the multicultural gap.</p>\r\n<p>Eastern Europe combines both two worlds, Europe and the Eastern World. The developers that are located in this part, understand both cultures, by showing good expertise in the technological field. They can speak fluently many foreign languages and posses the European value of ethics. Also, they know best the importance of having a professional attitude. All these specifications are better to take into consideration when hiring a web development outsourcing company.</p>\r\n<p>Eastern European programmers have good English skills, both in writing and speaking. Moreover, many of them are speaking fluently German, Italian or French languages. Their flexibility to communicate in your native language will lead to a high level of understanding.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',649,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(844,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,650,1569944099,1569602523,11,0,0,382,'textpic','Una posizione geografica molto favorevole','','','<p>Un altro motivo per affidare in outsourcing una azienda in Europa dell\'Est  la posizione geografica. In Europa dell\'Est  pi facile partecipare alle riunioni del team, verificare se la collaborazione continua essere positiva e a partecipare al processo. Inoltre  pi economico viaggiare in un paese vicino in Europa. Tale opportunit di vedere il processo porta a una migliore collaborazione e alla possibilit di aggiungere le modifiche che desideri.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,729,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',650,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:31:\"The favorite geography position\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:473:\"<p>Another reason to outsource to Eastern Europe is the favorite location. its easier to travel to East Europe and to participate in team meetings, to check whether the collaboration is successful and to participate in the process. Its cheap to go to the neighboring country and ensure that you can trust your service provider. Such an opportunity to see the process brings better control over the implementation and ability to add changes as you want or need it.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',650,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(845,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,651,1569944207,1569602523,11,0,0,383,'textpic','Uno sviluppo delle applicazioni per i Smartphone','','','<p>La tendenza dell sviluppo di applicazioni per i Smartphone e molto diffusa in Europa dell\'Est, provocando gli sviluppatori locali a creare alcune applicazioni molto popolari su Smartphone. Loro sono bravissimi nella costruzione d\'interfacce e in funzionalit complesse di tali applicazioni, con prezzi bassi e altissima qualit.</p>\r\n<p>Alcune statistiche su i progetti di sviluppo Web in Europa dell\'Est:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.doingbusiness.org/content/dam/doingBusiness/media/Annual-Reports/English/DB2018-Full-Report.pdf\">Ease of Doing Business 2018</a> mostra che i paesi dell\'Europa dell\'Est rappresentano una crescita considerevole rispetto agli anni precedenti.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://infoshare.pl/news/one,66,248,1,central-eastern-europe-developer-landscape-2017-a-report-by-stack-overflow.html\">PHP</a>  la lingua dei script pi popolare e diffusa in tutti i paesi dell\'Europa dell\'Est.<br /> <br /> Il numero degli sviluppatori che usano <a href=\"https://infoshare.pl/news/one,66,248,1,central-eastern-europe-developer-landscape-2017-a-report-by-stack-overflow.html\">Node.JS developer share</a>  aumentata in tutti i paesi dell\'Europa dell\'Est negli ultimi anni.<br /> <br /> La distribuzione di sviluppatori Web e Mobile  simile nei paesi dell\'Europa dell\'West.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',651,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:31:\"Advanced Mobile Web Development\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1628:\"<p>The trend of building and implementing Mobile Applications involved Eastern Europe, by provoking the local developers into creating some very popular applications on Smartphones. &nbsp;The developers located in Eastern Europe will impress you in building complex user interfaces and in complex functionalities of such applications, with low prices and very high quality. Compared to the American and Western Europe, the developers located in Eastern Europe offer low-cost products in outsourcing your Mobile Web Development.</p>\r\n<p>Some statistics and numbers related to the Web Development projects in Eastern Europe:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.doingbusiness.org/content/dam/doingBusiness/media/Annual-Reports/English/DB2018-Full-Report.pdf\">Ease of Doing Business 2018</a> rating shows that Eastern European countries demonstrated considerable growth in comparison with the previous years.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://infoshare.pl/news/one,66,248,1,central-eastern-europe-developer-landscape-2017-a-report-by-stack-overflow.html\">PHP</a> is reported to be the most popular and widespread language throughout Eastern European countries.<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://infoshare.pl/news/one,66,248,1,central-eastern-europe-developer-landscape-2017-a-report-by-stack-overflow.html\">Node.JS developer share</a> has risen throughout Eastern European countries over the past few years<br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://infoshare.pl/news/one,66,248,1,central-eastern-europe-developer-landscape-2017-a-report-by-stack-overflow.html\">The distribution of Web and Mobile developers</a> is similar across Eastern European countries.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',651,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(846,89,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,652,1569603266,1569602523,11,0,0,639,'textpic','Per concludere:','','','<p>Le aziende dell\'Europa occidentale spesso decidono di affidare in outsourcing dei servizi Web, alle aziende dell\'Europa dell\'Est perch:<br /> loro offrono un prodotto a basso costo con una alta qualit,<br />  comodo a viaggiare verso Europa dell\'Est,<br /> gli sviluppatori parlano benissimo inglese o tedesco,<br /> questi paesi sono in grado di offrire soluzioni innovative e uniche.</p>\r\n<p>Tieni presente che l\'outsourcing aiuta a ridurre i costi e a migliorare le prestazioni aziendali allo stesso tempo.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',652,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"To summarize:\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:554:\"<p>When the companies from Western Europe decide to use Eastern European app developers, they get such benefits: a low-cost product with a high-quality, comfortable time zone and easy to travel conditions, fluent English for successful cooperation. Moreover, these countries are able to del