merchants with a flexible shopping cart system, provides more than 50 payment gateways, &nbsp;it is based upon the PHP-based framework that helps in building scalable solutions. This platform comes packed with multiple plugins and extensions that can be easily integrated with the third-party apps. As it is built for the developers, so they do not have to start from scratch. The user needs expertise in PHP Programming. The Magento had two versions Magento 1 and Magento 2. The Magento 2 version is the latest development as more than 200,000 online retailers use it. This version offers tools to cover advanced marketing, catalogue management, and SEO needs.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(852,-1,622,0,0,0,1,1581950621,0,0,1556603138,1547549143,1,0,0,1792,'textpic','WooCommerce','','','<p>WooCommerce is a WordPress plugin that has user-friendly features and functionalities. It is free to download and renders enormous extendible features. If you want to start a perfect E-Commerce startup with a great website, then it is easily understandable and highly recommended. It provides plenty of options that support in building an amazing store with greater flexibility. Its professional, simple, possess latest WooThemes, and has many customization options. It connects all the major gateways to your website. It also renders Stripe and PayPal as the default payment gateways.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(853,-1,628,0,0,0,1,1582036868,0,628,1582033799,1582033799,13,0,0,2048,'textpic','Aimeos','','','<p>It is an open-source PHP library and an E-Commerce framework offering a set of featured components for online shop applications. The <a href=\"https://aimeos.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Aimeos</a>&nbsp;is integrated into simple to use components that are available for a wide range of frameworks. Its existing integrations include:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>TYPO3 Webshop extension</li> 	<li>Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>Laravel E-Commerce package</li> 	<li>Flow Online shop package</li> 	<li>SlimPHP E-Commerce package</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The main features of this platform consist of easy integration, faster operations, multi-store capability, highly scalable, flexible, mobile-optimized, and configurable.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"heade