4298461,7,0,0,5888,'textpic','A website increases your hours of operation','','','<p>Not only will your website be there 24 hours a day, 365 days a year with the possibility of reaching millions of people every day, but it will make it possible for your customers to contact you outside of your normal business hours. Your website, designed by W3DEVELOPMENT, is still working for you while you are at leisure or asleep.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(866,-1,438,0,0,0,1,1581950618,0,0,1556603298,1544298586,7,0,0,6144,'textpic','A website reduces costs','','','<p>A good website reduces publishing cost: It is the most affordable media where you can advertise your business and its products. You will reduce papers and print materials, and it is never locally, but a worldwide advertisement. You can keep your website more current, more affordable and easier to manage than any other media.</p>\r\n<p>A good website reduces marketing cost: You spend plenty hours in choosing the right word to say in a small space of a newspaper ad, or in a half minute in TV. A website offers an unlimited space for your business, you can put as many information as you need, by adding all type of multimedia content and making it more attractive than any other media.</p>\r\n<p>A good website reduces communication costs: The potential customers will get in the website all the information they need about your business, the images of the products, the map of the stores, the members of the team that offer the services, the phone number and e-mail where they can reach you, and any information you wish to communicate to the customers, but not only. Business partners, your team, suppliers, and everyone interested in your products and services will get this information from your website.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(867,-1,439,0,0,0,2,1583327420,0,0,1556603310,1544298649,7,0,0,6400,'textpic','A website enhances your company image','','','<p>The website is a representation of the vision of your business. It should reflect the spirit of you and your company. If its stylish and designed by W3DEVELOPMENT, it will highlight the best values for your store and products. It should be modern and updated, and even if it is a small business, it will portray itself in its big stature. The way you build your website is the image that the customers will perceive it.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(868,-1,441,0,0,0,1,1581950618,0,0,1556603333,1544298747,7,0,0,6912,'textpic','A website opens new channels of communication with staff, affiliates, agents and suppliers','','','<p>You can organize the content of the website in different levels, so different users can read vary information related to them. You can post information for your team in a closed location, so they reach it only by a password. It might include changes in the team, task schedule, events or notifications. Meanwhile, the wide web users access the product details, contact forms and public posts related to your company. You can put as much or as little information as you want on your site.&nbsp;</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:1