g skills. At the end of the setup, you can start building the online store.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(894,-1,360,0,0,0,1,1581950618,0,0,1559406791,1544250594,1,0,0,6400,'textpic','The easy platform','','','<p>Starting a new business is not easy. At least, the platform of the web store should be easy and helpful. If you choose a platform that adds stress in your work, then you should not focus on your own products and sales, but in the store itself. You better build your store in a platform you soon master and in which you are comfortable with.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify gives you the interactive way to build the website just by drag and drop the elements in the interface. You can set up the store just by moving the components in the way you like to arrange them, so you can quickly start selling. The process of adding new images to the store makes it unique and personalized. Also, the process of setting up the payment method is so easy so you can soon start making money, without worrying about the procedures.</p>\r\n<p>The beginning with Magento is a bit different. You should learn some technical terms and some code before start selling at a Magento store. Magento platform is less user-friendly and the process of setting up the store requires to navigate is some blocks before becoming a seller. Magento is powerful for experienced users, but a bit difficult for the beginners. This means you need some professional tricks to manage the full functionality it offers.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(895,-1,362,0,0,0,1,1581950618,0,0,1559406825,1544252701,1,0,0,6912,'textpic','Your budget, a key factor','','','<p>The budget is a factor you should consider in choosing the web platform. Shopify and Magento differ in their fees and in their operating costs. Shopify comes with a monthly fee, but it includes the host fee and maintenance service fee. Each premium application has an extra monthly fee.</p>\r\n<p>Magento is a free and open source software but it does not include the cost of hosting. Many Magento apps have fees and in an overall overview, you will need to consult to a web developer to integrate and to configure the Magento apps.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:1